src: ngemuva kwekuphotfula matikuletjeni wakhe matlakane wabambelela kuya enyuvesi ngemnyaka munye nanoma nje besebamemukele enyuv esi yasejozi (iuj) kutsi uyofundza tifundvo temtsetfo.
tgt: emva kokuphumelela kwakhe imatriki umatlakane ukhe waphumla unyaka wamnye nangona wayesele amkelwe kwiidyunivesithi yaserhawu tini (iuj) ukuba ayokwenza izifundo zobugqwetha.

src: wabuyela emuva kunel wayomcela lolunye futsi lusito loluyenti wabese umbonisa kutsi acele sikhulu sendzawo kutsi singete samupha yini umhlaba.
tgt: wabuyela kunel ukuya kucela olunye uncedo lobu limi waza wamcebisa ukuba athethe nenkosi yalapho malunga nokuba imnike umhlaba.

src: ngemuva kwekubona inchubekelembili yakhe epulasini lanel sikhulu sendzawo sabese simupha umhlaba longemahektha lange40 epulasini ibabirwa ba tau ya tswala lapho khona manje sekusepulasini lakhe lalima kulo.
tgt: emva kokuba inkosi ibone inkqubela yakhe kwifama kanel yamnika umhlaba ozi hektare ezingama40 kwifama ibabirwa ba tau ya tswala apho aliqhuba khona ngoku ishishini lakhe.

src: libutfo letemvelo livikela bobhejanes dale hes umelusi wetemvelo phakamani nyawo (loneminyaka yebudzala le26), lotinte esichiwini semvelo eumkhuze game reserve kwazuluna tal, ungulumumye webelu si laba1 659 temapaki ave lonkhe aseningizimu afrika (isanparks) lebanike umse benti wekunakekela imvelo etichiwini tekonga imvelo ta hulumende netangasese kuyo yonkhe iningizimu afrika.
tgt: oonogada bemiyezo yendalo bakhusela imikhombe dale hes umhloli wezendalo uphakamani nyawo (oneminyaka yobu dala engama26), nozinze kumyezo wolondolozonda lo, umkhuze game reserve kwiphondo lakwazuluna tal, ungomnye wabahloli bendalo abali1 659 nabanikwe uxanduva liliko lemiyezo yesizwe yasemzantsi afrika (isanparks) lokujo nga indalo kumaziko olondolozondalo karhulumente nawabucala kumzantsi afrika jikelele.

src: nyawo, loyincenye yemklamo wekulandzela temvelo lochutjwa yiepwp , ukholelwa ekutsi kubalulekile kufundzisa imimango mayelana nekunakekelwa kwemvelo.
tgt: unyawo, noyinxalenye ye projekthi yabahloli bezendalo eqhutywa yiepwp , ukholelwa ekubeni kubalulekile ukufundiswa koluntu malunga nokulondoloza indalo.

src: "sifanele kutsi sihambe siyo fundzisa imimango futsi siyente ivisise kutsi kungani kubalule kile kutsi kongiwe imvelo.
tgt: "kufanele siphume siye eluntwini ukuze silwazise ukuba kutheni kubalulekile ukuba siyilondoloze indalo.

src: ngu laphoke ummango utawuvisisa kutsi indzima ledlalwa tilwane tasendle", kwasho yena.
tgt: kulapho kuphela uluntu luyakuyazi indima nokubalule ka kwezilwanyana zasendle," utshilo.

src: loluhlelo, loluhlomisa bantfu labasha baseningizimu afri ka ngemakhono labawadzingako kute bakwati kusebenta etindzaweni tekonga imvelo nekuhlalisana kwetilwanyana netihlahla, sewente sicinise ko sekutsi nyawo uyakhona kunakekela umndeni wakhe.
tgt: le nkqubo, ixhobisa abemi basemzantsi afrika abase batsha ngezakhono aba zidingayo ukuze bakwazi ukusebenza kulondolozo lwendalo nenzululwazi engezilwanyana nezityalo, iqinisekisile ukuba unyawo uyakwazi ukukhathalela usapho lwakhe.

src: "luphahla lwendlu lelikhaya lemndeni wami manje seyifule lwe kahle kakhulu, alusavuti, futsi loko kungenca yemsebenti wami.
tgt: "ikhaya lam linophahla olo meleleyo ngoku, olungavuziyo.

src: kuyangitfokotsa kutsi ngatfola lelitfuba," kwasho yena.
tgt: konke oku kwenzeke ngenxa yomsebenzi wam.

src: edna molewa sewetse balandzele ligama lebujaha le litsi 'libutfo letemvelo' ngoba badlala umsebenti lomkhulu ekulweni nebugebengu, njenge kutingela kubulawe bobhejane ngalokungekho emtsetfweni.
tgt: umphathiswa wezendalo ugq edna molewa aba bahloli ubabiza ngokuba ‘ngoo nogada abakhusela imiyezo yendalo kuba badlala indima ebaluleke kakhulu ekulweni ulwaphulomthetho lwezendalo, olufana nokuzingelwa kubulawe imikhombe ngokungekho mthethweni.

src: "kulomnyaka lophelile kwakhishwa balandzeleli be temvelo la1 659 bayiswa etindzaweni letihamba embili ekutingelweni kubuye kubu lawe bobhejane ngalokungekho emtsetfweni kute bayokweleke lela ekuvikelweni kwemvelo.
tgt: "kulo nyaka uphelileyo kutyalwe abahloli bezendalo abali1 659 kwiindawo apho ukuzingelwa kubalawe imikhombe ngokungekho mthethweni kugquba khona ukuba bayokuncedisa ngokukhusela indalo.

src: batawutfola emakhono ekuba ngemancusa abobhejane ku letindzawo leti", kwasho yena.
tgt: bazakuxhotyiswa ukuba babe ngabakhuseli bemikhombe kwezi ndawo," utshilo.

src: nyawo bekayincenye yelicembu lelabamba umtingeli longekho emtsetfweni eumkhuze game reserve, lokwaholela ekutsi lesigebengu silahlwe li cala lebugebengu.
tgt: unyawo ube yinxalenye yeqela elabamba umzingeli ongekho mthethweni e–umkhuze game reserve, nokukhokelele ekufunyanisweni kwakhe enetyala.

src: "ngatigcabha ngemitamo yami futsi lelicala leli, kuba nelwati lolubanti ngekunakekelwa kwemvelo kwasita njengo ba kwaholela ekutsini abanjwe lomtingeli longekho emtsetfweni," kwasho yena.
tgt: "ndaziva ndizingca ngamalinge wam kwaye kweli tyala, ulwazi olunzulu ngokhuselo lwezilwanyana zasendle lwandinceda njengokuba lwakhokelela ekubanjweni kwalo mzingeli ungekho mthethweni," utshi lo.

src: luhlelo lwekudala imisebenti luvutsa emalangabi adele schormann working on fire (wof) ilawula luhlelo loluhlanganisile lwekulawula imililo lodalela imisebenti yebantfu labasha labanyenti labavela emimangweni lephuyile.
tgt: ukuthakazelele kakhulu ukudalwa kwemisebenzi adele schormann inkqubo yokucima imililo ebizwa iworking on fire (iwof) ilawula inkqubo edibeneyo yolawulo lwemili lo nethe yaqinisekisa ngokuba iqesha uninzi lolutsha oluvela kumakhaya ahlelelekileyo.

src: ngekwesekelwa ngetima li litiko letemvelo, loluhlelo luwela ngaphasi kweluhlelo lwetemisebenti yahulumende leyengetiwe (iepwp).
tgt: ngenkxaso yemali evela kwisebe lezendalo, le nkqubo ingena phantsi kwenkqubo yemisebenzi yoluntu enatyisi weyo (iepwp).

src: luniketa litsemba kulusha lolunyenti lolungatfoli imisebenti futsi selube nemphumelelo lencomeka kakhulu ekuvikeleni nasekulawuleni imililo yesiganga, lunciphisa lifutse lwayo.
tgt: inika ithemba kuninzi lolutsha olungafumani imisebenzi kwaye idlale indima enkulu ekuthinteleni nasekulawuleni imililo yamadlelo, nokunciphisa umo nakalo owenziwa yile mililo.

src: loluhlelo lucasha bantfu la bangetulu kwalaba5 000 la bavela emimangweni lephuyile luphindze futsi lubaceceshe kutekwati ngemlilo, temfundvo kanye nekuwucindzetela nala manye emakhono, njengelusito lwekucala, kubata, kupheka, temphilo netekuphepha kanye netekuchumana.
tgt: le nkqubo iqeshe abantu abangaphezulu kwabangama5 000 abasuka kwiindawo ezi hlelelekileyo kwaye ibaqeqeshe kwizakhono zokwazi ngemi lilo, ezemfundo, ukuthintela nokubamba umlilo unganwenwi kunye nezinye izakhono, ezifana noncedo lokuqala, ukuchwela, ukupheka, ezempilo nokhuseleko kunye nonxibelelwano.

src: sikhulu setekuchuma sewof lebogang maseko uchaze watsi loluhlelo luhlose bantfu labasha luphindze futsi lucasha bantfu labakhubatekile kutsi base bente etikhungweni talo letisetifundzeni.
tgt: igosa lonxibelelwano lewof uleboang maseko ucacisa uku ba le nkqubo igxile kulutsha ize iqeshe nabantu abakhubazeki leyo ukuba basebenze kumaziko abo amaphondo.

src: "sigcizelelaka kakhulu kutfutfukisa emakhono nekuni ka lusha imisebenti, lusha lolu sha loluvela etikolweni temabanga laphakeme noma lolusandza kuphotfula etikhungweni temfundvo lephakeme.
tgt: "sigxininisa kakhulu kuphuhliso lwezakhono size sibonelele ulutsha olusanda kuphuma kwizikolo zamabanga aphe zulu ngemisebenzi okanye olusanda kuthweswa izidanga kumaziko emfundo ephakami leyo.

src: kubaceceshwa balohlulelo, labange ma94% ngebantfu labasha, la bange31% bomake bese kutsi labayi3% ngebantfu labakhu batekile," washo acinisekisa.
tgt: kwabo baqeshwe kwiwof, abangama94% lulutsha, abangama31% ngabantu ba setyhini ize i3% ibe ngabantu abakhubazekileyo," ungqine watsho.

src: lorraine mokoena (lone minyaka yebudzala le31) wase mpumalanga ungulomunye webaceceshwa lowazuza kulo luhlelo.
tgt: ulorraine mokoena (one minyaka yobudala engama31) wasempumalanga ngomnye wabo baxhamlileyo kule nkqubo.

src: bekaloku asebenta lapha kawof yonkhe leminyaka le11 leyendlulile.
tgt: yiminyaka eli11 esebenza kwiwof.

src: ngemuva kwekuphotfula ma tikuletjeni washikashikeka imi nyaka lemibili angatfoli umse benti.
tgt: emva kokuphumelela kwakhe imatriki usokolile ukufumana umsebenzi isithuba seminyaka emibini.

src: sisi wakhe wabese umtjela ngaloluhlelo lwewof.
tgt: udade wabo wamxelela ngale nkqubo yewof.

src: kuphila nekucina kwemtimba nguyona ndlela lebaluleke kakhulu yekukhetsa labatawungena kulomsebenti futsi baceceshwa bafakwa eti gabeni tabo.
tgt: ukuphila qete yeyona nto ibalulekileyo kwizinto ezifunwayo phambi kokuba uthathwe kulo msebenzi kwaye ab a qalayo bavocwavocwa imizimba, beqeqeshwa.

src: ungaphumelela kusivivinyo ubese udzingeka kutsi uphumelele nakuluhlolo lwetemphilo kubeseke kuba ngukhona kucala lucecesho lwekucisha umlilo," kwasho yena.
tgt: xa uphume lele ukumelana nemithambo enzima yokuvocavocwa kufu neka uphu melele novavanyo lukagqirha uze emva koko uqalise uqeqesho lokuba ngumcimimlilo," utshilo.

src: mokoena wacala alijuniya lesicimamlilo futsi sewusebente ngekutikhandla wakhuphu ka waba ngumholi lomkhulu welicembu lebacimimlilo, uhola licembu lebacimimlilo laba18.
tgt: umokoena uqale njengomci mimlilo osaqalayo waza wase benza wenyuka wade wafikelela kwisikhundla sokuba ngumci mimlilo ophezulu weenkokheli zeqela labasebenzi, ekhokela iqela labacimimlilo abali18.

src: "lomsebenti uyintjintjile imphilo yami.
tgt: "lo msebenzi ubuguqulile ubomi bam.

src: ngimi kuphela lo nesibopho salokuya etfunjini se bantfwana bakitsi nebantfwana bami lababili.
tgt: ndim kuphela osebenzayo kubantwana base khaya nabantwana bam ababini.

src: manje ngiyakhona kondla umndeni wami ngiyise nebantfwana bami esikolweni," kwasho mokoena.
tgt: ngoku ndiyakwazi ukondla usapho lwam ndize ndithumele nabantwana bam eskolweni," utshilo umokoena.

src: "ukuvumile kutsi lomsebenti wekucima umlilo ngalokwetayelekile ungumsebenti wemadvodza futsi sewufundze kutsi acine abe nemandla ku lomkhakha.
tgt: uvumile ukuba icandelo locimomlilo ngokwesiqhelo lilicandelo elinabantu abangamadoda abaninzi kwaye ufunde ukuba omelele yena njengoko engumntu wasetyhini kulo msebenzi.

src: mokoena uphokophele ekube ni ngumphatsi wemisebenti yemacembu kuleminyaka lemibili letako.
tgt: umokoena uzimisele ekubeni ngumlawuli womsebenzi kule minyaka mibini izayo.

src: loku kutawumenta kutsi abe nesibopho sawo onkhe emacembu ewof lase mphumalanga.
tgt: oku kuza kumenza ibe nguye ojongene nawo onke amaqela ewof asempumalanga.

src: njengoba naku sesifikelwe sikhatsi semililo, mokoena unikete lamasu ekuvikela imililo yesiganga lalandzelako: ungalumeki imililo endzaweni levulekile uma ngabe angeke ukhone kuwu lawula.
tgt: njengoko sijongene nexesha lemililo yamadlelo, umokoena unikezela ngezi ngcebiso zi landelayo ukuthintela imililo yamadlelo: musa ukuntumeka imililo kwindawo evulekileyo xa ungazokwazi ukuyilawula.

src: kugucula temfundvo lephakeme amukelani chauke imfundvo lephakeme eningizimu afrika iyagucuka, akusiko kuphela kutsi sekulula ku tfola imfundvo lephakeme kodvwa futsi utfola leco ndziswe kahle kutsi imelane netidzingo tetimboni.
tgt: ukuguqula imfundo ephakamileyo amukelani chauke imfundo ephakami leyo yomzantsi afri ka iyaguquka, yaye le mfundo iphakamileyo aya nelanga nje ukufikeleleka kakhulu, kodwa ikwalunge lelaniswa neemfuno zoqoqo sho.

src: leti ngucuko timcoka ngoba live letfu lisebenta kulungiselela bantfu labasha kute bame lane nemisebenti nekufaka sandla kutemnotfo.
tgt: iinguqu ezi ziyafuneka njengoko ilizwe lisebenzela ukulungiselela abantu abase batsha imisebenzi nokuba negalelo kuqoqosho.

src: njengoba sive sigubha inya nga yelusha, ivuk’uzenzele ibukisisa indlela lusha lwale live luniketwa ngayo ema tfuba ekuphumelela litiko letemfundvo lephakeme nekucecesha.
tgt: njengoko eli lizwe libhi yozela inyanga yolutsha, ivuk’uzenzele iqwalasela indlela ulutsha lwelizwe olubonele lwa ngayo ngamathuba oku phumelela lisebe lemfundo ephakamileyo noqeqesho.

src: naledi pandor, indvuna yetemfundvo lephakeme nekucecesha lebekwe ngendlovana iniketwe u msebenti wekungenisa luhle lo lwemfundvo lephakeme yamahhala kulabo laba phuyile kanye nalabafundzi labavela kumindeni lehola imali lengetulu kwelizinga lelibekiwe kepha labasolo bangakhoni kukhokhela ti ndleko tasenyuvesi.
tgt: unyulwe ngenyanga yomdumba njengomphathi swa wemfundo ephakami leyo noqeqesho, unaledi pandor waza wanikwa u msebenzi wokuqalisa nge nkqubo yemfundo enga hlawulelwayo ukulungisele la abafundi abahluphekileyo nabo kuthiwa "bayalenga lenga".

src: emva kwesiteleka lesidze savelonkhe ngaphansi kwesihloko lesitsi: #fees mustfall, kwamenyetelwa ngengongoni kutsi lusha loluvela kumindeni lehola imali lengaphansi kwer350 000 ngemnyaka lutawu tfola imfundvo yemazinga laphakeme nekuceceshwa yamahhala.
tgt: emva koqhankqalazo lu kazwelonke oluthathe ixe sha elide phantsi komxholo othi: #feesmustfall , kwa ziswe okokuba ngenyanga yomnga ulutsha oluvela ku makhaya afumana imivuzo engaphantsi kwama350 000 eerandi ngonyaka luza kufu mana imfundo ephakamileyo noqeqesho engahlawule lwayo.

src: kuphake lwa kwalemfundvo kusachubeka fu tsi kutawutsatsa sikhatsi lesinge tulu kwemi nyaka lesihla nu.
tgt: sele izalisekiswa le nto, kwaye kuza kutha tha iminyaka emihlanu ukungeniswa kwayo.

src: luhlelo lwemfundzateindvuna pandor icinisekise kutsi kungeniswa kweluhlelo lwemfundzate kuchubeka kahle.
tgt: inkxasomali yebhasariumphathiswa pandor uqiniseki sile okokuba uku qaliswa kwenkqubo yebhasari kuhamba kakuhle.

src: "loluhlelo lolusha lwemfu ndzate likungenelela loku mcoka kwahulumende wase ningizimu afrika, ngoba, ecinisweni, bantfu baseningi zimu afrika imali yabo yentse la lekhokhela lemifundzate," washo njalo.
tgt: "le nkqubo yebhasari intsha ilinyathelo lokungenelela eliba luleke kakhulu likarhulumente womzantsi afrika nelabantu bomzantsi afrika kuba ziirha fu zabo ezi zihlawula le mali," utshilo.

src: loluhlelo lwemfundzate luni ketwa labo bafundzi labacala kungena emanyuvesi kanye nasemakolishi etifundvo te buciko bemisebenti yetandla kanye nekuceceshwa (ematvet), kuyo yonkhe iminyaka yekufundza.
tgt: le nkqubo yebhasari inikwa abafundi abalungeleyo abaqala ukungena eyunivesithi kwana bafundi beekholeji zemfundo noqeqesho kwezobugcisa (itvet), ngayo yonke iminya ka yokufunda.

src: lomfundzate wesekelwe nge mali leyengetiwe yahulume nde letigidzigidzi letir7.166 ngemnyaka we2018 – kwatsi tigidzigidzi ler4.581 tabeke lwa bafundzi labaphumelele kungena emanyuvesi kwatsi tigidzigidzi ler2.585 tabeke lwa bafundzi bemakolishi etvet.
tgt: kule bhasari urhulumente wongeze imali ezibhiliyoni zeerandi eziyi7.166 ngowa ma2018 – kuyo ezibhiliyoni eziyi4.581 yeyabafundi base yunivesithi abafanelekileyo ize yona ezibhiliyoni eziyi2.585 ibe yeyabafundi beekholeji zetvet.

src: indvuna pandor yatsi ema kolishi labukene nemikhakha letsite yetemfundvo angahle abe tikhungo tebuchwephesha letikhicita emakhono lancono kulowo mkhakha wesifundvo.
tgt: umphathiswa pandor uthe iikholeji ezizincutshe kwizifu ndo ezizodwa zingangamaziko abalaseleyo afana ngqo nazala ezona zona zakhono kwisigaba esithile semfundo.

src: sibonelo, likolishi lelilodvwa lingabukana kuphela nemse benti webunjiniyela betinjini bese kutsi lelinye libukane nebunjiniyela kutetindiza, wa chaza njalo.
tgt: umzekelo, enye ikholeji inga gxila kuphela kubunjineli bokulungisa oomatshini nezi thuthi ize enye igxile kubuchule bokuhamba ngenqwelomoya nezokuphapaha, uchaze ngeli tshoyo.

src: wangeta ngekutsi "ngiyatsemba kutsi kuvumela kutsi likolishi libukane kuphela netifundvo letitsite letimba lwa kulikusasa lemakolishi.
tgt: "ndikholelwa ekubeni ikamva leekholeji lisekubeni zibe ziincutshe kwizifundo ezithile," wongeze watsho.

src: "sifuna emakolishi etfu ente tifundzo letahlukahlukene.
tgt: "sifuna kungafanwa.

src: asifuni kutsi onkhe ente intfo lefanako.
tgt: asifuni okokuba zonke iikholeji zethu zenze into enye."

src: umshayeli wetikebhe longundzabamlonyeni allison cooper njengemshayeli we tikebhe letidvonsa letinye etransnet lindile mdletshe (loneminya ka yebudzala lenge30) usha yela tikebhe letinemandla letisebenta kusita kudvonsa leminye mikhumbi elugwini lasedurban.
tgt: umqhubi kadokolwane ushukumisa umzi allison cooper njengomqhubi ka dokolwane wakwa transnet ulindi le mdletshe (ominyaka inga ma30 ubudala) uqhuba oo dokolwane abanamandla abasetyenziswa ekunce diseni iinqanawa ukuba zikwazi ukungena kwizibu ko lasedurban.

src: nanoma titi ncane ngebukhulu, letikebhe tinemandla kakhulu kantsi kutishayela kudzinga likho no lelisezingeni lelisetulu.
tgt: noxa be bancinci, oodokolwane ba namandla ngolona hlobo kwaye ukuqhutywa kwabo kufuna ubunono nobuchule.

src: mdletshe watalwa futsi wakhulela eport shepstone wabese ufundza est faiths.
tgt: umdletshe wazalelwa wakhulela eport shepstone, wafunda est faiths.

src: "mine ngakhula kamna ndzi kakhulu.
tgt: "akukho nto sasinga dibani nayo ngethuba si sakhula eport shepstone.

src: lommango, lebalawula nawo lesichiwu ngekusebentisana neeastern cape parks and tourism agency (iecpta) ngapha nsi kwelikhayalethu com munal property association (ilcpa), batfole imali letigidzi ler6 levela kulitiko letemvelo kutsi basungule umkhakha wekukhulisa umnotfo ngetasendle kulesichiwu lesinemahekta la 1 400 lebatsengelwe sona litiko lekutfutfukiswa kwetindzawo tasemaphandleni netingucuku kutemhlaba.

src: bosotimboni bemakhemikhali labamnyama basefreyistata bakha ematfuba emsebenti more matshediso inkhapani yakule ndzawo lekhicita ema khemikhali iyasi ta ekulweni nekuswe lekala kwematfuba emse benti ngekutsi yakhe ema tfuba emsebenti lasimeme lalinganiselwa kuma70 endzaweni yaseharrismith, efreyistata.
tgt: oosomashishini bezamachiza basefreyistatha badala imisebenzi more matshediso inkampani yeli eyenza iikhemikhali incedisa kwidabi lokulwa ingxaki yokunqaba kwemisebenzi ngokuthi idale imisebenzi esisigxi na engama70 eharrismith kwiphondo lasefreyistatha.

src: ikevali chemicals yinkhapani yekucala lephetfwe ba ntfu labamnyama kulendzawo yasefreyistata lekhicita imihlo bo lehlukene yemakhemikhali ekucwenga emanti, ekuhlobisa endlini nekuhlanta imithoyi kanye nekwekunamatselisa.
tgt: ikevali chemicals yinkampani yokuqala yasefreyistatha eye yabantu abamnyama eyenza iikhemkhali.

src: lenkhapani yasungulwa nga2014 bangani labasihlanu labanelwati ngemakhemikhali, timphahla letitsengiseka masi nyane, kutfutfukiswa kwe mikhicito, kanye netinhlobo letahlukene teglu yekunama tselisa.
tgt: le nkampani yenza iintlobo ezahlukeneyo zeekhemikhali zokuhluza ukungcola emanzini, ezokucoca endlwini kunye nakwizindlu zangasese futhi yenza neglu yokuncamathisela.

src: umcondzisi lomkhulu wekevali chemicals funeka khumalo utsi ibis yasekela inkhapani yakhe kutsi itfole imishini nemathulusi kute icale kukhicita nekusungula umkhi cito wekucwenga emanti, weku hlobisa nekubulala emagci wane kanye netinhlobonhlobo teglu yekunamatselisa.
tgt: le nkampani yasekwa ngowa ma2014 ngabahlobo abahlanu abazingcali zeekhemikhali, kwiimpahla ezithengiseka ngokukhawuleza, kumsebenzi wokuqaliswa nokudidiyelwa kweemveliso ezintsha kunye nakwiintlobo ezahlukeneyo zeglu yokuncamathisela.

src: "uma sicala kwafanele kwekutsi sifake imali kute lebhizi nisi icale kusebenta kodvwa sabese sesitfola kusekelwa ngetimali belitiko letekuhwe belana netimboni (idti) ngekusebentisa ibis kanye nenhlangano yekutfutfukisa timboni (iidc)," asho anaba.
tgt: umlawuli wesigqeba wakwa kevali chemicals ufuneka khu malo uthi ibis yayinceda inkampani yabo yatsho yakwazi ukuthenga oomatshini kunye nezinye izixhobo zokuqalisa ukuvelisa iimveliso zokuhluza ukungcola emanzini, ezokucoca endlwini nezokubulala iintsholongwane kunye neglu yokuncamathisela.

src: ibis iluhlelo lwesibonelelo salenchubomgomo yaboso timboni labamnyama lehlose kuvula ematfuba lakhona kubosotimboni labamnyama eninizimu afrika ngekusebe ntisa indlela yekungenelela noma njani ngetimali nanga lokunye lokungadzingi imali, ngendlela lehlosiwe futsi lecha zwe kahle.
tgt: "ekuqaleni kwanyanzeleka ukuba sifake imali kweli shishini ukuze likwazi ukuqalisa ukusebenza kodwa ethubeni saye safumana inkxasomali kwisebe lezorhwebo noshishino (idti) ekhutshwa yibis kunye nequmrhu lophuhliso lwamashishini (ipic)," ucacise watsho ukhumalo.

src: khumalo utsi kwabatsatsa imali lelinganiselwa kutigidzi ler18 kutsi lebhizinisi ikhone kucala kusebenta netinyanga letilinganiselwa ku11 kutsi bacale kwenta inzuzo.
tgt: ibis yinkqubo yezibone lelomali yomgaqonkqubo woosomashishini abamnyama eyenzelwe ukuvulela amathuba oosomashishini abamnyama basemzantsi afrika ngokuthi banikwe uncedo olungayimali okanye lube zezinye izinto ezinge yomali olulungiselelwe kanye bona kunye neemeko zabo.

src: lenkhapani isabalalisa imikhicito yayo kuyo yonkhe iningi zimu afrika kanye naseuganda, namibia, nasetanzania.

src: khumalo utse lomtselela lenkhapani lebe nawo etimphi lweni tebantfu bendzawo mkhulu kunekwakha ematfuba emsebenti.

src: "kuko konkhe nalokungetulu kwekwakha ematfuba emsebe nti kubantfu bendzawo, sinelu hlelo lwekusisa emmangweni lapho sisita khona bomake basemadolobheni nasemakhaya kutsi batisungulele emabhi zinisi lasemancane lasebenta ngekukhicita imikhicito yekuhlobisa nekucoceka emakhaya," asho alandzisa.

src: munye waletisebenti lone ticu tebunjiniyela sthembiso mthembu utsite uyajabula kakhulu kutsi atfole umsebenti.
tgt: omnye wabasebenzi balo mzimveliso ngusthembiso mthembu onesidanga sobunjineli, uthi uvuya kakhulu ngalo msebenzi.

src: "besolo ngihleli ekhaya umnyaka wonkhe nginga wutfoli umsebenti.
tgt: "ndihleli ekhaya unyaka wonke ndingafumani msebenzi.

src: lelitfu ba lingisitile kutsi ngikhone kunelisa tidzingo tami nemndeni wami.
tgt: lo msebenzi undincedile kuba ngoku ndiyakwazi ukuzondla mna nekhaya lam.

src: noma ngineticu tebunjiniyela bemakhenikhali kodvwa bengingakwati lokunyenti ngekuhlanganisa imoto.
tgt: nango na ndinesidanga sobunji neli kwezokukhanda iinjini noomatshini akukho nto ingako bendiyazi ngokwenziwa kweemoto.

src: lokuceceshwa lesikutfolile kusisitile kutsi sibe nelwati lolujulile," asho ananatela.
tgt: olu qeqesho silufumeneyo lusincedile satsho sazithemba nathi ngomsebenzi wethu," utshilo.

src: sikhulu lesiphetse temisebenti mhlabawonkhe sakamahindra arvind ma tthew utsi lenkhapani ihlose kutsenga ma40% waletinye tetintfo talamaveni emapik up kutitolo takuleli.
tgt: isikhulu semisebenzi yehlabathi sakwamahindra uarvind matthew uthi le nkampani ineenjongo zokuthenga ama40% eentsimbi zepik up apha emzantsi afrika.

src: uma imphilo ikunika emalamula, walime amukelani chauke litiko letekulima lasenshonalanga kapa lichuba luhle lo lolusita balimi labasha nalasebabomnkantjubovu ngeluhlelo lwekusita kusu kela kucalwa nje ngelilanga lekucala – uma badzinga lusito lwemali – kute kube ngulapho nabo sebakhona kutimela.
tgt: amathuba owafumana ebomini, wasebenzise amukelani chauke isebe lezolimo lasentsho na koloni liqhuba inkqu bo enceda amafama asa qalayo nalawo sele emile ngenkxaso ukusuka mhla ubani waqalisa ukufama xa efuna uncedo ngezimali ade akwazi ukuzimela.

src: loluhlelo lwekusita ne kutfutfukisa balimi selusite bantfu labasha njenga wayne mansfield (lone minyaka lenge33 budzala) wasepaarl, losuke ekube ni ngusitolosiyandzindza lobekatsengisela malume wakhe emakethe yasekapa ngesikhatsi asafundza siko lwa watsengisa ngephandle kweminyele yakuleli laseni gizimu afrika emalamula lawalima yena ngekwakhe emhlabeni lawurentako.
tgt: inkqubo yokuxhasa noku phuhlisa amafama incede abantu abatsha abafana nowayne mansfield (one minyaka engama33 ubudala) wasepaarl, osuke ekubeni ngu mthengisi wasesitalatweni osebenzela utatomncinci wa khe emarikeni yasekapa xa kuvalwe izikolo waya ekube ni ngusomashishini othume la kumazwe angaphandle iilamuni azilima ngokwakhe kumhlaba awuqeshileyo.

src: eminyakeni lelishumi le yendlulile, ngesikhatsi angusomabhizinisi lone minyaka lenge23 budzala, mansfield wala litfuba leku sebenta epulazini lebeka cupha kulo emalamula bese uyawatsengisa.
tgt: kwisithuba seminyaka eli shumi edlulileyo, umansfield engusomashishini osakhasayo oneminyaka engama23 ubu dala, zange asithathe isithuba somsebenzi awayesifumana kwifama awayethenga kuyo iilamuni awayezithengisa ngelo xesha.

src: kwengeta ekutsini bekasesemncane futsi ete nenkhabunkhabu yekulima.
tgt: isizathu sakhe yayikukuba ngelo xesha waye ngenamdla kwinto yokuba ngu mfama.

src: nanoma kunjalo, emi nyakeni letsite ekuhambeni kwesikhatsi, wantjintja u mcondvo wakhe ngesikhatsi abona kukhula lizinga leku funwa kwemalamula.
tgt: kodwa ekuhambeni kwemi nyaka, oku kwaye kwatshi ntsha xa ebona indlela iilamu ni ezithengwa ngayo.

src: "ngaphindze ngacaphela kutsi balimi nabo bebenta loku bekwentiwa ngitsi tsi ne bositolosiyandzindza – bebatipakishela imikhicito yabo bese bayoyitsengisa emakethe ekapa.
tgt: "ndaqaphela ukuba amafa ma nawo enza le nto nathi bathengisi basesitalatweni sasiyenza ayezipakishela iimveliso zawo aze aye kuzi thengisa emarikeni yasekapa.

src: ngabese ngiyacaphela kutsi kunge nteka kutsi masinyane nje angeke sibe nebantfu la banyenti lesitawubatse ngisela tsine bositolosi yandzindza," kwasho yena.
tgt: ndaye ndaqonda ukuba thina njengabathengisi basesitala tweni siza kungabi nabantu siza kubathengisela.

src: kutsite nga2013, umlimi wendzawo wavuma kucece sha mansfield waphindze wamrentisela umhla ba longemahektha la12.
tgt: malunga nonyaka wama2013, umfama walengi ngqi wavuma ukuba afundise umansfield onke amaqhinga okuba ngumfama waza wamni ka umhlaba ozihektare ezili12 ukuba awuqeshe.

src: waphindze futsi wamfakela emaphayiphi ekunisela lo kwenta kutsi mansfield akho ne kulima.
tgt: waya wa faka nemibhobho yokunkce nkceshela into leyo yanceda umansfield watsho wakwazi ukulima.

src: nga2015, wakhona kutse ngisa emalamula lange mathani lange31 ngapha ndle kweminyele yale li laseningizimu afrika kwaphindze futsi kwatsi nga2016, lelinani lakhula kakhulu laba ngemathani la168.
tgt: ngowama2015, wakwazi ukuthumela kumazwe anga phandle umthwalo weelamuni ozitoni ezingama31.

src: loku kwenteke ngenca yelusito lolwatfolwa kulu hlelo lwekusita nekutfu tfukisa balimi lokungu lo lolwenta kutsi nga2015 atfole sibonelelo kuluhle lo lolukhulu lwekusitwa ngetekulima (icasp).
tgt: oku kwenzeka ngenxa yoku fundiswa nokuqeqeshwa ngu makhwekhwetha kunye nangoncedo awalifumana kwinkqubo yokuxhasa noku phuhlisa amafama into leyo yamenza wafumana isibone lelomali senkqubo ebanzi yokuxha sa ezoli mo (icasp) ngowama2015.

src: loku kwa menta wantinta wabuye fu tsi waba ngumlimi londlo ndlobele.
tgt: esi sibonelelomali samnceda kakhulu watsho wazinza futhi nefama yakhe yakhula.

src: kuhlomisa abalimi ngemakhono ebalimiloluhlelo lwekusita nekutfutfukisa balimi luhlose kwakha emakhono emima ngo nebantfu labebakadze bancisheke ematfuba phambi lini, ikakhulu labo labazuze ekuhlelweni kabusha kwe mhlaba.
tgt: ukuxhobisa amafama ngezakhonoinkqubo yokuxhasa nokuphuhlisa amafama ilungiselelwe ukuxhobisa ngezakhono abantu ababehlelelekile ngaphambili, ingakumbi abo baxhamla kwinkqubo karhulumente yokubuyiswa kwemihlaba.

src: lusita balimi labasakhasa, labalimela kutidlela bese batsengisa loko lokusa lako, balimi labanemhlabatsi lomncane kanye nebalimi labakhulu labalimela kutsengisa etimakethe letinkhulu.
tgt: inceda amafama asakhasayo, lawo alimela ukuzondla wona neentsapho zawo, lawo aneefama ezincinci kunye nalawo arhwebayo.

src: umlawuli wemklamo weluphiko lolubukene nekutfutfukisa tekulima shaheed martin kulitiko letekulima lasenshonalanga kapa utsite loluhlelo selusite balimi basimama.
tgt: umlawuli weeprojekthi wecandelo lenkxaso yophuhliso lwezolimo kwisebe lezolimo lasentshona koloni ushaheed martin uthi le nkqubo incede amafama atsho akwazi uku zimela.

src: inhi seyifike kutekunakekelwa ngetemphilo letincono vukuzenzele unnamed indvuna yetemphilo dkt.
tgt: inhi yinkqubo yeenkonzo zempilo engcono kakhulu vukuzenzele unnamed umphathiswa weze mpilo ugq aaron motsoaledi uthi umthethosihlomelo oyilwa yo weinshorensi yesizwe yezempilo (inhi) uza ku wuphucula umgangatho weenkonzo zempilo emza ntsi afrika.

src: aaron motsoaledi utsi umtsetfosivivinyo wekuchibela tindzaba te mshwalensi wavelonkhe we temphilo (inhi) utawenta kancono lizinga letinsita te temphilo eningizimu afrika.
tgt: ugq motsoaledi ebethe tha kutsha nje kwintla nganiso nonoondaba apho ebenika iinkcukacha ezi gcweleyo ngomthethosihlo melo oyilwayo wenhi kunye nomthethosihlomelo oyilwa yo wezikimu zezonyango.

src: motsoaledi bekakhuluma emhlanganweni webetindza ba losandza kubanjwa lapho beketfula khona umtsetfo sivivinyo wekuchitjelwa kwetindzaba tenhi kanye nemtsetfosivivinyo wekuchi bela tindzaba tetikimu tete kwelashwa.
tgt: le mithetho iyilwayo inga maqalela amalinge okulu ngiselela ukuba abantu abaninzi bafumane iinkonzo zonyango ngenhi.

src: lemitsetfosivivinyo ivula indlela yekutsi babe banengi bantfu labatfola tinsita tete mphilo ngekusebentisa inhi.
tgt: umthetho oyilwayo ngu mthetho ongekagqitywa osafuna ukugqithiswa kuwo onke amanqanaba okwenzi wa komthetho.

src: umtsetfosivivinyo luhlaka lwemtsetfo.
tgt: imithetho eyilwayo emininzi ibhalwa lisebe likarhulumente, isebe elo likhokelwa ngumphathi swa walo.

src: imitsetfosivivi nyo leminyeti yentiwa litiko lahulumende ngekucondzi swa yindvuna lefanele.
tgt: umthetho oyilwayo kufuneka uvunywe yikha bhinethi phambi kokuba unge niswe epalamente.

src: lomtse tfosivivinyo ufanele kutsi ubese uvunywa yikhabhine thi ngembi kwekutsi wetfulwe ephalamende.
tgt: ukungeniswa kwale mi thetho iyilwayo mibini ku thetha ukuba umzantsi afri ka sele kumbovu ukuba ube nenkqubo yeenkonzo zempilo zomntu wonke, into leyo ethe tha ukuba inhi iza kuba ngu mthetho kungekudala.

src: lokwetfulwa kwalemitse tfosivivinyo lemibili kusho kutsi inigizimu afrika seyi dvute ngesinyatselo sinye ekutsini itfole tekunakekelwa kwebantfu ngelizinga lelihle letemphilo ngalokufananako lokusho kutsike masinyane nje inhi itawuba ngumtse tfo.
tgt: le nkqubo iza kuqinisekisa uku ba bonke abemi bomzantsi afrika bayazifumana iinko nzo zempilo ezibalukeleki leyo, nokuba umntu usebenza phi na okanye akanayo imali yokubhatala inhi.

src: inhi iyinchubo yekusita ngetimali letawenta sicinise ko sekutsi tonkhe takhamuti taseningizimu afrika titfola tinsita tetemphilo letibalule kile, ngekungakhatsali ngeti mo tabo temsebenti kanye ne kutsi bayakhona yini kufaka imali ngco kulesikhwama.
tgt: ugq motsoaledi uthi urhulu mente uyayazi ukuba abanye abantu bakholelwa ekubeni akufuneki kuthethwe noku thethwa ngenhi, ingeka lungiswa inkqubo karhulu mente yezempilo ekwisimo esimaxongo kuqala.

src: motsoaledi utsite hulu mende uyati kutsi kukhona bantfu labakholelwa eku tsini kungakacalwa nje kutsi kukhulunywe ngenhi, ku nesidzingo sekutsi kucalwe ngekulungisa simo setinsita tetemphilo letintengantenga ko sasenigizimu afrika.
tgt: uthi urhulumente uyazazi iingxaki zeenkonzo zempi lo ezingekho mgangathweni nezisokolekayo ukuba zifu nyanwe kumaziko ezempilo karhulumente.

src: utsite hulumende uyatati letinkinga telizinga lelibi ne kweswelakala kwemakhono kutekunakekelwa ngetemphi lo tahulumende.
tgt: ugq motsoaledi uthi isi cwangciso sophuhliso sesi zwe (indp) saphawula ukuba ikhona ingxaki kwi inkonzo zempilo kumaziko karhulumente kwaye ngo kuqalisa inkqubo yenhi kuza kulungiswa ingxa ki yeenkonzo zempilo ezi ngekho mgangathweni ku maziko karhulumente kunye neyeendleko eziphezulu ku maziko abucala.

src: mtsoaledi utsite luhlelo lwekutfutfukisa lwavelonkhe (indp) yakucaphela loku nekutsi futsi ekufezekiswe ni kwalenhi, kudzingeka kutsi kulungiswe lelizinga le libi letinsita tetemphilo kanye netindleko tetinsita tete mphilo letibitwa tikhungo tete mphilo letitimele.
tgt: nangona izilungiso kule mi thetho iyilwayo zisagwadlwa, isebe liza kuqalisa ngeeproje kthi zenhi ezine ubuncinane.

src: ngesikhatsi kusasebanjwe tinkhulumomphikiswano mayelana netichibelo tale mitsetfosivivinyo, lelitiko lita wufezekisa lokungenani imi klamo lemine yenhi, lefa ka ekhatsi tinsita tetemphilo etikolweni, tinsita tetemphi lo talabagula ngengcondvo, tinsita tetemphilo tabomake labakhulelwe labanebumati ma nekukhulelwa kwabo eti bhedlela letinge22 letitsintse ke kakhulu kanye newesi fo semdlavuta (ioncology), ngekusita kakhulu igau teng nekwazulunatal, ko dvwake kube kungabekwa eceleni letinye tifundza.
tgt: ezi projekthi ziquka iinkonzo zempilo ezikolweni, iinko nzo zempilo zabaphazamiseke engqondweni, iinkonzo zempi lo zoomama abakhulelweyo abaneengxaki ngezisu zabo kwizibhedlela ezichapha zeleke kakhulu ezingama22 kunye neoncology .

src: motsoaledi uphindze watsi tindleko letibitwa tikhungo temphilo letitimele atifinyele lwa takhamuti taseningizimu afrika letinyenti.
tgt: nangona nje nawo amanye amaphondo eza kuhoywa, kodwa ezi pro jekthi ziza kugxininisa kakhu lu kwiphondo lakwazuluna tal nelasegauteng.

src: sekubekwe loyo bekakadze alijaji lelikhu lu sandile ngcobo yikho mishini yetekuncintisana ku tsi ente lucwaningo ngetindle ko tetinsita tetemphilo leti bitwa tikhungo tetemphilo letitimele.
tgt: ugq motsoaledi uphinde wongeza wathi imali ebi zwa ngamaziko onyango abucala ayifikeleki kube mi beli abaninzi, kanga ngokuba kutyunjwe lowo wayesakuba yijaji eyintloko usandile ngcobo yikomishi ni yezokhuphiswano ukuba aqhube uphando ngeendleko zempilo kumaziko onyango abucala.

src: "letichibelo lesitetfula ko tentelwe kuletsa lusito lolu dzingeka kakhulu kutigu lane letititfola tikuletinkhulu tinkinga tekubabete imali," kwasho yena.
tgt: ezi zilungiso ziza kuqaliswa ziza kunceda kakhulu aba ntu abagulayo abasengxakini yokungabi namali.

src: motsoaledi utsite sichibe lo sekucala salomtsetfosivi vinyo sitawucedza kukhokha ngekuhlanganyela nomake kutsi kube khona imali nawe loyikhiphako ekhikhini lakho.
tgt: ugq motsoaledi uthi isilu ngiso sokuqala kulo mthetho uyilwayo siza kubhangisa le nkqubo isetyenziswayo ngo ku yokuba abantu kufuneka bongeze imali kule ibhatalwa zizikimu zonyango zabucala.

src: imisebenti yesikhungo sekunika lusito ngeticelo letifakiwe yanga2018 vukuzenzele unnamed yini sikhungo sekunika lusito ngeticelo letifakiwe?
tgt: imisebenzi yeofisi kazwelonke yokuqwalasela izicelo yowama2018 vukuzenzele unnamed yintoni iofisi kazwelonke yokuqwalasela izicelo (icach)?

src: sikhungo sekunika lusito ngeticelo letifakiwe (icach) luhlelo lwesikhashana lolacalwa litiko letemfundvo lephakeme nekucecesha kusita titjudeni letifuna kungena eluhlelweni lwetikolo temfundvo lephakeme nekucecesha ngemuva kwamatekuletjeni (ipset) kodvwa kutfolakale kwekutsi tingahle tibukane nesimo lapho khona: bafake sicelo ngesikhatsi esikhungweni labasitsandzako kodvwa sicelo sabo sangamukeleki kantsi nyalo sikhatsi sesihambile kutsi bangafaka lesinye sicelo kulenye indzawo.
tgt: iofisi kazwelonke yokuqwalasela izicelo yavulwa lisebe lemfundo ephakamileyo noqeqesho ukuze incede okwethutyana abafundi abafanelekileyo abaqala kwizinga lemfundo ephakamileyo noqeqesho (ipset) abafuna uncedo ngale miba ilandelayo: abo bafake isicelo sokufunda kwangethuba kwiziko lemfundo abalithandayo saze isicelo sabo asaphumelela ke ngoku sele bedlulelwe lixesha ukuba bangafaka isicelo kwamanye amaziko.

src: bafundzi labangemukelwa bangakafaki sicelo ngoba bangenako loko lokudzingekako kute bafake sicelo sekufundza ngenca yemiphumela yabo lengemihle yelibanga le11 kodvwa kutfolakale kwekutsi imiphumela yabo yelibanga le12 iyabavumela kwekutsi bangangena.
tgt: abo bangakhange bafake zicelo kuba bengawafumenanga la manqaku afunwayo kwibanga 11 ukuze umntu athathwe.

src: abakafaki sicelo kusenesikhatsi ngenca yesizatfu lesitsite noma lesinye noma abakafaki sicelo nje sanhlobo.
tgt: abo bangakhange bafake sicelo ngexesha ngenxa yezizathu ezahlukeneyo okanye khange bafake sicelo kwaphela.

src: abati kwekutsi bafuna kufundzela ini nabacedza matekuletjeni.
tgt: aba bangayaziyo ukuba baza kufundela eliphi ikhondo.

src: bayati kutsi bafuna kufundzela ini kodvwa abanasiciniseko sekutsi loku labakhetse kukufundzela kungumsebenti lolungile yini.
tgt: abo bayaziyo into abayifundelayo qha bengaqinisekanga ukuba eli khondo balithandayo libalungele na.

src: tinsita letiniketwa yicach ticelo tematfuba ekufundza leticondziswe kupset (emanyuvesi, emanyuvesi etheknoloji, ematheknikhali nemakolishi ekufundzela umsebenti nemkhakha wetemfundvo nemitimba yekucecesha.
tgt: iinkonzo ezinikezelwa yicach izicelo zokufuna indawo zokufunda kwizinga lepset (iidyunivesiti, iidyunivesiti zezobuchwepheshe, iikholeji zemfundo noqeqesho lobugcisa nobuchule (iitvet) kunye namaqumrhu amacandelo emfundo noqeqesho (iiseta) ulwazi ngeendawo ezinceda ngemali yokufunda (inkcukacha ngensfas) iinkonzo zengcebiso ngamakhondo (iingcebiso, ulwazi, ukuboniswa nokucetyiswa ngamakhondo/ulwazi ngeendawo ezinceda ngemali yokufunda, kunye neentlobo ezahlukeneyo zemali yokufunda).

src: lwatiso netinsita ngetimali (lwatiso nge nsfas).
tgt: ukuxhasa amagcisa (iziko lesizwe lokuxhasa uphuhliso lwamagcisa).

src: loluhlelo lwecach lucala ngamhla ti3 bhimbidvwane 2018, masinyane ngembi kwekukhishwa kwemiphumela yeluhlolo lwensc, kantsi lutawusebenta kudzimate kuphele inyanga yendlovana nga2018.
tgt: icach ivula ngomhla wesi3 kweyomqungu, isithutyana nje emva kokuba iziphumo zeemviwo zebanga 12 zikhutshiwe kwaye iza kuvula kude kuye ekupheleni kweyomdumba ngowama2018.

src: sigaba sesi2: emaejenti atawushayela lomfundzi lofake sicelo mahhala, batamshayela kulesikhungo sekutsintsana bese babhalisa yonkhe imininingwane ledzingekako eluhlweni lwedatha yecach, kufaka ekhatsi loku umfundzi langatsandza kukufundzela kanye nesifundza langatsandza kufundzela kuso.
tgt: inqanaba 2: umsebenzi wecach uza kumtsalela umnxeba umfundi lowo, kwiziko lemibuzo aze ambhalise kuluhlu lwecach, enika iinkcukacha ngekhondo elikhethwe ngulo mfundi kunye nephondo abafuna ukufunda kulo.

src: sigaba sesi3: imininingwane yonkhe yalona lofake sicelo kanye nemiphumela yamatekuletjeni itawucinisekiswa ibuye idluliselwe kuleso sikhungo semfundvo lephakeme kwentelwe kutfolelwa sikhala nekungeniswa kuleso sikolo uma kuphumeleleka.
tgt: inqanaba 3: iinkcukacha zomfakisicelo kunye neziphumo zakhe zebanga 12 ziyaqinisekiswa zize zizithumele zona ngokwazo kumaziko emfundo ephakamileyo ngeenjongo zokukhangela ukuba umfundi lowo angayifumana na indawo yokufunda futhi athathwe.

src: sigaba sesi4: luhlelo lwecach lutawucinisekisa lolwatiso lwemfundzi bese balutfumela etikhungweni letisolo tinetikhala letivulekile.
tgt: inqanaba 4: icach iza kuqinisekisa iinkcukacha zomfundi ize izithumele kumaziko emfundo asenazo iindawo zokufunda.

src: lapho kusolo kunetikhala khona kantsi bafundzi banako loku lokudzingekako, tikhungo titawushayela labo labafake ticelo ngco.
tgt: amaziko aseneendawo zokufunda kwaye nomfundi lowo enazo ezi zinto zifunwayo, iziko lemfundo elo liza kuqhagamshelana nomfundi ngqo ngokwalo.

src: lekufanele ukwati icach angeke yacinisekisa noma bani lofake sicelo kutsi utasitfola sikhala sekufundza.
tgt: izinto ekufuneka ziqatshelwe icach ayizibopheleli ithi umfakisicelo uza kuyifumana indawo yokufunda.

src: icach angeke yati kwekutsi lesikhungo sitamphendvula nini lona lofake sicelo kute bamtfolele indzawo.

src: kusutsa kuhambisana nekutfola imiphumela lemihle more matshediso bantfwana labange tulu kwetigidzi leti yimfica kulolonkhe laseningizimu afrika laba setikolweni tahulumende sebayakhona kwenta umse benti wabo kancono, sibo nga loluhlelo lwahulumende lolucinisekisa kwekutsi tisu tabo tihlale tisemfi ngekudla lokunemsoco.
tgt: abantwana abahluthiyo baqhuba kakuhle kwizifundo zabo more matshediso abantwana besiko lo abangaphezulu kwizigidi ezisithoba kwizikolo zikarhulumente emzantsi afrika banakho ngoku ukwenza umsebenzi wabo wesikolo.

src: litiko letemfundvo lesise kelo (idbe), ngekusebentisa luhlelo lwavelonkhe lwe tikolo lwekondla (insnp), liyengcile injongo yalo yekunika kudla bantfwana bakuleli labalinganiselwa kumaphesenti lange75.
tgt: oku kwe nzeka ngenxa yenkqubo ka rhulumente eqinisekisa uku ba bafumana ukutya oku nezakhamzimba.

src: lweni onkhe malanga ba ntfwana labalinganiselwa eti9 032 622 velonkhe.
tgt: isebe lemfundo esisise ko (idbe), lisebenzisa inkqubo karhulumente yo kutyis a a bantwana ezikolweni (insnp), lifike legqithisa kwinjongo ebe lizibekele yona yokubone lela ngokutya abantwana besikolo abamalunga nama 75% kweli lizwe.

src: utsite tikolo letingasiyo ince nye yaloluhlelo kufanele kutsi tivakashele emahhovisi asesigodzini sabo uma ngabe tifuna kuba yincenye yalo.
tgt: umlawuli wensnp ese beni, uneo rakwena, uthi izikolo ezingama20 619 ziphekela zize ziphakele abantwana besikolo abazi 9 032 622 ngosuku kulo lonke eli.

src: n gemnyakatimali wa nga2015/16, tigidzi letili nganiselwa kur5 703 tafa kwa kuloluhlelo.
tgt: uthi izikolo ezingaxha mliyo kule nkqubo kufune ka ziye kwiiofisi zesithili ukuba nazo zifuna ukuba yinxalenye yale nkqubo.

src: rakwena utsite lemali lecitfwe kuloluhlelo iyachi tjiyelwa njalo ngemnyaka kute ihambisane nekunyuka kwetintfo, kantsi ibhajethi yanga2017/18 ilinganiselwa kutigidzi letir6.4.
tgt: ngonyakamali wama 2015/16, imali emalunga neebhiliyoni zeerandi ezi yi5 703 yaye yabekelwa bu cala ukulungiselela insnp.

src: loluhlelo lucedza kulamba kwesikhashana kantsi futsi lufaka sandla kunhlalakahle yebantfwana.
tgt: urakwena uthi le mali i c hi th w a ku l e n kqu bo iyongezwa rhoqo ngonya ka kulungiselelwa umba wokunyuka kwamaxabi so ezinto, ke ngoko imali ebekelwe insnp yowa ma2017/18 imalunga nee bhiliyoni eziyi6.4 zeerandi.

src: "bantfwana labanyenti ba vela emakhaya lahluphekile langakhoni kuba nekudla labangakudla, kantsi ku labanye bafundzi, lokudla labakudla esikolweni ngiko kudla labakudlela lilanga lonkhe.
tgt: insnp ilicebo lexesha eli futshane lokugxotha ikati eziko kwaye inegalelo elihle kakhulu kubomi babafundi.

src: kudla labakudla esi kolweni kuyabasita kutsi bakhone kufundza, kulale lisisa nekutimbandzakanya eklasini," washo njalo.
tgt: "abantwana abaninzi ba phuma kumakhaya angatha thi ntweni, angenamali yo kuthenga into esiwa phantsi kwempumlo, kwaye abanye abantwana oku kutya baku fumana esikolweni, yiyo yodwa abayityayo ngosu ku.

src: emanani ebafundzi lababha lisako etikolweni nalabange na sikolo anyukile ngenca yaloluhlelo lwekutfola kudla esikolweni.
tgt: ukutya abakufumana esikolweni kuyabanceda abafundi kwizifundo zabo, bakwazi ukuhlala bemamele bethatha nenxaxheba kwi zifundo zabo," utshilo.

src: kungasikudzala, ikhabhi nethi ivume kushicilelwa kwe mbiko wekulingani swakwensnp lobhalwe litiko letekuhlela, kuca phela kanye nekulungisa (idpme).
tgt: u rakwena wongeze ngelithi amanani abantwana abaya esikolweni enyukile futhi abantwana basiha mba kakuhle isikolo ngenxa yale nkqubo yokutyiswa kwabantwana ezikolweni.

src: uchaza imphume lelo netinyatselo letingatsa tfwa kuphumelelisa lemita mo.
tgt: kwezi ntsukwana zimba lwa zidlulileyo, ikhabhi nethi ivumile ukuba kupapa shwe ingxelo yokuvava nywa kwensnp, ebhalwe lisebe lezokucwangcisa, ukuhlola nokuvavanya (idpme).

src: umcondzisi wekulinganisa kadpme, jabu mathe, utsite injongo lenkhulu yekuli nganisa kwekutsi kuhlolwe kutsi ngabe insnp yenti wa ngalendlela letawuba nemiphumela lekhombisa umehluko lomkhulu kutem philo kantsi kube nenzuzo emfundvweni yebafundzi.
tgt: le ngxelo ichaza izinto eziyimpumelelo eze nziwe yinsnp kunye na manyathelo anokuthathwa ukuphucula indlela esebe nza ngayo.

src: uphindze wagcizelela kwe kutsi injongo yaloluhlelo seyiphelele kwekutsi kwenti we kancono temphilo nesimo sekudla kahle kwebafundzi labaphuye kakhulu eningi zimu afrika.
tgt: umlawuli wezokuhlola kwidpme, ujabu mathe, uthi eyona njongo ipha mbili yokuvavanya insnp ibikukujonga ukuba ingaba isebenza ngendlela eza kwenza umahluko obo nakalayo kwimpilo na kwindlela abaqhuba ngayo abafundi kwizifundo zabo.

src: loluhlelo lu hlose kufinyelela kubo bonkhe bantfwana laba setikolweni tahulumende letisemkhakheni welizi nga lebuphuya 1 kuya ku3, letilinganiselwa kumaphe senti la60 etikolweni leti phuye kakhulu eningizimu afrika.
tgt: ukubethelele ukuba eyo na njongo ingundoqo ye nsnp kukuphucula impilo yabafundi abaphuma ku makhaya asokolayo kunye nokuqinikisa ukuba imizi mba yabo yomelele ngenxa yezakhamzimba abazifu mana ekutyeni.

src: yolisa uphotsa indlela yakhe leya emphumelelweni dale hes lutsandvo lwebuciko luholele fuma kutsi asungule ibhizinisi lephumelelako.
tgt: uyolisa uphila ngokuthengisa izinto ezihonjiswe ngeentsimbi dale hes ukuthanda imisebenzi yobugcisa kuncede ufuma waziqalela ishishini eliqhuba kakuhle kakhulu.

src: yolisa fuma uhambe luhambo loluma ngalisako kusu kela ekuphileni imphilo yebuphuya emphuma langa kapa, kuya lapho afinyelela kutfola kho na lutsandvo lolukhu lu lwebuc iko nem s e benti wetandla kantsi nya lo ubamba imihlangano sikolwa lapho ashiyelana khona ngemakhono akhe nalabanye bomake labanga sebenti.
tgt: uyolisa fuma usu ka kude kakhulu.

src: fuma watalelwa elokishini ngephandle equeenstown emphumalanga kapa, lapho bebahlala endlini lencane nemalunga la15 emndeni wakhe.

tgt: njengoko iyinyanga ye zokhenketho, eli qela sele libambe imisitho emibini eyinxalenye yamalungise lelo, entenda futhi ephekela amalungu ecandelo lezokhe nketho ebetyelele apha.

src: kudlala ngemagagasi kususa bantfwana emgwaceni vuyo ndlovu kuntjweza emantini akusiwo umdlalo noma indlela yeku tijabulisa kulusha loluhlala emkhatsini kwelidolobha kati lasedurban kwazu lunatal kodvwa kuyindle la yekubalekela kuganga.
tgt: amaza asusa abantwana ezitalatweni vuyo ndlovu isurfing, okanye ukutyibiliza phezu kwamaza, ayilohlobo lomdlalo okanye into nje yokuzonwabisa yabantu abatsha abahlala embindi ni wesixeko sasedurban kwiphondo lakwazuluna tal koko ikwaluhlobo lomdla lo apho umntu angakwazi ukupholisa ingqondo.

src: isurfers not street chi ldren yinhlangano lebo nelela kuphakelwa kweti fundvo tekuntjweza tama hhala ebantfwaneni labahla la emigwaceni nelusha le libondzinga sitsebeni leli tfolakala emkhatsini kwale lidolobhakati.
tgt: isurfers not street chi ldren ngumbutho oqeqe sha simahla abantwana basezitalatweni kunye na bantu abatsha abangathathi ntweni abahlala kumbindi wesixeko ngezakhono zo kutyibiliza phezu kwamaza.

src: lenhlangano ibukene ngco nekulwa nekuswelakala kwemakhaya ebantfwaneni futsi icinisekisa kutsi lusha lwenta lokutsite lokwakha ko ngetimphilo talo.
tgt: lo mbutho usabela kanye kwikhwelo elahlatywayo lokuliwa kwengxaki ya bantwana abangenama khaya kwaye uqinisekisa ukuba abantu abatsha be nza izinto ezakhayo ngobo mi babo.

src: masipala wasethekwini madvute nje ucedza kwese kela lenhlangano ngekuni kela ngemabhodi eku ntjweza lali10.
tgt: umasipala wasethekwini uxhase lo mbutho kutsha nje ngokuwuliza ngeebhodi ezili10 zokwenza isurfing.

src: lamabhodi entelwe ku tsi asebente kutfutfukisa tekuntjweza futsi entiwe ngeligwebu lelenta ku tsi labo labasafundza ku ntjweza bandande emantini bangangcwili.
tgt: ezi bhodi zenzelwe uku phuhlisa kwaye zenziwe ngento engathi yirabha ence da abo basafunda ukwenza isurfing ukuba bangatshoni.

src: umphatsi walomasipa la welitiko lekutfutfukisa temidlalo nekukhibika te ddi adams watsi lamabhodi atawusita labo labanesifiso sekuntjweza.
tgt: umlawuli wesebe likama sipala lezemidlalo nolo nwabo uteddi adams uthi ezi bhodi ziza kunceda abo bafuna ukuba ngabantu abenza isurfing.

src: "lomnikelo uyincenye yendlelamasu yamasipa la yekutfutfukisa temi dlalo nekucinisekisa ku tsi lonkhe lusha, ngapha ndle kwekubuka buhla nga nelizinga letenhla lo, luyafinyelela kutinsi ta ngalokulinganako kute lusitakale lwente kancono kuluhlobo lwemdlalo lelu wutsandzako.
tgt: "esi sipho siyinxalenye yezicwangciso zikamasi pala zokuphuhlisa ezemi dlalo nokuqinisekisa ukuba abantu abatsha, kungajo ngwanga bala labo nakufu ma kweepokotho zamakha ya abaphumo kuwo, banazo izixhobo eziza kubanceda ukuba bagqame kuhlobo lomdlalo abawukhethileyo.

src: "langelihle nkosi (lone minyaka yebudzala le16) lomntjwezi ubonge lomasi pala ngalomnikelo.
tgt: ulangelihle nkosi (one minyaka yobudala eli16) ongomnye wabo benza isurfing ubulela umasipala ngesipho asenzileyo.

src: "kuyangitfokotisa kuta kutifundvo tekuntjweza ngoba tiyangincedza ku gcina umtimba wami usesimeni lesikahle fu tsi ngiyatsandza kudlala ngemagagasi."
tgt: "ndiyakuthanda ukuza kufunda isurfing kuba inde nza ukuba ndomelele futhi ndiyakuthanda ukutyibiliza phezu kwamaza."

src: nkosi wa gcugcutela labanye laba nesifiso sekuntjweza kutsi bete babeyincenye bafundze kabanti ngekuntjweza.
tgt: unkosi uyabakhuthaza abo ban qwenela ukwenza isurfi ng ukuba baze kuthatha inxaxheba bafunde banzi ngayo.

src: sandile mqadi umceceshi wesurfers not street chi ldren club, watsi lenhla ngano beyihlose kufu ndzisa bantfwana emakho no ekuntjweza njengendle la yekubasusa emgwaceni.
tgt: usandile mqadi, ongumqe qeshi wesurfing esurfers not street children club, uthi iinjongo zalo mbutho kukufundisa abantwana isurfing into leyo eza kuba nceda ukuba bangahlali ezi talatweni.

src: "sisita bantfwana la bahlala emigwaceni nala bo lababuya kumimango lephuyile.
tgt: "sisebenza nabantwa na abahlala ezitalatweni kunye nabo baphuma ku makhaya asokolayo.

src: tinsita tetfu atikhokhelwa kantsi futsi samukela bantfu labasha labaneminyaka yebudzala lesuka kulesihlanu kuya ku lenge23," kwasho mqadi.
tgt: unce do esilunikayo lusimahla kwaye sinceda abantu aba tsha abaneminyaka yobu dala ephakathi kwemihlanu nengama23," utsho umqa di.

src: wangeta ngekutsi lama bhodi masipala lanikele ngawo atawusita imitamo yabo futsi bantfwana la baningi batawukhona kuba yincenye yaloluhlelo.
tgt: wongeze wathi ezi bhodi umasipala alize ngazo ziza kunceda kumalinge abo kwaye abantwana abani nzi baza kukwazi ukuthatha inxaxheba kule nkqubo.

src: isurfers not street chi ldren club yetfula tifu ndvo tekuntjweza kusu ka ngemsombuluko kuya kulesihlanu ngensimbi ye08h30 kanye neye13h30.
tgt: isurfers not street chi ldren club iqhuba uqeqesho lokwenza isurfing uku suka ngomvulo ukuya ngolwesihlanu ngo08h30 nango13h30.

src: litiko letemphilo elimpopo libeka kumunyisa ezingeni lelisha lekungaze kufikwe kulo kanego lewele namore matshediso kumunyisa kumco ka ekukhuleni lokunemphilo kwemntfwana nasekudleni kwetinswane kodvwa bo make labaningi labasebe ntako batfola bumatima ku chubeka nalenchubo emva kwekuphela kwelivi se babuyela emsebentini.
tgt: isebe lezempilo laselimpopo ligxi ninisa ukubaluleka kokuncancisa kanego lewele no more matshediso ukuncancisa ku luncedo kakhulu kwimpilo yomntwa na futhi kuzigcina iintsana zondlekile kodwa oomama abaninzi abaphangelayo ba banobunzima ngokuncanci sa xa bebuyela emisebenzini emva kwekhefu lasemva kokubeleka.

src: loku kubangwa kutsi kute tindzawo letikahle eti ndzaweni letiningi bomake labanentinswane labasebe ntela kuto lapho bangakha ma lubisi noma bamunyise bantfwana babo ngesikhatsi semsebenti, kubenta balahle kelwe sifiso sekuchubeka bamunyise ngenca yekutsi bacitsa sikhatsi lesinyenti basemsebentini bantfwana bangekho nabo.
tgt: oku kubangelwa kuku ba kungekho zindawo zi fanelekileyo emisebenzini zokuba abadlezana banca ncise iintsana zabo okanye bakhame ubisi, baze bangabi namdla wokuqhubeleka be ncancisa kuba bachitha ixe sha labo elininzi emisebe nzini iintsana zabo zingekho.

src: kumtamo wetfu wekubuka na nalenseyeya, litiko le temphilo laselimpopo li sungule ligumbi lelilekuca la lekumunyisa nekukhama lubisi emahhovisini alo.
tgt: ngelinge lokuzama uku lungisa le ngxaki, isebe lezempilo laselimpopo livule kwiiofisi zalo iziko lokuqala ngqa lokuncancisa nokukhama ubisi.

src: leligumbi lekumunyisa le tfulwe ngumphatsiswatiko dkt.
tgt: eli ziko lokuncancisa livu lwe ngokusesikweni ngu mphathiswa wephondo ugq phophi ramathuba.

src: licanjwe ngeligama lama ke albertina sisulu lesigu bha umkhosi weminyaka le likhulu yekutalwa kwakhe lomnyaka.
tgt: eli ziko lithiywe ngegama likamama albertina sisulu.

src: siyatsemba kutsi leligu mbi angeke lisekele kuphe la bomake labamunyisako, kodvwa litawugcugcutela la manye ematiko kutsi asekele bomake labamunyisako eti ndzaweni labasebentela kuto.
tgt: sinethemba lokuba eli ziko alizikunceda kuphela ooma ma abancancisayo abapha ngelayo koko liza kukhutha za amanye amasebe ukuba abaxhase oomama abanca ncisayo emisebenzini.

src: tisebenti talelitiko tingavu mela bantfu labasala neba ntfwana kutsi baletse ti nswane emsebentini nge tikhatsi tekudla kute timu nyiswe.
tgt: abasebenzi besebe baza ku vumeleka ukuba bacele aba ntu ababonasela abantwa na ukuba bazise abantwa na emisebenzini ngesithuba sesidlo sasemini ukuze ba ncancise.

src: leligumbi linga setjentiswa futsi bomake labafuna kukhama lubisi ngesikhatsi semsebenti.
tgt: eli ziko liza kuse tyenziswa nangabadlezana abafuna ukukhama ubisi besemsebenzini.

src: lomunye wetisebenti talelitiko mpho kutumela longumake wemawele lane tinyanga leti11, umfana nentfombatane, uyalitfokote la leligumbi.
tgt: omnye wabasebenzi bese be umpho kutumela nongu mdlezana onamawele, eli yinkwenkwe neliyintombi, aneenyanga ezili11 ubudala, uvuyiswa kakhulu kukuvu lwa kweli ziko.

src: "leligumbi litasisebe ntela sibomake ngoba li tawuphindza lisinike litfuba lekukhama lubisi ngekukhu luleka endzaweni lelungele loko," washo njalo.
tgt: "eli ziko lokuncancisa liza kusinceda kakhulu thina njengabadlezana kuba siza kukwazi ngoku ukukhama ubisi endaweni efaneleki leyo ngaphandle kokupha zanyiswa," utshilo.

src: bomake labavakashela li tiko nganoma ngabe ngutiphi tizatfu bahamba nebantfwa na babo nabo batawuvunye lwa kusebentisa leligumbi kumunyisa bantfwana.
tgt: oomama abandwendwela isebe bephethe iintsana zabo, nokuba balindwendwele ngantoni isebe, baza ku vunyelwa ukuba bancancise iintsana zabo.

src: umphatsiswatiko ramathu ba watsi ialbertina sisulu breastfeeding room ngiyo yodvwa kuso sonkhe si fundza.
tgt: umphathiswa wephondo uramathuba uthi ialbertina sisulu breastfeeding room iliziko elifana lodwa kweli phondo.

src: umphatsiswasito utsemba kutsi lomkhankhaso uta wugcugcutela kukhula neku vikela tindlela letivulekile tekumunyisa ngenhloso yekuzuza kukhula loku mcoka lokunemphilo e mntfwaneni.
tgt: umphathiswa wephondo unethemba lokuba eli ziko liza kunceda ukuba ooma ma bakwazi ukuncancisela ezindaweni ezikhuselekileyo nezilungiselelwe kanye oku ngeenjongo zokuqinisekisa ukuba baba nabantwana aba khula bondlekile futhi be sempilweni.

src: "lubisi lwelibele lunayo yonkhe imisoco ledzingwa tinswane futsi ayikho lenye indlela lelingentiwa ngayo ngaphandle kwekumunyi sa," kwaso umphatsiswa tiko.
tgt: "ubisi lwebele luneza khamzimba ezifunwa kanye zintsana kwaye lelendalo, soze lenziwe ngoomatshi ni," utshilo umphathiswa wephondo.

src: umphatsiswatiko wetemphilo elimpopo dkt.
tgt: umphathiswa wephondo laselimpopo ugq phophi ramathuba ephahlwe ngoomama abancancisayo abeze kuzimasa lo umsitho wokuvulwa kweziko.

src: kubhalisa umshado wesintfu kuvikela imindeni dale hes eningizimu afrika, imishado yesintfu iyincenye leyamuke lekile kumasiko nemigu bho yesintfu.
tgt: ukubhalisa umtshato wesintu kukhusela iintsapho dale hes emzantsi afrika, imitshato yesintu yamkelekile kwaye ithathwa njengenxalenye yamasiko nenkcubeko.

src: noma kunja lo, kubalulekile kwati kwe kutsi lemishado kufanele iphatfwe ngekulingana nangalokusemtsetfweni, kute kwekutsi lamalunge lo abo bobabili lekuyindvo dza nemfati bavikelekile.
tgt: noko kunjalo kubalulekile ukuba sikuqonde uku ba le mitshato kufuneka iqhutywe ngendlela esemthethweni nefanelekileyo, ukuze kukhuselwe amalungelo endoda na womfazi ngokunjalo.

src: umcondzisi ngetemtsetfo kukhomishana yekulinga na ngekwebulili marissa van niekerk, uchaza imi shado yesintfu netintfo letibalulekile lekufanele bantfu batati.
tgt: umlawuli wezomthetho wekhomishini elwelwa ulingwano ngokobuni umarissa van niekerk, ucacisa ngemitshato yesintu kunye nezinye izinto ezibalulekileyo ngawo.

src: vuk: iyini imishado yesi ntfu?
tgt: vuk: yintoni imitshato yesintu?

src: mvn: imishado yesintfu yenti wa ngekusebentisa emasiko nemihambo lehlonishwako kubantfu baseningizimu afrika.
tgt: mvn: imitshato yesintu iqhutywa ngokwamasiko nezithe the zentlanga ezahlukeneyo zomzantsi afrika.

src: vuk: nguyiphi imitsetfo leku fanele lemishado ihambisane nayo?
tgt: vuk: ingaba le mitshato ku funeka iqhutywe ngokweyiphi imithetho?

src: mvn: imishado yesi ntfu ilawulwa ngemtsetfo wekunakwa kwemishado yesintfu, 120 wanga1998.
tgt: mvn: imitshato yesintu iphantsi komthetho wokuhlonitshwa kwemitshato yesintu wowe1998 (umthetho unombolo 120 wowe1998).

src: letidzingo letilandzelako kufanele kufinyelelwe kuto: ■ emacala omabili kufanele avume kutsi ayashada.
tgt: kufuneka iqhutywe ngokwale migaqo ilandelayo: ■ abatshati bobabini kufune ka bavumelana ukuba baza kutshatana.

src: ■ labalingani bobabili ku fanele babe ngetulu kwe minyaka le18, ngaphandle kwekutsi labatali noma bondli ngalokusemtse tfweni baniketa imvume uma ngabe munye noma bobabili bangebantfwana.
tgt: ■ abatshati bobabini kufune ka babe neminyaka yobu dala engaphezulu kweli18, ngaphandle kokuba aba zali okanye abagcini babo abasemthethweni ngabo ababakhululelayo, ukuba omnye wabatshati uselula.

src: ■ lomshado kufanele ubha liswe kulitiko letase khaya kungakapheli tinyanga letintsatfu kute kuvikelwe tinshisekelo tebalingani, bantfwana nemndeni uma kwentekile kwaba nekudivosa neku fa.
tgt: ■ lo mtshato kufuneka ubha liswe kwisebe lemicimbi yezekhaya zingaphelanga iinyanga ezintathu ukuze kukhuselwe abatshati, abantwana kunye namalungu osapho xa kunokwenzeka lo mtshato uqhawulwe okanye kubekho oswelekayo.

src: ■ uma ngabe ubhalisa lo mshado, umlingani ku fanele aletse emakhophi amatisi wakhe nesivume lwano semalobolo (uma sikhona).
tgt: ■ xa kubhaliswa lo mtshato, abatshati kufuneka baphathe iincwadizasizi zabo kunye nesivumelwano selobola (ukuba sikhona).

src: lokungenani kufanele kube nafakazi munye lovela emndenini ngamunye.
tgt: kufuneka kubekho ingqina nokuba linye elikhoyo eliphuma kwikhaya ngalinye.

src: ■ indvodza lefuna kushada umshado wesintfu wesibi li nalomunye umfati ku fanele ibhalele enkhantolo ifake sicelo.
tgt: ■ indoda efuna ukutshata umfazi wesibini ngokwesi ntu kufuneka ifake isicelo enkundleni.

src: ■ bantfu labayincenye ye mshado wesilungu angeke bashade umshado wesi ntfu.
tgt: ■ abantu abatshate umtshato wesilungu abavumelekanga ukutshata isintu.

src: lomtsetfo wekunaka u mshado wesintfu ubeka kwe kutsi bobabili laba labasha dile banemalungelo lafanako njengendvodza nemfati.
tgt: umthetho wokuhlonitshwa kwemitshato yesintu uthi boba bini abatshati kolu hlobo lomtshato banamalungelo afa nayo njengendoda nomfazi.

src: vuk: ngutiphi tinkinga leti ngaba khona emshadweni wesintfu?
tgt: vuk: ingaba zeziphi iingxaki ezinokulindeleka emtshatweni wesintu?

src: mvn: kungabhaliswa kuba nga tinkhinga letinkhulu.
tgt: mvn: ukungawubhalisi umtshato kungenza iingxa ki ezinkulu.

src: kubhaliswa kuniketa bufa kazi bekutsi lomshado ukho na, kucinisekisa kwekutsi umshado longakabhaliswa ukhona kulukhuni.
tgt: ukuwubhalisa kwenza ukuba abatshati babe nobungqina bokuba umtshato ukhona ngenene, kuba kunzima kakhulu ukuqinisekisa ukuba umtshato ongabhaliswanga ukhona ngenene.

src: loku ku tawuba nemtselela emandleni enkhantolo ekukhona ku vikela balingani nabadivosa, kuhlomula kulifa laloshonile kanye nemalungelo ebantfwa na nemalunga emndeni.
tgt: oku kwenza kube nzima nakwiinkundla zomthetho ukuba zikhusele amalungulo abatshati xa kuthe kwakho uqhawulomtshato, xa kuchotshelwe imiba yelifa lomntu oswelekileyo kunye namalungelo abantwana kunye namalungu osapho.

src: lolunye ludzaba lolubalule kile emshwadweni wesintfu kwekutsi ebalingani abakuvi sisi kudivosa nekwehlukana.
tgt: enye into edla ngokubange la ingxaki phakathi kwabatshati kukungahluli phakathi koqhawulomtshato nokwa hlukana.

src: hulumende welekelela emakhaya dale hes ngenca yekwenyuka kwentsengo yeku dla netintfo tase khaya hulumende usebe nta ngekutikhandla kwe hlisa lomtfwalo wetimali lobekwe emahlombe eba ntfu baseningizimu afri ka ngenca yekungatsa tfwa kwentsela yeku dla lokutsite.
tgt: urhulumente unceda amakhaya dale hes njengoko amaxabi so ezinto enyuka urhulumente wenza konke anakho ukuphungula umthwalo ohleli emagxeni abantu abaninzi bomzantsi afrika ngokuthi ezinye izinto ezithe ngwayo zingafakwa irhafuntengo (ivat).

src: kugatsatselwa intsela kuhlo se kwe lekele la emakha ya lanemholo lo mncane, bese aci tsa incenye lenkhulu yemali lebayiholako eti ntfweni tasekhaya.
tgt: iinjongo zokungafaki ivat kukuphungulela umthwalo amakhaya amkela imivuzo ephantsi, wona achitha isixa esikhulu semivuzo yawo kwizinto zasekhaya.

src: tintfo letingatsatselwa i ntsela atifakelwa i15% yentsela ntsengo (ivat).
tgt: izinto ezingafakwa irha fu azibhataliswa irhafuntengo eyi15%.

src: loku ku hloswe kusi ta ba ntfu ba seni ngizimu afrika kutsi bonge i mali.
tgt: injongo yoku kukunceda abemi bomzantsi afrika ukuba bonge imali.

src: kunetinhlo bo teku dla lokuba lulekile leti19 leti ngafake lwa ivat letifaka ekha tsi loku: u mbila, sitambu, lilayisi, sinkhwa lesimnyama, ti tselo, tibhidvo, ti nhlanti nemacandza.
tgt: ezi ntlobo zokutya zinge navat zili19 ziquka: umbo na, umngqusho, irayi si, isonka esimdaka, iziqhamo, imifuno, intlanzi esetotini, amaqanda.

src: kwengeta, tintfo letifa na nedizili, phethiloli napharafini, kanye na letinye tinsita letifaka ekha tsi kucashwa kwendzawo yekuhlala, sitimela neteku tfutsa tasemgwacweni neti nsita tekufundza, nato ange ke tiyikhokhe ivat.
tgt: ezinye izinto ezingabhataliswa ivat ziquka idzi li, ipetro li kunye neparaf ini kwakunye neenkonzo ezithile ezifana nemali yerenti, imali yokukh wela uloliwe nezinye izithuthi kunye nemali yokufunda.

src: ngenyanga yendlova na hulumende umemetele kwekutsi utawukhuphu la ivat kusukela ku14% kuya ku15%.
tgt: ngenyanga yomdumba urhu lumente wabhengeza ukuba uza kuyinyusa ivat isuke kwi14% iye kwi15%.

src: hulumende ubuye wabona kwekut si emakhaya laphuyile atawucindzeteleka kakhulu ngetimali.
tgt: urhulumente waqonda ukuba oku kuza ku wafaka ezingxakini zezimali amakhaya asokolayo.

src: kwehlisa lokwenyu ka kwemazinga ekuphi la, ndvuna wetimali nhlanhla nene ucoke litsimba lelitawukhi pha tiphakamiso kwe kutsi ngutiphi letinye tintfo tasekhaya leti ngangetwa kuleti leti ngatsatselwa intsela.
tgt: ukuphungula umthwalo weengxaki obangwa ngamaxabiso ezinto aphezulu umphathiswa wezemali unhlanhla nene watyumba iqela eliza kucebisa ngezinye izinto zase khaya ezinokongezwa kuluhlu lwezo zingabhataliswa ivat.

src: ngekuva kwelucwaningo lolubanti nekutsintsana ne bantfu, lelitsimba lancoma kwekutsi letinye tintfo tifa kwe kuloluhla.
tgt: emva kokuba eli qela liqhu be uphando olunzulu labamba neendibano zokubonisana noluntu, liye lacebisa ukuba kongezwe ezinye izinto ezise tyenziswa emakhaya kuluhlu lwezo zingafakwa vat.

src: sithibe uphila imphilo yakhe lencono njengomuntfu lonealbinism galoome shopane lerato sithibe uyintfo mbatane lenealbinism.
tgt: usithibe uphila kamnandi ngoku anealbinism galoome shopane ulerato uligqiyazana elinealbinism .

src: uyatigcabha ngekuba nalo mba la esikhu njeni sa khe futsi akavume li tinkho lelo leti ngasiliciniso kutsi timtsi kamete.
tgt: uyazidla ngeli bala lim hlophe kuye futhi akazihluphi ngabo bathetha izinto ezimbi phofu ezingeyonyani ngalo.

src: "kubalule kile kubantfu labafana na mi kutsi banga vumi kutsi labanye ba chaze kutsi babobani.
tgt: "kubalulekile ebantwini abafa na nam ukuba singabamameli abanye abantu abacinga ukuba bayasazi kodwa bengasazi.

src: ti gcabhe ngekuba nealbinism ngoba wakheke waba mu hle," asho alandzisa.
tgt: "mu sa ukumamela abanye abantu ukuba bathini ngawe, udalwe wafana wedwa," utshilo.

src: sithibe (loneminyaka lenge28) lohlala ekroonstad esifundzeni sasefreyistata, uchaza kwekutsi simo sakhe sihamba emndenini lapho khona umuntfu wakhona uba nemelanin lenganele le menta abe mhlophe esikhu njeni sakhe, etinweleni noma emehlweni.
tgt: usithibe (oneminyaka yobu dala engama28) wasekroon stad efreyistata ucacisa athi eli bala limhlophe kuye liyimfuza.

src: "asisiwo umutsi noma bantfu labafana netilwane letingatiwa kutsi tivelaphi njengoba bantfu bacabanga.

src: ungunobuhle lobuye asebentise timphahla tekugcoka tesimanje kwatisa nekucwayisa ngebantfu la banealbinism kantsi ubuye amelele bantfu labaphila nekukhubateka efreyistata.
tgt: ungunobuhle ose benzisa iimpahla ukufundisa ngealbinism kwaye uphambili kumaphulo okulwela abantu abakhubazekileyo efreyistatha.

src: utsi ukhulele emndenini lonelutsandvo longazange umente ative anemehluko noma angatsandvwa kahle ngoba amhlophe esikhu njeni.
tgt: uthi wakhula kwikhaya elishushu nelinothando apho enga zange azive ukuba ungumntwa na owahlukileyo kwabanye ngenxa yokuba enealbinism .

src: "bengingavisisi kwekutsi kungani umbala wesikhu mba sami wehlukile kunala banye bantfu, kungani njalo uma ngiphumela ngapha ndle bantfu bangibite nge magama futsi bangibuke njengesihambi.
tgt: "ndandingazi ukuba kutheni ibala lesikhumba sam lahlukile kwelabanye abantu, ndingasazi nesizathu sokuba xa ndihamba ngaphandle abantu bendibiza ngamagama amabi futhi ufike abanye bendithe ntsho ngokungathi ndingumntu olahlekileyo.

src: "lokwecwaswa lokubekwa kubantfu labanealbinism kwenta sithibe awubonge kakhulu umndeni wa khe, awunikete ludvumo ngalokuba ngumfati lotime le nalocinile lelekanguye namuhla.
tgt: "indlela ebonwa ngayo ngabantu ialbinism yamenza usithibe wayibona indlela abantu bakowabo ababaluleke ngayo kuye, futhi elibulela negalelo labo ekumenzeni eli nenekazi lingenaxhala futhi lingoyiki bani alilo namhlanje.

src: letinye tintfo laphumelele kuto sithibe nalekatigcabha ngato tifaka ekhatsi kutsi aniketwe umchele wekuba ngumiss free state albi nism 2018 nekutsi akhetfwe njengalomunye walabase maphetselweni kula bayiface of free state fashi on week 2018. njengoba inyoni kuyi nyanga yekwatisa ngealbi nism, sithibe utsi utawujabu la kubona bantfu labanyenti labanealbinism bativeta kantsi benta tintfo letinhle kulomkhakha wabonobuhle naleminye imikhakha.
tgt: ezinye zezinto angasoze azili bale ebomini bakhe usithibe ziquka ukuwongwa ngokuba ngumiss free state albinism ngowama2018 kunye nokukhethwa njengomnye unobuhle ufikelele kumjikelo wokugqibe la wokuba ngunobuhle onguno zakuzaku wombonisozimpahla, iface of free state fashion week yowama2018.

src: sithibe uphila imphilo yakhe lenco no njengomuntfu lonealbinism ngabe bantfu labanealbinism bangatinakekela njani?
tgt: njengokuba eyomsintsi iyinyanga yokufundisa ngealbinism usithibe uthi angavuya kakhulu ukuba angabona abanye abantu abanealbinism bethatha inxa xheba kwicandelo loonobuhle nakumanye amacandelo.

src: konkhe lodzinga ku kwati ngekucala ib&b dale hes ngabe ufuna kunge nisa imali ngekutsi unikete tivakashi indzawo yekulala, ubanikete indzawo labangahlala kuyo kamnandzi ngalesikhatsi ba vakashile endzaweni yanga kini?
tgt: iinkcukacha ezibalulekileyo ngokuqala ib&b dale hes ingaba ufuna ukuzenze la imali ngokunika abakhenkethi iindawo zokulala, ubenze bangabulibali ubububele kunye nendlela abe behleli ngayo kamnandi ngethuba betyelele kwingingqi yenu?

src: mabed and breakfast (mab&b) atindlela letine nzuzo ngekutsi ube nguso mabhizinisi kumboni ye tekuvakasha.
tgt: ukuqalisa ishishini lebed and breakfast (ib&b) yenye yendlela ezingcono kakhulu yokuziqalela ishishini kwicandelo lezokhenketho.

src: naku konkhe lodzinga kukwati ngekucala b&b yakho.
tgt: nazi iinkcukacha ekufuneka uzazi malunga nokuziqalela ib&b.

src: iyini ib&b?
tgt: yintoni ib&b?

src: ngekusho kwetourism grading council of south africa, emab&b mabhizinsi lanendzawo yekulala leneti nsita letifanako naletiniketwa emakhaya.
tgt: ngokwebhunga lokuhlela lezokhenketho lomzantsi afrika, ib&b yindawo yoku lala engenabucukubhede buninzi efanayo nje nalo naliphi na ikhaya.

src: likamelo ngalinye kufanele libe nendlu yekugezela, kantsi sidlo sasekuseni kufanele sibe khona kulamanani ekulala.
tgt: igumbi ngalinye kufuneka libe nendlu yalo yangasese, kwaye imali yesidlo sakusasa kufuneka iqukwe kule yokula la.

src: kungeta kuloko, kuniketa tinsita kulelikamelo kufanele kwenteke onkhe malanga ngalesikhatsi tivakashi titahle li.
tgt: ukongeza, igumbi kufuneka licocwe yonke imihla xa kukho indwendwe elihlala kulo.

src: ib&b ivumele kutsi ibe namakamelo etivakashi la matsatfu kuphela.
tgt: iindlu eyenziwe ib&b inganamagumbi amathathu kuphela ubukhulu.

src: uma ngabe linemakelo langetulu kunalo ku, ngakoke indzawo yakho kufanele kutsi ibitwe ngekutsi yiguest house.
tgt: ukuba le ndlu inamagumbi angaphezu lu kwamathathu, ayiseyob&b kufuneka ibizwe ngokuba iyiguest house .

src: ngutiphi tinchubo lekufanele utilandzele kute ucale libhizinisi yeb&b?
tgt: ngawaphi amanqanaba alandelwayo xa kuvulwa ib&b?

src: sinyatselo sekucala lekufanele usitsatse kutsi uye kuma sipala wendzawo uyafaka sicelo sekuniketwa imvume yekusebentisa indzawo yakho njengebhizinisi leninendzawo yekulala.
tgt: inqanaba lokuqala kukuya kumasipala wakho uye kufaka isicelo sokunikwa ilungelo lokuguqula indlu yakho ibe lishishini lokulalisa nokuntenda iindwendwe.

src: ungahle udzinge imvume kubomakhelwane wakho, bese ukhangisa tatiso kwatisa bantfu, uma ngabe bafuna kuphawula kulesicelo sakho.
tgt: kungafune ka ukuba ufumane nemvume kubamelwane bakho, uze uxhome nezaziso zokwazisa abantu ngokubanzi, ukwenzela abo banokuwukhaba lo mbono wakho.

src: uma ngabe utfola imvume kumasipala, kungadzingeka kwekutsi uhambisane na letinye tidzingo temtsetfo.
tgt: xa sele uyifumene imvume kumasipala, kuza kufuneka ukuba wanezise nezinye izinto ezifunekayo ngokomthetho.

src: tintfo letibalulekiie lekufanele utinakeindzawo – indzawo lapho ku tfolakala khona ib&b yakho ibaluleke kakhulu.
tgt: izinto ezibalulekileyo ekufuneka uziqwalaseleindawo – indawo ekuyo ib&b yakho ibaluleke kakhulu.

src: uma ngabe uhlala endzaweni lengahehi tivakashi, ngakoke kutawuba lukhuni kwenta kutsi ibhizinisi yakho iphumelele.
tgt: ukuba uhlala kwindawo engathandwa kakhulu ngabakhenkethi kuza kubanzima kakhulu ukuba ishishini lakho liqhube kakuhle.

src: timali – tekuvakasha tiba khona ngetikhatsi letitsite, nga koke kutawudzingeka kutsi wonge kakhulu kute uchubeke usebente ngetikhatsi letingasi matasatasa ekhatsi nemnyaka.
tgt: izimali – ishishini lezokhenketho lihamba ngokwamaxe sha onyaka, ke ngoko kufu neka ube nemali oyibekileyo eza kuqhuba ngala maxesha onyaka anqatyelwe ngabakhenkethi.

src: kuphila imphilo lensha – imphi lo loyiphilako itawuntjintja nga lokuphelele uma ngabe uba ngumnikati web&b.
tgt: ubomi obutsha – ubomi bakho buza kutshintsha kakhulu xa ungumntu oneb&b.

src: kutawu hlala kudzingeka kwekutsi uhlala uvuka ekuseni uyolala ebusuku, kantsi kutawufuna wente tingucuko ngenca yeti vakashi letitawuta ekhaya la kho.
tgt: amaxesha amaninzi kuza kufuneka uvuke ngonyezi futhi ngamanye ulale ebusuku, kwaye kufuneka uyiqhele into yokuba uza kuba nabanye abantu aba zindwendwe abaza kusebenzisa eli khaya lakho.

src: kantsi kutawufanele ku tsi wente siciniseko sekuhlala ulungisa ugcine netivakashi takho tinelisekile ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi.
tgt: kwaye kufu neka uqinisekise ukuba indlu yakho ihlala isemgangathweni futhi icocekile ukwenzela ukuba iindwendwe zakho zaneliseke ngalo lonke ixesha.

src: kukhangisa ib&b yakho – timboni tetindzawo tekulala tiyancintisana, ngakoke kutawudzingeka kutsi usise sikhatsi sakho nemali ekukhangiseni ib&b.
tgt: ukwazisa ngeb&b yakho – icandelo lokulalisa nokuntenda iindwendwe linamashishini amaninzi kakhulu, ke ngoko kufuneka uzinike ixesha futhi ube nayo nemali yokwazisa nokuthengisa ib&b yakho.

src: emadvodza emadvo dzeni: yiba yindvo dza, mfana wami vukuzenzele unnamed ngesikhatsi *tshepo mofokeng aneminya ka le10 budzala, uphile ati kutsi dzadzewabo lomdzala loneminyaka le17 wadlwengulwa.
tgt: njengendoda yoqobo, ndithi nawe ube yindoda emadodeni, nyana vukuzenzele unnamed ngela xesha *utshepo mofokeng waye neminyaka eli10, wahlala engcungcuthekiswa ngaphakathi yintlungu yoku dlwengulwa kukadade wabo ominyaka ili17 ubudala.

src: ngesikhatsi lomhlaseli wadzadzewabo labehlomile atjela tshepo kutsi alale phasi angabukeli, usakuva nanyalo kukhala kwadzadzewabo.
tgt: ngethuba umhlaseli oxhobileyo eyalela le nkwenkwana ukuba mayilale phantsi ingajongi, usa liva nanamhlanje ilizwi lesikhalo sikadade wabo ezindlebeni zakhe.

src: ngemuva kwalokuhlasela, lendvodza yatjela letela mani kutsi tibaleke tingabuki emuva.
tgt: emva kolu hlaselo, le ndoda yamyalela yena nodade wabo ukuba babaleke bangabheki ngasemva.

src: ngesikhatsi babaleka kabuhlungu baya ekhaya, dzadzewabo wamtjela kutsi akatsembise kutsi ngeke atjele muntfu ngalokudlwengulwa kwakhe.
tgt: ngeli xesha begoduka kubuhlungu kunjalo, udade wabo wamcela ukuba athembise ukuba akasokuze axelele namnye umntu ngolu dlwengulo.

src: tshepo wakugcina esifubeni loko kodvwa lemfihlo yamenta wahlala njalo amunyu emoyeni.
tgt: utshepo wasigcina isithembiso sakhe kodwa eli hlebo lamenza waba krakra kakhulu umphefu mlo wakhe.

src: "ngesikhatsi ngikhula, bengimbona lomdlwenguli ahambahamba khona lapha ekatlehong kantsi loko kwangenta ngatfukutsela kakhulu.
tgt: "ngeli xesha ndikhula, ndandi mana ndimbona lo mdlwenguli apha ekatlehong lo nto yandenza ndakhulelwa ngumsindo ngakumbi nangakumbi.

src: angizange ngikwemukele kutsi akazange atjeziswa ngalesento sakhe.
tgt: azange ndikwazi ukuyamkela into yoku ba angafumani sohlwayo ngoko wakwenzayo.

src: "ngesikhatsi sekamdzala, se kalibhungu leselicinile, tshepo akazange akhone kubamba lulaka lwakhe, bekamhlasela njalo lomuntfu lowadlwe ngula dzadzewabo nakatfuke wambona.
tgt: "utshepo uthe xa eyinkwe nkwana efikisayo nekhula amandla akakwazi ukuyilawula ingqumbo yakhe, waza wamana ukumhlasela umdlwenguli ka dade wabo nanini na xa embona.

src: wantjintja ekubeni ngumntfwana lonekuthula waba ngumfanyana lohlala atfutkutsele.
tgt: wasuka ekubeni yinkwenkwana engenankathazo wayidyongwana esoloko ilugcwabevu ngumsindo.

src: timbili tintfo letasindzisa tshepo kulendlela yakhe yebudlova.
tgt: zaba mbini izinto ezasindisa utshepo kobu bundlongondlo ngo.

src: kwekucala, bekabu sisekile kutsi abe nababe kanye nemnakabo lomdzala labebati kutsi budlova abusilo likhambi nanome kodvwa bebangati kutsi kubangelwa yini kutsi tshepo atiphatse ngalendlela, bakhona kumeluleka bambuyisela endleleni lecondzile.
tgt: okokuqala, wayenethamsa nqa lokuba notata nomkhuluwa ababesazi ukuba ubundlongo ndlongo abusiso isisombululo nangona babengayazi intsusa yabo apha kutshepo, kodwa ba kwazi ukumkhokelela kwindlela ethe tse neyakhayo.

src: kwesibili kungenelela kwemaphoyisa kajantji lelabona ngesikhatsi tshepo ahlasela kwekugcina umdlwenguli wadzadzewabo.
tgt: okwesibini okumsindisileyo kukungene lela kwamapolisa akwaloliwe ambonayo utshepo ehlasela umdlwenguli kadade wabo.

src: lomdlwenguli wasala aphuke umlente kodvwa ngesikhatsi tshepo achazela emaphoyisa kajantji kutsi lomuntfu wentani yonkhe leminyaka leyandlu la, ancuma kutsi alikhulule lelibhungu ngekulecwayisa.
tgt: lo mdlwenguli washiyeka ophuke umlenze kodwa emva kokuba utshepo ewacacisele yonke into eyayenzwe yile ndoda kwiminya ka eyadlulayo, amapolisa akwa loliwe alikhulula eli tyendyana ngokulityityimbisela nje umnwe.

src: lomdlwenguli wamikiswa esi bhedlela kodvwa akazange aye kuyowumangala.
tgt: umdlwenguli wasiwa esibhedlele kwaye akazange afake simangalo.

src: sekuvamile kuhlaselwa kwabomake, nanome kunjalo tshepo bekakhatsatekile kakhu lu.
tgt: noko kunjalo, ukuhlaselwa kwabasetyhini kusahleli kuqhu beka, kwaye utshepo uya exha laba nangakumbi.

src: ngesikhatsi asasengumfu ndzi lapha epretoria technikon, wasita ekusunguleni licembu lekucaphelisa emadvodza ngendzima yawo lekumele kutsi ayidlale emmangweni kantsi nga2004, wabhalisa licembu lemadvodza isouth african men’s action group (isamag) njengenhlangano lengekho ngaphasi kwahulu mende.
tgt: ngethuba engu mfundi epretoria technikon, wancedisa ekusekweni kombu tho wokuvula amadoda amehlo ukuba ayiqonde indima yawo ekuhlaleni waza ngowama2004, wabhalisa umbutho wamadoda obizwa isouth african men's action group (isamag) njengo mbutho ongekho phantsi kuka rhulumente.

src: lamuhla, isamag ineti sebenti leti10 letisebenta ngalokugcwele egauteng, efreystata, enyakatfo nsho nlanga, elimpopo nasempu malanga.
tgt: namhlanje, isamag inabase benzi abali10 abasebenza isigxi na kwaye ineeofisi egauteng, efreyistata, emntla ntshona, elimpopo nasempumalanga.

src: lenhlangano itimisele ngekuletsa luntjintjo kutenhlalo.
tgt: izinikele ekukhuthazeni inguqu kwezentlalo.

src: umlayeto wayo lomcoka utsi ‘emadvodza sibili akabahlu kumeti bomake.’ (real men don’t abuse women) .
tgt: umyalezo wayo ongundoqo uthi ‘amadoda okwenene awaba phathi kakubi abantu basetyhini’ (real men don’t abuse women) .

src: ligama lesingisi lelitsi "real" limele responsible (kuba nemtfwalo), enlightened (kukhanyelwa), archetypal (kuba sibonelo) kanye naloving (kutsandza)," kusho yena njalo tshepo.
tgt: igama elithi ‘real’ sisishunquleli sala magama esingesi: responsi ble (thembekileyo), enlightened (khanyiselwe), archetypal (yiba ngumzekelo) kunye noloving (nokuthanda)," utshilo umo fokeng.

src: "luhlelo lwekubeka laba dvuna ebuholini labasikati bangafakwa lube nemtselela emadvodzeni lamanyenti.
tgt: "uninzi lwamadoda lufunde iindlela zokuziphatha ezisekelwe kugonyamelo lwamadoda.

src: bekashaywa asasebantfwana ngakoke akasiboni sizatfu sekutsi kungani bangakhulisi bantfwababo nabo ngaleyo ndlela.
tgt: kuba ayebethwa ebuntwaneni ngoku awaboni sizathu sokuba kutheni engenako ukukhulisa kwa ngalo ndlela abantwana bawo.

src: emasikweni lamanengi, emadvodza ayabusa bese kutsi bomake bona babe sezingeni linye nebantfwana ngaleyo ndlelake kwemukelekile nje kutsi nabo bomake bacondziswe tigwegwe ngendlela lefananako neyebantfwana," kwasho yena njalo tshepo.
tgt: kwizizwe ezininzi, amadoda aphethe baze bona abantu base tyhini babonwe bekwinqanaba elinye nelo labantwana ke ngoko kuthathwa njengento eyamkele kileyo into yokubaphatha njenga bantwana.

src: "wonkhe umuntfu unendzima lekumele kutsi ayidlale ekugu culeni tingcondvo," kwasho tshepo.
tgt: umntu ngamnye unendima ekufanele eyidlalile ukuguqula indlela abacinga ngazo abanye," utshilo umofokeng.

src: ukholelwa ekutseni bantfwa na kufanele kutsi bakhuliswe ngaphandle kwekubafaka umcondvo wekutsi intfo letsite yentiwa bulili lobutsite kuphela.
tgt: ukholelwa ekubeni abantwana bakhuliswe ngendlela engazi kugxininisa umahluka ngokwe sini.

src: umkhukhu uguculwe waba spa lesinetsetekile nonkululeko mathebula uthaini masakane utentele ligama ngekutsi agucule umkhukhu wakhe ube spa, indzawo yekutilungisa kutsi ube muhle .
tgt: ityotyombe elidelelekileyo liphu culwe laba yibeauty spa nonkululeko mathebula thaini masakane uzenzele igama ngokujika ityotyo mbe libe yindawo yoku qhunkqa nokuzihombi sa, ibeauty spa .

src: ibhizinisi yakhe isebotshabelo efreystata, ivictory body and nail studio , ikhula ngemfutfo futsi iheha bantfu tindzawo tonkhe kutsi batewumonyo ngwa.
tgt: uzinze ebotshabelo efrey stata, ishishini lakhe, ivictor body and nail studio, likhu la ngokukhawuleza kwaye linomtsalane kumntu wonke ofika eze kufuna ukufekethi swa ngandlela ithile.

src: emva kwekutsengisa itupperware aneminyaka le19, lentfombi leneminyaka lenge28 budzala itsi beyivele inelutsa ndvo lolukhulu lwekuticalela ibhizinisi yayo ngakoke seyi jabulile nyalo kutsi seyilicalile leli bhizinisi.
tgt: sele evela kuthengisa izitya zakwatupperware ngexesha eneminyaka eli19, uneminya ka engama28 ngoku uthi wayesoloko ekulangazelela ukuba angaziqhubela elakhe ishishini kwaye unovuyo lokuba wayiqala le ndlela.

src: "ngicale ngekutsi ngise bentele lomunye kulemboni kulaphoke ngatfola khona sipiliyoni," kwasho yena njalo, angeta ngekutsi wenta tifu ndvo tekutimonyonga, icosmetology ekolishi lasemothe letvet lelisebloemfontein.
