tgt: "ndaqala ngokuse benzela omnye umntu oneshishini elifana neli kwaye kulapho ndathi ndafumana khona amava," utshilo, wongeza athi wafu ndela izifundo zobugci sa bokutsheyisa noku hombisa umzimba, icosme tologist kwikholeji imotheo tvet, ebloemfontein.

src: ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi wakulungela kutsi akhone aphume atimele futsi akazange asabuka emuva kusukela leso sikhatsi.
tgt: ekugqibeleni uye wakulungela ukuzi phumela ecaleni ngo kwakhe kwaye akakhange aphinde eme.

src: ibhizinisi yakhe ina makhasmende lamanyenti ebotshabelo futsi linani lama khasimende akhe liyakhula.
tgt: ishishini lakhe linabantu abe bekade befuna uncedo olufana neli ebotshabelo kwaye unabantu bakhe abeza rhoqo kuye.

src: emakhasimende akhe uwalu ngisa tinzipho temino neteti ntwane, kufocofocotwa, kususa boya nekulungiswa buso.
tgt: kweli shishini lakhe kwenziwa iinzipho zezandla nezenyawo, uku susa uboya, ukuthambisa nokuhonjiswa kobuso.

src: titfombe tespa sakhe le sisemkhukhwini latitfumele etinkhundleni tekuchumana tibe nelisasasa lelikhulu, lapho ba ntfu bebadvumisa khona umco ndvo lomusha wamasakane basho nekusho futsi kutsi uya wakhutsata emantfombatana aselokishini.
tgt: iifoto zendawo yakhe yokuvocavocwa ongenaku tsho ukuba isetyotyombeni ngenxa yobuhle bayo azifake kumajelo oluntu onxibele lwano zithandwe ngabantu abaninzi bencoma ubuchule bukathaini besithi ungumze kelo omhle wokuvuselela amantombazana asezilo kishini.

src: spa lesisemkhukhwini we masenke lamanyako lobukeka njengalotayelekile lapha nge phandle, lespa sinelingekhatsi lelinetsetekile lelilungele kahle kakhulu kutimonyonga.
tgt: le ndawo yokuvocavocwa yakhelwe kwityotyombe lamazinki amatsha, kwaye xa uyijongile ungapha ndle awunakuyicingela ukuba ngaphakathi lino bunewunewu nobu qheleqhele obufanele kanye ukuntenda nokufekethisa.

src: "kuta kwebantfu labangaka kwabangetulu kwaloko bengi kucabanga.
tgt: "yandothusa indlela abantu abalixhasa ngayo ishishini lam.

src: bonjiniyela labasebancane bacece shwa bukhoma ekwakheni imigwaco vukuzenzele unnamed akunaliklasi lelincono lanjiniyela losacece shwa kunekutsi aye endzaweni lekwakhiwa kuyo lenebulukhuni nalenetintfuli asebente ngemishini lebanga umsindvo kanye nemadvodza nebafati labajuluke bamanti nte basebenta ngekutikha ndla.
tgt: iinjineli ezisakhulayo zifumana uqeqesho zisebenza ekwakhiweni kweendlela vukuzenzele unnamed alikho igumbi loku fundela elibhetele lenjineli esaqeqe shwayo kunasembenzini apho abasebenzi bebila be soma futhi kuqhuma nothu li kuphithizela oomatshini abangxolayo.

src: thabiso dladla nasumay maharaj bonjiiniyela laba sitako labatfolakala lapho kusetjentelwa khona (emaare) labafundza umsebenti kubalingani babo labane lwati labasebentisana nabo ngalesikhatsi kulungiswa umgwaco wen2 losemkha tsini wasemthunzini nasempa ngeni ogwini lolusenyakatfo yakwazulunatal.
tgt: uthabiso dladla nosumay maharaj ziinjineli ezince disayo [iiare] ezisafunda ukwenza umsebenzi kwii njineli ezinamava kun2 olungiswayo phakathi kwemthunzini kunye neempangeni kummandla ongakwinxweme lomntla wakwazulunatal.

src: "senta imisebenti lecishe ifane njengemaare.
tgt: "senza imisebenzi efanayo neyeeare.

src: senta lucwaningo, siyabala, senta imi yalelo yebasiti, imiyalelo ya sesayithini kantsi siphendvu la noma miphi imibuto yabo njiniyela lesiyibutwa ngulaba labakhako," kusho dladla.
tgt: senza uhlolo, sibale nezixhobo zokuse benza, senze oko kuthiwa masikwenzwe njengeenjine li ezincedisayo, senze oko kufanele ukwenziwa kule ndawo yokusebenza kwaye siphendula nayiphi na imi buzo yezobunjineli ebuzwa yile nkampani yenza indle la," utshilo udladla.

src: maharaj lowacala kulomkla mo ngenyanga yengci nga2016, kantsi ngaphambilini bekasakha tindledlana letise celeni kwemgwaco enta ne midvwebo yejiyomethri eport elizabeth esikhungweni se kucecesha sasanral, utsite sewuvele ufundze tifundvo letinyenti letibalulekile suke la wenyukela ngasenyakatfo.
tgt: umaharaj owaqala kule projekthi kweyethupha ngowama2016, kwaye nga phambili ebesenza iindle dlana ezisecaleni kwendle la kunye noyilo lwejometri ebhayi kwiziko loqeqesho lakwasanral, uthe sele efunde izinto ezininzi ezi balulekileyo oko wathi weza kweli phondo lakwazu lunatal.

src: "sengifundze indlela bu njiniyela bekwakha lebu lukhuni ngayo nekutsi tintfo tihlangana njani kutsi tise bente.
tgt: "ndiye ndafunda ukuba icandelo lecivil enginee ring linzima kangakanani na kwanangendlela yonke into ehlangana ngayo ukwenza izinto zisebenze."

src: akusiko nje kwenta imidvwebo yetindledlana letiseceleni kwemgcwaco kuphela.
tgt: ayikuko kodwa nje ukuyila iindle dlana ezisecaleni kwendle la.

src: kusebenta ngetakhi wo, emadreyini nemidvwebo yejiyomethri.
tgt: kukusebenza ngeza khiwo, imibhobho yokuha mbisa amanzi kunye ne mizobo emile oku kwe jometri.

src: kahlehle kusho kufundza kuhlanganisa tintfo tonkhe ndzawonye bese utenta kutsi tisebente," asho njalo.
tgt: okubalulekileyo kukufunda indlela yokubeka yonke into kunye nokuyenza ukuba isebenze, "utshilo.

src: dladla wangena kulomkla mo ngemuva kwetinyanga leti10 ngemuva kwekutsi ayosebenta kuloluhlelo lwe kucecesha lwakasanral.
tgt: udladla wathatha inxa xheba kule projekthi malu nga neenyanga ezili10 emva kokuba eyinxalenye ye nkqubo yoqeqesho lwa sesanral.

src: ujabulile kutsi utawusebe nta kulomklamo lomatima lekawuchaza njengalomkhu lu kantsi ufaka ekhatsi ema bhuloho lamakhulu lambalwa kanye nemabhuloho lama ncane ekugijimisa emanti.
tgt: uyavuya kukusebenza kwiprojekti enomcelimnge ni ayichaza njengento eyahlu kileyo nequka ukwakhiwa kweebrorho ezinkulu ezini nzi kunye nezinye ezinci nci ezinqumla phantsi kwe ndlela.

src: "bengisebenta nangekuba ngumhloli ngibuye ngisite labakhi lapho badzinga ku caciselwa kumidvwebo.
tgt: "ndiye ndabandakanye ka ekuhloleni nasekunce diseni inkampani eyenza indlela apho ifuna ukuca ciselwa khona ngemizobo.

src: uma kufika endzabeni yekusebe nta ngemihlaba, sibuye sihlole lomhlaba longetulu leku gcwaliswe ngawo kanye na longephasi.
tgt: xa kufikelelwa kumsebenzi wokulungiswa kusembiwa umhlaba ekuza kwakhiwa kuwo, siyahlola kananjalo uhlobo lomhlaba ogalelwa ukudiba imingxunya egru njiweyo kunye nohlobo lo mhlaba ongaphantsi eku galelwa phezu kwawo lo mhlaba mtsha.

src: sisandza kucala kwenta umsebenti wekuhla nganisa umhlaba nematje kute kufakwe ibtb kantsi senta luhlolo lwawo wonkhe umsebenti lowentiwe bakhi," asho ayibeka.
tgt: kutshanje siye saqala ukwenza umse benzi wokufaka itela ngoko ke sisebenzisa ibtb kwaye sihlola wonke umsebenzi owenziwe yinkampani eye nza indlela, "utshilo.

src: sumay utsi kusebenta ku lomklamo kuta netinkhinga tako.
tgt: usumay uthi ukusebe nza kwiprojekthi kunemice limngeni.

src: bafundzi etikolweni tase makhaya batfola lusito more matshediso litiko lemfundvo lesisekelo licale lu hlelo lolutawuhlo mulisa bafundzi labanyenti emimmangweni yase makhaya leyayincishwe ematfuba ekufundza phambi lini.
tgt: abafundi kwizikolo zasemapha ndleni bafumana uncedo more matshediso isebe lemfundo esisise ko lisungule inkqubo eza kunceda uninzi lwabafundi kwiindawo zase maphandleni ezihleleleki leyo ngokwezemfundo.

src: lomklamo wabasiti ngemfundvo yasemakhaya (ireap) luhlelo lweminya ka lemitsatfu lolutawucala kusetjentiswa nga2018 kute kube nga2021 njengeluhle lo lwekulinga, kantsi luhlose kuhlomulisa tikolo leti188 eningizimu afrika ngaleso sikhatsi.
tgt: iprojekthi yootitsha la abancedisayo ema phandleni (ireap) yi nkqubo yeminyaka emitha thu eza kuphunyezwa uku suka ngowama2018 kude kube ngowama2021 kwisi gaba sokulinga, kwaye yenzelwe ukuba kuzuze izikolo ezimalunga ne188 emzantsi afrika ngeli xesha.

src: lelitiko linelitsemba lekutsi loku kutawufaka sandla ku mazinga ekufundza neku fundzisa kuloluhlelo lwemfu ndvo lesisekelo.
tgt: isebe lithemba ukuba oku kuza kubanegalelo ekuphu culeni umgangatho wokufu nda nokufundisa kwinkqubo yemfundo esisiseko yasema phandleni.

src: loluhlelo lusalingwa eti godzini letimbili kusinye sa letifundza letintsatfu letinga kasebenti kahle etindzaweni tasemakhaya.
tgt: le nkqubo ngoku isalingwa kwizithili ezibini kwipho ndo ngalinye kula amathathu asemaphandleni aneziphu mo zemfundo ezingezihla nga.

src: tifaka ekhatsi sigodzi sasealfred nzo east neor tambo coastal emphu malanga kapa, sigodzi sa seilembe nesaseumzinya thi kwazulunatal, kanye nesigodzi sasesekhukhune nesasemopani elimpopo.
tgt: ezi zithili ziquka i alfred nzo east kunye nezi thili zonxweme lweor tambo empuma koloni, isi thili iilembe kunye neumzi nyathi kwiphondo lakwazu lunatal, kunye nesithili sase sekhukhune nesasemopani elimpopo.

src: umcondzisi lomkhulu wekusetjentiswa kwekha rikhulamu nekunotsiswa kwayo kulitiko lemfundvo lesisekelo seliki tlhabane, u tsite lelitiko selimeme bantfu labasha labalinganiselwa kulabange750 lebaphase matikuletjeni kutsi basite ngetemfundvo etikolweni tasemakhaya.
tgt: umlawuli oyintloko wokuphunyezwa kunye nokuphuculwa kwekhari tyhulam kwisebe lemfundo esisiseko useliki tlhabane, uthe isebe liqeshe abantu abatsha abaphumelele iba nga le12 abamalunga nama750 ukuba babe ngootitshala abancedisayo emaphandleni ezikolweni.

src: "baceceshiwe kancane lo kutabenta kutsi bakhone kusebenta lemisebenti la baniketwe yona.
tgt: "bafumene uqeqesho olu sisiseko oluza kubaxhobisa batsho bakwazi ukwenza imi sebenzi eyabelwe bona.

src: batawu fakwa kusigaba sekucala nalesisemkhatsini, lekufaka ekhatsi libanga 1 kuya ku4,"asho achaza.
tgt: baza kusebenza kwiiklasi zesiga ba esisiseko nakwezesigaba esiphakathi, eziquka ibanga loku1 ukuya kwele4," ucha zile watsho.

src: labasiti ngetemfundvo yasemakhaya balindze leke kutsi basite ngetintfo letihlukene letiphatselene nekharikhulamu, ikakhu lukati kwenta kancono kunyumeresi, ilitheresi ne makhono ekufundza.
tgt: ootitshala abancedisayo emaphandleni kulindeleke ukuba bancedise ngemise benzi eyahlukeneyo enxu lumene nezifundo, ngoku kodwa ukuphucula isifundo sezibalo, esobuchule boku funda nokubhala (ilitherasi) kunye nezakhono zokufu nda.

src: "lena ngulenye indlela yekuniketa lusha emandla etindzaweni letinemnotfo longahambi kahle ngeku tsi kutfutfukiswe emakhono nelwati lwemsebenti," kusho tlhabane.
tgt: "le yindlela yokuxho bisa kananjalo ulutsha kwiindawo ezihlelelekileyo ngokwezoqoqosho ngoku sebenzisa uphuhliso lweza khono kunye namava omse benzi," utshilo utlhabane.

src: utsite labasiti ngemfu ndvo yasemakhaya balindle ke kutsi behlise lomtfwalo wabothishela etikolweni tasemakhaya ngekutsi basite ngemisebenti lephatselene nekharikhulamu njengeku sebentisana nabo ngemi sebenti yasekhaya, emace mbu lenta tibalo, emace mbu lafundzako, emace mbu emisebenti yebuciko, nemiklamo yetekulima.
tgt: uthe ootitshala abance disayo emaphandleni kuli ndeleke ukuba baphungu le umthwalo wootitshala kwizikolo zasemaphandleni ngokuncedisa ngemisebenzi ehambelana nekharityhu lam efana nokuququzelela amaqela emisebenzi yesiko lo, amaqela ezibalo, amaqela okufunda, amaqela emise benzi yobugcisa bokuyila kunye neeprojekthi zolimo.

src: umphatsisikolo ntombi kayise mkhize wasesiko lweni semabanga laphansi iozwathini primary lese ndzaweni yasenodwengu esigodzini saseilembe une litsemba lekutsi loluhlelo lutawusita bafundzi ngema khono ekubala nekufundza.
tgt: untombikayise mkhize oyi nqununu yesikolo samaba nga aphantsi iozwathini pri mary enodwengu kwisithili saseilembe uthemba ukuba le nkqubo iza kunceda uni nzi lwabafundi bakhe abatsa la nzima ngokufunda noku bala.

src: sikolo sakhe sinebafundzi laba387 kusukela kuliba nga r kuya ku7 lababhalise kulomnyaka.
tgt: isikolo sakhe esiqala kwiba nga r siphele kwibanga 7 sinabafundi abamalunga nama387 kulo nyaka.

src: "bafundzi betfu labanyenti bavela emakhaya lange nabatali kantsi labanye ba nakekelwa bogogo.
tgt: "uninzi lwabafundi bethu luvela kumakhaya angena bantu badala ngelixa abanye bephuma kumakhaya aphethwe ngoomawokhu lu.

src: abanabo bantfu labangabasita ngemi sebenti yesikolo yasekhaya noma babakhutsate kutsi bafundze, kantsi loku kwe hlisa lizinga labenta ngalo eklasini," asho achaza.
tgt: abanabo abantu aba nokubancedisa ngomsebenzi wesikolo okanye ukubakhu thaza ukuba bafunde, kwaye oku kuchaphazela indlela abaqhuba ngayo kwizifundo zabo," uchaze watsho.

src: "lenye inkinga kwekutsi bafundzi betfu labasema bangeni laphansi bafundzi swa yonkhe intfo nge sizulu kantsi uma ba ndlulela kumabanga lase mkhatsini kufanele bagu cuke bente tonkhe tifundvo ngesingisi, ngakoke kuba yinkinga lenkulu kubo kutsi bagucuke.
tgt: "enye ingxaki kukuba abafundi bethu abakwisi gaba sesiseko bafundiswa zonke izifundo ngesizulu kwaye xa beya kwisigaba esiphakathi kuyanyanzeleka ukuba batshintshe benze uni nzi lwezifundo ngesingesi, ngoko ke kubangumceli mngeni omkhulu kubo ukuba baqhele ukufunda ngesingesi."

src: ngalesikhatsi sekulinga, sikale lomtselela nemphume lelo ngekutsi sente lucwani ngo nekuhlola kwaloluhle lo lwereap .
tgt: ngexesha lesigaba sokuli nga, siza kuhlola ifuthe kunye nendlela esebenza ngayo inkqubo yereap ngokwenza uvavanyo nohlo lo lwenkqubo yereap .

src: sibuye safuna lusito lalabasitfupha laba neticu tasenyuvesi kodvwa basengakasebenti njenge bachumanisi balomklamo.
tgt: siye sacela noncedo lwabantu abathandathu abanezidanga abangaphangeliyo okwango ku ukuba basebenze njenga baququzeleli beprojekthi.

src: batawuba khona kusinye ngasinye sigodzi lesinge nelele.
tgt: baza kubekwa kwisithili ngasinye esithatha inxa xheba.

src: labachumanisi balo mklamo batawubuye basite kutsi bente lucwaningo ne luhlolo lwalomklamo.
tgt: abaququzeleli be projekthi baza kusinceda kananjalo ekubekeni iliso nasekuhlolweni kweproje kthi.

src: idriving ambitions ifundzisa bantfu labakhubatekile kushayela vukuzenzele unnamed bantfu labakhubatekile bavamise kuba ne bumatima bekutfola ematfuba lafananako nala babo labanemitimba lenga kakhubateki.
tgt: idriving ambitions ifundisa abantu abakhubazekileyo ukuqhuba vukuzenzele unnamed abantu abakhubazeki leyo kumaxa amaninzi abawafumani lula amathuba njengabantu abangakhubazekanga.

src: kunye kwaloku kufundza kushayela imoto.
tgt: amanye ala mathuba aquka ukukwazi ukuqhuba imoto.

src: kepha luhle lo lolungakavami lwenhlanga no iquadpara association of south africa (iqasa) selu fundzise bantfu laba120 labakhubatekile kushayela timo to letakhiwe tafanela tidzingo tabo, labange80 balabantfu sebawatfolile emalayisensi abo ekushayela.
tgt: kodwa inkqubo eyodwa eqhutywa yiquadpara association of south africa (iqasa) ifundise abantu abakhubazekileyo abangama120 ukuqhuba iimo to ezilungiselelwe abantu abakhubazekileyo, kwaba bantu abangama80 sele bezifumene iilayisenisi zabo zokuqhuba.

src: "bantfu labakhubatekile bahlala njalo babukene netinsayeya letinkhulu kakhulu nekuhamba baye lapho bafuna kuya khona, ikakhulu ngoba abakwati kuse bentisa tigitjelwa temmango letinyenti.
tgt: "abantu abakhubazekileyo kumaxa amaninzi bayasokola ukuzihambela baye kwiindawo abafuna ukuya kuzo, kwaye isizathu soku ubukhulu becala kukuba bengakwazi ukusebenzisa izithuthi zika wonkewonke.

src: besifuna kuyisombulula lenkinga futsi, lokuba luleke kakhulu, kwenta bantfu kutsi bakhone kucasheka," kwasho sikhulu lesiphakeme (iceo) sakaqasa ari seirlis naye lokhubateke sicu semtimba sangentasi.
tgt: sifuna ukuyi lungisa le ngxaki, kodwa eyona nto siyifuna ngamandla kukuba bakwazi ukufumana imisebenzi," litshilo igosa eliphezulu lesigqeba (iceo) seqasa uari seirlis naye okhubazeke iingalo nemilenze.

src: loku bekunguyona nshiseke lo lechuba luhlelo lwedriving ambitions, lolwasungulwa nga2013.
tgt: koku okwabangela ukuba kuqaliswe le nkqubo yoku fundisa ukuqhuba yakwadriv ing ambitions ngowama2013.

src: iqasa yahlangana nenkampani yakaavis lecashisa ngetimoto yakhulumisa na nayo ngekufundzisa bantfu labakhubatekile kutsi bakwati kushayela timoto letakhiwe ta fanela tidzingo tabo.
tgt: uqasa waya wadibana nenkampani eqeshisa ngeemoto uavis ukuze babonisane ngomba wokufundisa abantu abakhubazekileyo ukuqhuba izithuthi ezilungiselelwe kanye le meko yabo.

src: "iavis yasivisisa lesidzingo, yaphindze futsi yakubona kubaluleka kwabo njengoba nje bacashisa ngetimoto letishayelwa ngetandla kuphela.
tgt: "uavis wayiqonda le ngxa ki, futhi wabona nokubalule ka kwayo njengoko beqeshisa ngeemoto ezinobuxhakaxhaka bokuqhuba obusetyenziswa ngezandla.

src: bavu ma kusinikelela ngetimoto tetfu tekucala kutsi tisetjentiselwe kufundzisa kushayela," kwasho seirlis.
tgt: baye bavuma ukusipha imoto yokuqala esasiyise benzisa ukufundisa abantu uku qhuba," utshilo useirlis.

src: kufaka ticelo tekuba kulo luhlelo kuvulelwe bantfu labakhubateke imikhono nemi lente kanye nalabo labakhu bateke sicu semtimba sangentasi lasebavele banawo emalayisensi ekufundzela kushayela.
tgt: izicelo zabantu abafuna uku funda ukuqhuba zivulelekile kubantu abakhubazeke amanqe kunye nabo bakhubazeke iingalo nemilenze banelayisenisi yokufunda ukuqhuba.

src: "bahlolwa bodokotela labe laphana ngekukwentisa umse benti lotsite (maoccupational therapist) kwenta siciniseko se kutsi bayakhona yini kunyakata masinyane futsi kalula nekutsi futsi bayakhona yini kushayela ngetilawuli letentiwe tafane la tidzingo tabo ngaphandle kwekuba sesimeni lesiyingoti.
tgt: "baya kuvavanyo olwenziwa yingcali yokuncedisa izigu lane zikwazi ukuzenzela izinto (ioccupational therapist) uku qinisekisa ukuba banazo izakhono zokuqhuba ngendlela engazikubeka abanye abaqhubi engozini.

src: kubeseke kwentiwa luhlolo lwekuncuma kufaneleka kusi twa ngetimali kute kutfolakale kutsi ingabe bangakhona ku lukhokhela malini loluhlelo, bese kutsike lena lenye imali yekuphelelisela bayayikhokhelwa," kwachaza seirlis.
tgt: emva koko kuye ku jongwe imeko yezimali yomntu lowo, oko kukuthi, angakwazi ukubhatala malini na, ize xa ingazukwanela leyo anayo, enye ayibhatalelwe," ucacise watsho useirlis.

src: bahlanganyeli baneluchunge chunge lolugcwele lwetifundvo tekufundza kushayela, kute kube ngulapho sebaku lungele kutsi sebangenta luhlolo lwabo.
tgt: abantu abathatha inxaxheba kule nkqubo banikwa iiyure ezaneleyo befundiswa ukuqhu ba, bade babe bakulungele uku ya kuvavanywa.

src: lomunye lowachuba kahle kakhulu kuloluhlelo lweqa sa ngucarol khoza, lowatfola ingoti yemoto eminyakeni lemibili leyendlulile.
tgt: omnye wabantu abalisebenzisayo eli thuba ngucarol kho za, owafumana ingozi yemoto kwiminyaka emibini eyadlu layo.

src: lengoti yamshiya akhubateke sicu sem timba sangentasi.
tgt: wafumana umonzakalo owamkhubaza amanqe.

src: igo george ihola embili ekuhlomiseni bantfu labakukhubatekile vukuzenzele unnamed kufinyelela tigitjelwa temmango kuvamise kuba yinsayeya kubantfu labakhubatekile ngoba emabhasi lamanyenti kanye nemakhumbi ete tisetjentiswa letidzingekako kute kugitjeliswe bagibeli labakhu batekile.
tgt: igo george ihamba phambili kuma phulo okuxhobisa abakhubazekileyo vukuzenzele unnamed ukusebenzisa izithuthi zikawonkewonke yingxaki enkulu abajamelene nayo abantu abakhubazekileyo njengoko iibhasi kunye neeteksi ezininzi zingenabo ubuxhakaxhaka obufunekayo ukuze zikwazi ukubakhwelisa.

src: bomasipala kulo lonkhe le live lakitsi nabo manje sebeme ngetinyawo basombulula lenkinga.
tgt: oomasipala kulo lonke eli nabo ngoku bafuna ukuqalisa iinkqubo eziza kusombulula le ngxaki.

src: masipala wendzawo wasegeorge wendlala emazinga lamasha ekutsi tigitjelwa temmango tingabasebentela kanjani bantfu labakhubatekile.
tgt: kwaye umasipala wengingqi wasegeorge nguye ohamba phambili ngokwendle la izithuthi zikawonkewonke ezinokutshintshwa ngayo uku ze zikwazi ukukhwelisa abantu abakhubazekileyo.

src: ngekusitwa ngetimali tesi bonelelo lesivela kulitiko letekutfutsa, inchubo yetigitjelwa letingemabhasi lajike letako (ibrt) ego george kwamanje inemabhasi lamancani lange35, emabhasi lamakhulu lange36 kanye nema bhasi lasemkhatsini ngebukhu lu lange33.
tgt: inkqubo yeebhasi eziquqa zibuyelela, igo george, ixhaswa ngemali lisebe lika zwelonke lezothutho kwaye kungoku nje ineebhasi ezincinci ezingama35, iibhasi ezinku lu ezingama36 kunye neebha si eziphakathi ezingama33.

src: wonkhe lamabhasi akhiwe afanela titulo letine masondvo.
tgt: zonke ezi bhasi ziyakwazi ukukhwelisa abantu abahamba ngesitulo esinamavili.

src: lamabhasi lamakhulu kanye nalawo lasemkhatsini ngebukhulu anetindzawo tekweelekthronoki tekuhamba tihlalo temasondvo, tihla lo letikhetsekile kanye naletinye tisetjentiswa letetayelekile.
tgt: iibhasi ezinkulu neziphakathi zinendawo ethotywa ngombane elungiselelwe ukukhwela noku hlala abantu abahamba ngezitulo ezinamavili kwakunye nezinye izinto eziqhelekileyo ebhasini.

src: lamabhasi lamancani anakwa ngalokukhetsekile, lokwatsi, ngesikhatsi acala kusetjentiswa nga2015, aba wekucala ngca eningizimu afrika kuba nesisetjentiswa lesingumshini wekuphakamisa bagibeli la bahleti etihlalweni temasondvo.
tgt: kodwa umsebenzi omkhulu wenziwe kwezi bhasi zincinci, zona ukufika kwazo ngowama2015, yayizezokuqa la emzantsi afrika ukuba nenqwanqwa lokunyusa abantu abahamba ngezitulo ezinama vili zibakhwelisa.

src: aphindze futsi abe nendzawo yetihlalo temasondvo kanye neminyango levulwa iphindze ivalwe yimishini lesebenta nge mandla emoya (ngehydrau lics), leyenta kube lula kutsi bagibeli labakhubatekile bakwati kungena ebhasini.
tgt: zikwanayo nendawo yokuba bamise izitulo zabo ezinamavili futhi amacango azo anehayidrolikhi, loo nto yenze ukuba abantu abakhuba zekileyo bakwazi ukuzikhwela.

src: "leli ngilo kuphela luhlobo lwemabhasi eningizimu afri ka lelifinyeleleka ngalokuphe lele," kwasho umphatsi wego george james robb.
tgt: "olu hlobo lweebhasi lulo kuphela emzantsi afrika eku lula ukuba lukhwelwe nguye wonke umntu," utshilo umlawuli wego george ujames robb.

src: "lena ngulenye yetinsika letibaluleke kakhulu kunchu bo yego george.
tgt: le yenye yezinto ezingundoqo ezibalula ngayo igo george.

src: kubalule ke kakhulu kutsi wonkhe muntfu egeorge akwati kufinye lela tigitjelwa temmango kute kutsi akwati kutfola ematfuba emsebenti, ekuyotsenga etitolo, etenkholo, ekukhibika kanye ne tinsita letifanana nekunakekelwa ngetemphilo.
tgt: kubalulekile ukuba wonke umntu wasegeorge akwazi ukuzisebenzisa izithuthi ziwonkewonke ukuze akwa zi ukuya emsebenzini, ezivenkileni, ecaweni, kwiindawo zolonwabo kunye nezo kufu maneka kuzo iinkonzo zezempilo.

src: "bagibeli labakhubatekile bayakutfokotela kucatjangelwa kwetidzingo kanye netinsayeya tabo temihla nemalanga tekuya etindzaweni letikhashane nase khaya, kanye nekutimela lokuta nekutsi batihambele bona ngekwabo."
tgt: "abakhweli abakhubazekileyo bayayibulela into yokuba imeko yabo iqondwe kunye neenzima abadibana nazo imihla nezolo bezama ukuya kwiindawo ezi kude namakhaya abo, kwaye nokuba kuqondwe ukubaluleka kokungaxhomekeki emntwini, uzihambele wedwa."

src: rodrique felix, lomunye walabasebentisa lamabhasi, wabandzakanyeka engotini yesidududu etinyangeni le18 letengcile.
tgt: urodrique felix, omnye wabantu abasebenzisa ezi bha si, yena wafumana ingozi ye sithuthuthu kwiinyanga ezinga ma18 ezidlulileyo.

src: kwamanje sewu hamba ngesihlalo semasondvo kepha utsi lamabhasi akwenta kube lula kutsi aye esibhedlela.
tgt: kungoku nje uhamba ngesitulo esinama vili kwaye uthi kulula kakhulu ukuhamba ngezi bhasi xa esiya esibhedlela.

src: "empeleni, yonkhe igeorge itivuna kahle kakhulu ngalokwecile tihlalo temasondvo, lokuyintfo lenhle kakhulu," kwasho rodrique.
tgt: "okuyinene kukuba sonke isixeko sasegeorge sicetywe ngendlela ethathela ingqalelo abantu abanezitulo ezinamavili, into leyo iluncedo kakhulu ku thi sonke," utshilo urodrique.

src: yati tinhlobo tekuhlukunyetwa letihlukene vukuzenzele unnamed uma ngabe uku budlelwano lapho uhlukunyetwa khona noma umntfwana lo nakekelwa nguwe uyahlu kunyetwa, ungatsatsa tinya tselo tekutivikela noma uvikele lomntfwana nge kutsi uye enkhantolo noma ubike loludzaba embutfweni wemaphoyisa aseningizimu afrika (isaps).
tgt: zazi iindlela ngeendlela zokuxhatshazwa vukuzenzele unnamed okokuba uphatheke kakubi eluthandweni okanye umntwa na ophantsi kwakho uphe thwe kakubi, ungawathatha amanyathelo okuzikhusela okanye okukhusela umntwa na ngokuya ezinkundleni zamatyala okanye ngokuya kuxela le meko kumbutho wamapolisa asemzantsi afri ka (isaps).

src: umtsetfo wekuhluku nyetwa emakhaya uniketa labo labahlukunyetwako emakhaya kuvikeleka lokundlulele lokungentiwa ngekusebentisa umtsetfo.
tgt: umthetho wobundlo bongela basekhaya unika amaxhoba obundlobongela basekhaya olona khuseleko luliqilima olunokunikwa ngumthetho.

src: kuhlukunyetwa kwente ka ngetindlela letihlukene kantsi kubalulekile kutsi bomake bavisise letinhlobo letihlukene tekuhlukunye twa kute bativikele.
tgt: ukuphathwa kakubi kuzi bonakalisa ngeendlela ngeendlela kwaye kubalule kile okokuba abantu aba bhinqileyo bazazi iintlobo ngeentlobo zokuphathwa kakubi ukuze bakwazi uku zikhusela.

src: kuhlukunyetwa emakhaya kwenteka ngalesikhatsi umuntfu abuketana naloku:ukushaywa: sibonelo, uma ngabe ushaywa noma wetfu swa ngeludlame.
tgt: ubundlobongela basekhaya benzeka xa umntu ephantsi kwezi meko zilandelayo:ukuphathwa kakubi ngo kwasemzimbeni: umzekelo, xa ubethwa okanye ugrogriswa ngobundlobongela.

src: kuhlukunyetwa ngetemacansi: uma ngabe lolohlukunye kwato adlwenguliwe noma acindzetelwe kutsi ente tento letiphatselene nemacansi noma abukele tento tetemacansi leti hlambalatako.
tgt: ukuphathwa kakubi ngokwe sondo: xa ixhoba lidlwengulwa okanye linyanzelwa ukwenza okanye ukubukela izenzo zesondo ezilithoba isidima.

src: kuhlukunyetwa emoyeni, ngemlomo noma ngekwengco ndvo: loku kwenteka uma nga be umuntfu uhlala adzelelwa njalo, entiwe ative amncane noma abitwe ngemagama lahlambalatako.
tgt: ukuphathwa kakubi ngokwa semphefumlweni, ngentetha nangokwasengqondweni: oku kwenzeka xa umntu esoloko ethukwa, ephoxwa okanye esenyeliswa.

src: kuhlukunyetwa ngekwete mnotfo: loku kwenteka uma ngabe ungavunyelwa kwekutsi utentele imali yakho.
tgt: ukuphathwa kakubi ngokwe zoqoqosho: le nto ingenzeka xa ixhoba lithintelwa ukwamkela umvuzo.

src: kwetfuswa: sibonelo sekwe tfuswa kungalesikhatsi lolohlukunyetwako atfola imi layeto noma emasms lamsa bisako nalatfusako.
tgt: isoyikiso: umzekelo wesoyiki so kuxa ixhoba lifumana iisms okanye imiyalezo esongelayo neyoyikisayo.

src: kuhlukunyetwa: sibonelo kungaba ngendlela yekutfola tincingo njalo njalo noma ulandzelelwa njalo kuba nala kubukako kantsi loku kuku bangele kutsi wesabe.
tgt: ukuxhatshazwa: umzekelo kukusoloko utsalelwa umnxe ba okanye ukusoloko ujongiwe, nto leyo ekwenza woyike.

src: kulandzelelwa: kwenteka ngalesikhatsi lona lokuhlu kumetako aloku akulandzela noma afune kukhuluma nawe ngenkhani ungatsandzi kukhu luma naye.
tgt: ukuchwechwelwa: kwenzeka xa lowo ukuphethe kakubi esoloko ekulandela okanye ekunyanzela okokuba uthethe naye noxa ungafuni.

src: kukhulumisana kubalulekile kute wati umntfwanakho vukuzenzele unnamed akusilula kukhuli sa umntfwana, ko dvwa lusito lolunca ne loluvela kubosolwati lungaba lusito lolukhulu ekucinisekiseni kwekutsi wenta ngendlela lekahle longakhona ngayo.
tgt: ukuthetha kubaluleke kakhulu ekwazini umntwana wakho vukuzenzele unnamed akululanga uku khulisa umntwana, kodwa uncedo olu ncinane lweengcali lunga nceda kakhulu ekuqiniseki seni okokuba wenza konke okunokwenza.

src: ngekusho kwechildline south africa, inhlangano lengatfoli inzuzo levikela bantfwana kuto tonkhe ti nhlobo teludlame kantsi ye nta kube nendlela yekuna kwa kwemalungelo eba ntfwana eningizimu afrika.
tgt: ngokwabakwachildline south africa, umbutho onga sebenzeli nzuzo okhuse la abantwana kuzo zonke izenzo zobundlobongela nokhuthaza ukuhlonitshwa kwamalungelo abantwa na emzantsi afrika, aba zali mabathethe ngendlela eyakhayo nabantwana.

src: ungabatsetsisi; khuluma nabo ngenhlonipho; bavu mele bakhetse; ababe yince nye yekutsatfwa kwetincu mo; bafundzise lokukahle nalokungasikahle; bese uya bakhutsate kutsi basho indle la labativa ngayo.
tgt: musa ukubangxolisa: the tha nabo ngembeko; benze bazikhethele; babandakanye xa kuthathwa izigqibo; bafundise okuhle kokubi; kwaye bakhuthaze ukuba bazivakalise izimvo zabo.

src: ningakwenta loku nge kubamba imihlangano ye mndeni njalo njalo, lapho wonkhe umuntfu atawukhu luma abuye alalele.
tgt: oku ungakwenza ngokubamba iintlanga niso zosapho rhoqo, apho wonke umntu athi athethe kwaye aphulaphule.

src: kukhu luma yindlela lekahle yeku fundzisa bantfwana kantsi ungakhutsata kutiphatsa kahle ngekutsi uvele uba chazele tintfo.
tgt: uku thetha yeyona ndlela ingco no kakhulu yokufundisa abantwana, kwaye unga bakhuthaza okokuba bazi phathe kakuhle ngokuthi nje ubachazele izinto.

src: ichildline south africa yecwayisa ba tali kutsi balalelisise neku tsi babe nesineke, njengoba kungenteka kutsi bantfwa na bangakwati kusho indlela labativa ngayo nalebacaba nga ngayo.
tgt: umbutho ichildline ucebisa abaza li okokuba baphulaphule ngononophelo kwaye babe nomonde, kuba abantwana basenokungakwazi ukuthe tha into abayicingayo okanye abanemvakalelo yayo.

src: bantfwana badzinga kwati kutsi yini leyamukelekile nalengakamukeleki cinisekisa kutsi bayati kutsi kungani kudzingeka umtse tfo nekutsi kutawuba nemi phumela uma ngabe bawu phula.
tgt: abantwana kufuneka bayazi into eyamkelekileyo nengamkelekanga qinisekisa okokuba bayazi ukuba kutheni imithetho ifuneka nokokuba ukuba bayayaphula kuza kubakho iziphumo.

src: hlala wenta ngendle la lefanako kantsi uyifeze lemiphumela.
tgt: kufuneka uso loko ungagungqi kwaye ezo ziphumo uzinyanzelise.

src: ngalesikhatsi bantfwana baya ngekukhula, bakhutsate kutsi bacocisane ngalemitsetfo bese uyabace la kutsi basite ngekuncuma lemiphumela.
tgt: ngokuya bekhula abantwa na, bakhuthaze okokuba bayixoxe le mithetho kwaye benze bancedise ekumiseleni iziphumo.

src: babonge njalo bantfwana uma bente kahlengekubatjela kwekutsi utitsandza kangakanani letintfo letihle labatentako, tento letimbi tingahle titi phelele.
tgt: soloko ubancoma abantwana ngokuziphatha kakuhle ngokubaxelela indlela ozithanda ngayo izinto ezintle abazenzayo, ukuziphatha kakubi kunga thi shwaka.

src: kungeta, bonga umsebenti lomuhle kancono kunekubajezisa.
tgt: ngaphezu koko, imivuzo ingcono kune zohlwayo.

src: ngalesikha tsi batali labanyenti babonga bantfwana ngetinto teba ntfwana tekudlala nemaswi di, kubonga lokuhle kuba kubanga, kumamatseka nekukhombisa inshisekelo kubo.
tgt: noxa abazali aba ninzi bevuza abantwana ngezinto zokudlala okanye iilekese, eyonayona mivuzo kukwanga, uncumo noku bonisa ukuba nomdla kubo.

src: kwakha kutetsemba kubalulekile kutsi usite umntfwanakho ekwakheni indlela yekutetsemba.
tgt: ukwakha ukuzithemba kubalulekile okokuba umncede umntwana wakho azithembe.

src: unga basita bantfwana bakho ngekutsi ubabonge ngekutsi bazame kusita nekusebe ntisa imicabango yabo, ku hlakanipha nekudlala nabo; kubakhutsata kutsi bakhu lume; ubente bative bakhe tsekile nekutsi ubatjele kutsi babaluleke kangakanani; futsi utsembeke, kute kutsi batsembele kuwe.
tgt: abantwana bakho ungabanceda ngokubancoma kuba bezame ukunceda no kusebenzisa ingqondo yabo, ngobukrelekrele nokutha nda ukudlala; ubakhuthaze ukuba bathethe, bazive bebalulekile nokubaxelela okokuba babalulekile; nawe kufuneka uthembeke ukuze nabo bakuthembe.

src: kutiphatsa lokunebungoti akukamukelekiakukaze kwamukeleke kulimata bantfwana.
tgt: ukuba ngqwabalala akulungangaakwamkeleki ukuba ngqwabalala ebantwaneni.

src: tento tekubalimata tifaka ekha tsi kumemeta, kubatfuka, kubasabisa nekubenta bative babancane.
tgt: ukuziphatha okwenzaka lisayo kuquka ukungxolisa, ukuthuka, ukubasongela nokubenza bazive benge yonto.

src: kutfuka embi kwebantfwana noma kuba tfuka kungabenta bative ban gakaphephi futsi basatjiswa.
tgt: ukuthuka phambi kwabantwana okanye uku bathuka kungabenza bazive benexhala kwaye besengozini.

src: litfuba lekugcina lekubhalisela kuvota vukuzenzele unnamed imphelasontfo yekubha lisela kuvota itawu ba ngemgcibelo, ti26 nangelisontfo, ti27 bhimbi dwane 2019 ngekusho kwasi hlalo wekhomishini yelukhe tfo letimele (iiec), glen mashinini.
tgt: ithuba lokugqibela lokubhalisela uvota vukuzenzele unnamed impelaveki yokubha lisela ukuvota izakuba ngomgqibelo, umhla wama26 nangecawa, umhla wama27 kweyomqungu yowama2019 ngokutsho kukasihlalo wekhomishini yonyulo ezimeleyo (iiec), uglen mashinini.

src: mashinini watsi tonkhe titeshi tekuvota leti22 932 titawuvulwa kusuka ngensi mbi ye08h00 kuya kuye17h00 kulemphelasontfo yekubhalisela kuvota.
tgt: umashinini uthi zonke izikhululo zokuvota ezi ngama22 932 ziza kuvula ngentsimbi ye08h00 zivale ngeye17h00 ngempelaveki yokubhalisela ukuvota.

src: "loku kwentelwa kuvumela bavoti labasha babhalise nekutsi labo labangacali kuvota babuyekete futsi bahlole imininingwane yabo.
tgt: "oku kukuvumela abavoti abatsha ukuba babhalise bona asebebhalisile balungi se baze bakhangele iinkcu khacha zabo zokubhalisa.

src: "mashinini watsi nyalo kune bavoti labatigidzi leti26.1 lababhalisile kuloluhlu lwebavoti lwavelonkhe.
tgt: "umashinini uthi bazizigidi ezingama26.1 abavoti aba bhalisileyo kumqulu wabavoti odibeneyo wesizwe.

src: iiec ihlose kungeta loku ngenani bavoti labasha la basigidzi kuloluhlu lwe bavoti ngembi kwelukhetfo lwe2019.
tgt: iiec inethemba lokongeza nokuba sisigidi esinye ubu ncinane sabavoti abatsha kumqulu wabavoti phambi konyulo lowama2019.

src: mashinini watsi kubhali sela kuvota kutawentiwa na setikhungwini tekucondzisa similo (majele) eveni lonkhe kute tiboshwa nato tisebentise lilungelo lato lekuvota.
tgt: umashinini uthi ukubha lisela ukuvota kuzakuqhu tywa nakumaziko ezolule ko (iintolongo) kweli lizwe jikelele ukunika amabanjwa ithuba lokuba asebenzise ilungelo lawo lokuvota.

src: "mayelana nekuvota, tiboshwa titsatfwa njenge bavoti lababhalisele kuvota esigodzini lijele lelikuso.
tgt: "ngokuphathelene noku vota, amabanjwa athathwa njengabhalisele ukuvota kwizithili zovoto apho iinto longo zawo zikhoyo.

src: "emalunga emndeni alabo lababoshiwe labaseti khungwini tekucondzisa similo ayacelwa kutsi atfumele bomatisi babo kubo ngembi kwekucala kubhalisela kuvota," kwasho mashinini.
tgt: "iintsapho zabo baseluvale lweni kumaziko ezoluleko ziyacelwa ukuba zibazisele iincwadizazisi zabo lingekaqalisi eli phulo lokubhalisela uvoto," utshilo umashinini.

src: kubhalisela kuvotaiiec iyatsemba kutsi bavoti, lesevele babhalisile, batawusebentisa lelitfuba kuvakashela etiteshini tekuvota bayohlola kutsi babhalisile nekucinisekisa kanye nekulungisa imininingwane yemakheli abo.
tgt: ukubhalisela ukuvotaiiec inethemba lokuba abavoti asebebhalisile baza kusebenzisa eli thuba ukutyelela izikhululo zabo zovoto ukuyokukhangela ukubhali swa kwabo kwaye baqinisekise iinkcukacha zeedilesi zabo.

src: naku lekufanele ukwati: tonkhe takhamuti taseni ngizimu afrika letineminya ka le16 nangetulu letina matisi losemtsetfweni tinga bhalisela kuba bavoti (nano ma kutawuvota kuphela labo labaneminyaka lokungenani le18 ngelilanga lekuvota).
tgt: naku ekufanele ukuba ukwazi: bonke abemi bomzantsi afrika abaminyaka ili16 nangaphezulu ubudala abaneencwadizazisi banga bhalisa njengabavoti (nango na ingabo baminyaka ili18 ubudala ngosuku lokuvota abanokuvota).

src: tindlela longatigcina ngato uphephile kulesikhatsi semaholide akhisimusi dale hes sikhatsi semaholi de akhisimusi sikhatsi senjabulo.
tgt: iindlela zokuzigcina ukhuselekile ngezi holide zekrisimesi dale hes iiholide zekrisime si zilixesha leziyu nguma nolonwa bo.

src: kodvwa siphindze siletse bungoti lobukhulu lobu fana netingoti tetimoto, kweba nalamanye emacala.
tgt: kodwa zikwalixesha lokuxhaphaka kwezehlo ezifana neengozi zeemoto, ubusela nolwaphu lomthetho.

src: landzela leticwayiso kucinisekisa kutsi uba nesikhatsi lesiphephile na lesitfokotisako netihlobo takho.
tgt: sebenzisa ezi ngcebiso ukuqinisekisa ukuba ukhuselekileyo futhi uyalonwabela eli xesha nezihlobo zakho.

src: hlala uphephile emigwacenitingoti temgwaco tiba tini ngi kakhulu ngesikhatsi semaholide akhisimusi, lapho bantfu labanengi bashona.
tgt: hlala ukhuselekile ezindleleniiingozi zendlela zanda kakhulu ngexesha leeholide zekrisimesi, futhi zibulala abantu abaninzi.

src: kute uhlale uphephile, cinisekisa kutsi: wenta luhlolo lwemoto ngembi kwekucala luhambo, kute ucinisekise kutsi imoto yakho isesimeni lesikahle.
tgt: ukuze uhlale ukhuselekile, qinisekisa ukuba: uyasihlola isithuthi sakho phambi kokuba ungene endleleni ukuya apho usingise khona, ukuqinisekisa ukuba imoto yakho ikumga ngatho ofanelekileyo.

src: wena nebagibeli bakho nihlala nibophe ema bhandi.
tgt: wena nabakhweli ba kho nihlala niwanxibile amabhanti okhuselo.

src: utsatsa likhefu njalo emva kwemahora lamabili uma ushayela libanga lelidze.
tgt: uyaphumla rhoqo emva kweeyure ezimbini xa uqhuba imigama emide.

src: gwema kushayela udza kiwe.
tgt: nokuba kuyintoni na ungaqhubi xa usele.

src: landzela silinganiso sesivinini lesibekiwe bese ulandzela yonkhe imitse tfo yemgwaco.
tgt: qhuba ngesantya esimiselweyo futhi uthobele yonke eminye imithetho yezendlela.

src: caphela letinye tigitje lwa nalabahamba nge tinyawo.
tgt: uyaziqaphela ezinye izithuthi nabahambi ngeenyawo endleleni.

src: gwema kusebentisa lucingo uma ushayela.
tgt: awusebenzisi mnxeba xa uqhuba.

src: kuvikeleka kwebantfwanatindzawo tetiningi letivakashelwako tihlala timatasatasa, lokusho kutsi kunematfuba ekutsi u mntfwana wakho advuke lapho kugcwele khona bantfu.
tgt: ukhuseleko lwabantwanaiindawo ezininzi zoku chithela iiholide zizindawo ezixakeke kakhulu, into ethetha ukuba ungala hlekana nomntwana wa kho phakathi kwabantu abaninzi.

src: kubalulekile futsi kutsi uhlale ubagadzile bantfwa na bakho uma benta tintfo letifana nekubhukusha e lwandle noma badlala eti ndzaweni tekudlala.
tgt: kukwabaluleke kakhulu ukubabeka esweni abantwana bakho xa besenza imidlalwana efana nokuqubha elwandle okanye bedlala kwiindawo zokudlala.

src: nati letinye ticwayiso tekugci na umntfwana wakho a phephile: cinisekisa kutsi ba ntfwana labancane bahlala bagadziwe ngumuntfu lomdzala.
tgt: nazi iingcebiso zokugcina abantwana ba kho bekhuselekile: qinisekisa ukuba abantwana abancinci babaphantsi kweliso lomntu omdala okhathalayo.

src: emotweni, cinisekisa kutsi bantfwana labancane bahlala bafase libhandi.
tgt: emotweni qinisekisa ukuba abantwana abancinci banxityiswe amabhanti.

src: fundzisa bantfwana labasakhulile inombolo yamakhalekhikhini wakho labatayishayela uma basesimeni lesibucayi.
tgt: fundisa abantwana bakho abadala ukuba bayazi iinombolo yomnxeba wakho weselula ukulungiselela xa kunokuvela ingxaki.

src: cinisekisa kutsi ba ntfwana labangakwati kubhukusha kahle ba gcokiswa tinsita teku bhukusha.
tgt: qinisekisa ukuba abantwana abanga kwaziyo ukuqubha kakuhle bafakwa amabhanti asenga lweni avuthelwayo xa bequbha.

src: fundzisa bantfwana kutsi bangagibeli imoto yemuntfu labangamati futsi banga khulumi nemuntfu labangamati.
tgt: fundisa abantwana bakho ukuba bangakhe balinge bakhwele kwisithuthi somntu abangamaziyo kwaye bangathethi nabantu abangabaziyo.

src: bamba umntfwana ngesandla uma useti ndzaweni letimatasatasa nanoma weca umgwaco.
tgt: mbambe ngesandla umntwana wakho xa ukwiindawo ezixa kekileyo naxa uwela indlela.

src: fundza tintfo letisisekelo telusito lwekucala kute ukhone kutisebentisa uma usesimeni setemphilo lesibucayi.
tgt: funda uncedo lokuqala lwabaqalayo ukuze ukwazi ukunceda xa kunokuvela ingxaki yezonyango.

src: bugebenguliyakhula lizinga letehlakalo tekugcekeza etindlini kanye netekweba ngesikha tsi semaholide akhisimusi.
tgt: ulwaphulomthethokukho ukwanda kwe mikhuba efana nokuqhe kezwa kwezindlu nobusela ngeli xesha leeholide zekrisimesi.

src: hlala ucaphele ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi bese ulandzela nati tindlela tekutivikela: uma uyovakasha, cinisekisa kutsi onkhe emafasitelo netivalo tendlu yakho tikhiyiwe.
tgt: hlala ubaze amahle ngawo onke amaxesha uze uthathe la manyathelo okhuselo alandelayo: xa uhamba usiya kuchitha iholide yakho qinisekisa ukuba iifestile zivaliwe neengca ngo zekhaya lakho zi tshixiwe ukuba omnye waba mmelwane bakho uza kuba ekhona, mcele ukuba abeke iliso kwindlu yakho.

src: uma munye kubomakhelwane bakho atawubakhona, mcele akubukele indlu yakho.
tgt: ngeli xesha ukwiholide, zigcine endaweni efihlakeleyo izinto zakho ezibalulekileyo ezifana neminxeba yeselula nezipaji.

src: ngalesikhatsi uvaka shile, cinisekisa kutsi tintfo letibalulekile letinjengabomakhalekhikhini netikhwama temali atikho emehlwe ni ebantfu.
tgt: yigcine uyitshixile imo to yakho xa uyishiya nokuba lixesha elingakanani na.

src: imoto yakho ayihlale ikhiyiwe uma uyishiya ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi.
tgt: zama uku livula icango ngoku sele litshixiwe ukuqinisekisa ukuba litshixiwe ngenene.

src: sebentisa imali ngebuhlakani allison cooper sikhatsi semaholide akhisimusi akufuneki sishiye kuvuleke u mgodzi wetikweleti.
tgt: yisebenzise ngobunono imali kule krisimesi allison cooper ixesha leeholide zekri simesi akufanelekanga ukuba likushiye use matyaleni.

src: "kusebentisa imali ngalo kwendlulele kufana nesi kweleti lesikukhatsatako le siviwa nguwe wedvwa.
tgt: "ukusebenzisa imali ngokugqithisileyo kuku faka ematyaleni ubonoku waphepha.

src: ku ncono kakhulu kugwema kusebentisa imali ngalokwe ndlulele kulokhisimusi ngo ba kungaba nemtselela lo mkhulu emalini yakho isikhatsi lesidze," kwasho umphatsi wetekutsenga nekutsengisa wedebtsafe ma tthys potgieter.
tgt: kungcono ukuba uyisebenzise ngobunono i mali ngeli xesha leeholide ze krisimesi kuba ukuba awenzi njalo ungazibona unengxaki yemali oku kuchaphazele nezicwangciso zakho," utshilo umlawuli wezentengiso wakwadebtsafe umatthys potgieter.

src: "bumnandzi bekusebenti sa imali ngalokwendlulele ngelweti nangengongoni yintfo yesikhashana letawe nta batsengi badvonse mati ma ngenca yetincumo leba ngakaticabangisisi labati tsetse ngasekupheleni kwa bhimbidvwane 2019. ungase bentisi imali longenayo," kwangeta potgieter.
tgt: "oba bumnandi bokuyitya imali ngenyanga yenkanga neyomnga bobethutyana nje elifutshane futhi abantu baza kubuva ekupheleni kweyo mqungu yowama2019 ubu nzima bokungasebenzisi ima li ngobunono.

src: mellony ramalho weafri can bank watsi tisebenti ti vamise kuholelwa ngembi kwesikhatsi ngengongoni, lokwenta sikhatsi sekulindza kuhola ngabhimbidvwane sibe sidze.
tgt: musa ukuzifa ka ematyaleni ongenayo ima li yokuwahlawula," wongeze watsho upotgieter.

src: "bhimbidvwane yinyanga lematima ebantfwini labani ngi, labanye bagcina base bentisa emacredit card noma baboleke imali.
tgt: umellony ramalho waseafrican bank uthi abasebenzi bayifumana ngaphambi kwexesha imivuzo yabo kwinyanga yomnga, into ke leyo eyenza ukuba libe lide ixesha lokulindela imivuzo yabo yenyanga yomqungu.

src: potgieter ucwayisa batse ngi kutsi bacale kutsenga tintfo tangengongoni kusanesikhatsi futsi bacinisekise kutsi banekudla lokwanele futsi banetinhlobo teku dla letitawuhlala sikhatsi lesidze, kute bakhone kulawula indlela lebayise bentisa ngayo imali yabo nekugwema kutsenga sekute sikhatsi tintfo setibita kakhulu.
tgt: "inyanga yomqungu yi nyanga enzima kubantu abaninzi, apho abanye ba ncama babhenele kumakhadi wetyala abizwa icredit card okanye ekubolekeni imali.

src: potgieter wecwayise batsengi nganati tindlela labangayonga ngato imali: batsenge kudla lokuningi lokutawuhlala sikhatsi lesidze.
tgt: upotgieter ucebisa abantu ukuba bakuqalise kwange thuba ukuthenga izinto ze krisimesi kwaye bazithenge ngezixa zonke iintlobo zo kutya abakusebenzisayo futhi bakhethe ezi iintlobo zihlala ixesha elide, ukuze baqinisekisa ukuba abagqithi kwimali ebebeyibekele ukuthenga ngayo ukutya futhi abaziboni sele besengxakini yokuthenga izinto ngemizuzu yokugqibela sele zibiza kakhulu.

src: babuke kutsi angeke bagibelisane emotweni leyodvwa.
tgt: indlela upotgieter abacebisa ngayo abathengi ngeendlela zokungasebenzisi mali ngokugqithisileyo: thenga ukutya ngezixa futhi ukhethe iintlobo zokutya ezihlala ixesha elide lisebenzise icebo loku khwelisana nabanye abantu emotweni.

src: kusebentisa timoto letimbalwa kusho kutsi kutawusebenta imali lencane kuphethilomu.
tgt: ukusebenzisa iimoto ezimbalwa kuthetha ukusebenzisa amafutha ezithuthi ama ncinci nemali encinci.

src: gwema kusebentisa imi gwaco lekhokhelwako uma kukhonakala.
tgt: ziphephe iindlela ezihlawulelwayo ukuba unayo indlela endaweni yokuthenga izipho into onokuyenza ungasuke ucele abantwana ukuba babhakele izihlobo zakho ngokwabo izibiliboco namaqebe ngwana amnandi.

src: bantfwana abasebentise tintfo labatisungulele tona kwenta tipho tetihlobo kunekutsi titsengwe.
tgt: zithenge kusengethuba izinto zekrisimesi.

src: kuphela kwemshado ngekwemtsetfo dale hes nasewulinge konkhe longakwenta kutsi umshado wakho uphumelele, idivosi kungaba yintfo lencono kini nobabili wena nemlingani wakho.
tgt: uqhawulomtshato ngokusemthethweni dale hes xa sele uzame yonke into ukwenza ukubaumtshato wakho usebenze, uqhawulomtshato lungayeyona nto ingcono kuni nobabini nomlingane wakho.

src: idivosi ilukhuni futsi ibanga sitresi emindenini kantsi futsi nenchubo yetemtsetfo ingakudida.
tgt: uqhawulomtshato lunzima kwaye luyadakumbisa kwii ntsapho zibe nazo iinkqubo zomthetho ziyenza ingqondo iphixane.

src: idivosi ngulesikhatsi umshado uphela ngekwemtsetfo enkantolo yemtsetfo.
tgt: uqhawulomtshato kuxaumtshato uqhawulwe ngokusesikweni enkundleni yezomthetho.

src: kunetinhlobo letimbili tedivosi: lengaphikiswa – lapho khonaomabili emacembu avumelana kutsi idivosi ku fanele kutsi yenteke; futsi ingaphikiswa – lapho khona emacembu angavumelani ngaledivosi nome ngemibandzela yayo.
tgt: kukho iindidi ezim bini zoqhawulomtshato: olun gaphikiswanga – apho bobabini abalingane bavumelanayo ukuba uqhawulomtshato kufanele luqhubeke; noluphikiswayo – apho abalingane bangavumelaniyo ngoqhawulomtshato olo okanye bangavumelaniyo ngemiqathango yalo.

src: josephine peta, sisebenti lesikhulu sekuphatfwa kwemtsetfo ehhovisi lemmeli wemndeni etikweni letebulungiswa nekutfutfukiswa kwemtsetfosisekelo, uchaza kutsi inchubo yedivosi icala ngesikhatsi kukhishwa emasamanisi.
tgt: ujosephine peta, noligosa lolawulo lezomthetho eliphezulu kwiofisi yegqwetha lejaji elijongene nemiba yeentsapho yesebe lezobulungisa nophuhliso lomgaqosiseko, ucacisa ukuba uqhawulomtshato luqala xa kukhutshwe iisamani.

src: "umuntfu lofuna kutsi umshado wabo uphele angatfola emasamanisi edivosi enkantolo lephakeme nome yesifundza, nome bangabona na nemmeli kutsi abasite kulenchubo.
tgt: "umntu ofuna ukuba umtshato wabo uqhawulwe angafuma na iisamani zoqhawulomtshato kwinkundla ephakamileyo okanye kweyenqila, okanye unokuya kwigqwetha ukuba limncede kulo nkqubo.

src: lowo locala inchubo yedivosi emkhatsini walabo labashadile ubitwa ngekutsi ngummangali bese kutsi lolomunye yena ubitwa ngekutsingummangalelwa," kwasho yena njalo peta.
tgt: lo mlingane ufaka isicelo sokuqala inkqubo yoqhawulomtshato ubizwa ngokuba ngummangali aze omnye umlingane abizwe ummangalelwa," utshilo upeta.

src: peta uchaze kutsi emasamanisi edivosi kufanele: asho kutsi sekute lelinye litfuba lekubuyisela lobudlelwane esimeni lesifanele, ente kutsi kube nekwehlukaniswa kwemphahla labanayo labayihlanganyelako nome kufezekiswe imibandzela lekwa vunyelanwa ngayo ngesikhatsi kusayinwa lesivumelwane semshado ekucaleni kwalomshado, kanye, nekuchaza kutsi ngumaphi emalu ngiselelo lentelwe bantfwana balaba labashadene, njengekutsi nje umntfwana utawuhlala nabani.
tgt: upeta ucacise ukuba iisamani zoqhawulomtshato kufuneka: zichaze ukuba akukho themba lokuba ungaze uphinde ulungiseke lo mtshato, zilungiselele ukohlulwa kwempahla ekuditye nweyo ngayo okanye unyanzeliso lwemimiselo ekuvunyelwene ngayo kw isivumelwano somtshato esatyikitywa ekuqalweni kwalo mtshato, zize zicacise ukuba ngawaphi amalungiselelo aza kwenziwa ngabantwana besi sibini, afana nokuba abantwana baza kuhlala kubani.

src: "lamasamanisi kufanele kutsi aphindze futsi asho kutsi ummangalelwa unetinsuku leti10 – nangabe ahlala endzaweni yinye nemmangali, nome tinsuku letinge20 – nangabe lamacembu ahlala etifundzeni letahlukene, kute aphendvule lamasamanisi," kwengeta peta.
tgt: "iisamami kwakhona kufuneka zichaze ukuba lowoungummangalelwa uneentsuku ezi10 zokuphendula iisamani – kwimeko apho bahlala khona kummandla omnye kunye nommangali, okanye iintsuku ezingama20 – ukuba bahlala kumaphondo awohlukeneyo," wongeze watsho upeta.

src: nangabe licala selivuliwe, emadokhumenti atfunyelwa emuva kummangali, lokunguye lotsatsa emasethi lamabili alamadokhumenti ayowanika mabhalane wenkantolo yemajaji wakuleyo ndzawo ummangalelwa lasebenta kuyo nome lahlala kuyo.
tgt: xa sele livuliwe ityala, amaxwebhu abuyiselwa kummangali, ekufanele eyokuwanikezela kunothimba wendawo ahlala okanye asebenza kuyo ummangalelwa.

src: "mabhalane wenkantolo yemajaji utawubeseke yena utsatsa lawo madokhumenti ayowanika ummangalelwa matfupha bese sewukhipha sicisekiso lesibhalwe kutsi uwentile lowo msebenti, kufakazela kutsi vele lawo madokhumenti wanikwa wona.
tgt: "ngoko ke unothimba uza kusa la amaxwebhu kummangalelwa buqu aze akhuphe isiqinisekiso sokuba uwahambi sile, ukuqinisekisa ukuba amaxwebhu asiwe.

src: nangabe kunebantfwana, lihhovisi lemmeli wemndeni kufanele kutsi latiswe," kwaphawula yena njalo peta.
tgt: kwimeko apho kuchaphazeleka khona abantwana, iofisi yegqwetha lejaji elijongene nemiba yeentsapho kufuneka yazisiwe," uphawule watsho upeta.

src: emva kwetinsuku leti10 nome letinge20, mabhalane wenkantolo yemajaji angayibhalisa ledivosi kuluhlu lwemacala enkantolo.
tgt: emva kwexesha leentsuku ezi10 okanye ezingama20, ummangali angalubhalisa uqhawulomtshato kumqu lu wamatyala enkundla.

src: kumadivosi laphikiswako, ummangalelwa kufanele kutsi awaphendvule lamasamanisi ngekutsi afake satiso senhloso yekutivikela kuloludzaba.
tgt: kuqhawulomtshato oluphikiswayo, ummangalelwa kufuneka ephendule iisamani ngokufaka isaziso senjongo yokuphikisa uqhawulomtshato olo.

src: "nangabe asakwenti le loko, kufanele kutsi aphindze futsi afake sicelo sekutiphendvulela kungakapheli sikhatsi lesitsite.
tgt: "xa sele kwenzekile konke oko, kukwafuneka efake impendulo ayakuzithethelela ngayo phakathi kwexesha elicacisiwe.

src: sicelo sekutiphendvulela sitatimende lapho ummangalelwa aphendvula khona letinsolo labekwa tona letikulamasamanisi.
tgt: le mpendulo yinkcazelo apho ummangalelwa aphendula kuyo izityholo ezikwiisamani.

src: emva kwalesicelo sekutiphendvulela, ummangali angaphindza futsi asiphendvule lesicelo sekutiphendvulela nome afake satiso sekutsi kuhlalwe phasi kulalelwe lelicala.
tgt: emva kokuba ifakiwe lo mpendulo, ummangali naye usenokuyiphendula lo mpendulo okanye afake isaziso sokumisela umhla wokuxoxa.

src: "loludzaba lutawubeseke selubekelwa lusuku kutsi litekwe," kwephetsa peta njalo.
tgt: "ke ngoku ityala liya kumiselwa umhla wokuxoxa," uqukumbele watsho upeta.

src: vyini idivosi lengakaphendvul wa?
tgt: vyintoni uqhawu lomtshato oluzen zekelayo?

src: inkantolo iyayikhipha idivosi ngobe kungakaphendvulwa nangabe emasamanisi akhishiwe atfunyelwa kulowo lekushadwe naye kodvwa wangawaphendvuli ngesikhatsi lesincunyiwe.
tgt: inkundla iyakunikezela ngoqhawulomtshato oluzenzekelayo ukuba iisamani bezinikezelwe kumlingane aze ke angaphenduli phakathi kwexesha elimiselweyo.

src: kukhulelwa kweekhthophikhi kusimo setemphilo lesibucayi allison cooper bomake labahla ngabetane ne kukhulelwa kweekhthophikhi babati kahle buhlungu benhlitiyo lobubangwa kukhulelwa kweekhthophikhi, ngenca yemiphumela yeluhlolo lwemchamo nelwengati lekhomba kutsi ukhulelwe.
tgt: ukukhulelwa okwenzeka ngaphandle kwesibeleko yingozi edinga inkathalelo yezempilo kaxakeka allison cooper abantu basetyhi ni abaye bafuma na ukukhulelwa okwenzeka ngaphandle kwesibeleko babazi kakuhle ubuhlungu bentliziyo obubangelwa koku, ngenxa yeziphumo ezithembisayo ezingqina ukuba bakhulelwe kuvavanyo lomchamo nolwegazi.

src: bushy mhlari, loyisenior registrar ectopic obstetrics and gynaecology edr george mukhari academichospital, lowachaza watsi kukhulelwa kweekhthophikhi akwentekanga esikhaleni sesibeletfo, lapho khona kukhulelwa kuvamise kwenteka khona.
tgt: ngokutsho kukagqr bushy mhlari, oyisenior registrar kwicandelo leectopic ob stetrics and gynaecology edr george mukhari academic hospital , ochaze ukuba ukukhulelwa ngaphandle kwesibeleko kukukhulelwa okwenzeke ngaphandle komngxuma wesibeleko.

src: watsi ngalokwetayelekile, emva kwekutsi sidvodza sihlangene nelicandza lokwenteka ngekhatsi emashubhini efallopian , licandza leselilumbene nesidvodza lihamba eshubhini liye esikhaleni lesinotsile sesibeletfo lapho khona lichumeka kumkhakha weendometrial bese umntfwana ucala kubakhona .
tgt: uye wathi ngokuqhelekileyo, emva kokuchunyiswa kweqanda yimbewu yobudoda – okuthi kwenzeke ngaphakathi kwemibhobho yesibeleko, iqanda elichunyisiweyo lihamba ngombobho liyokutsho ngaphakathi kumngxuma wesibeleko apho lincamathela khona kwinwebu engaphakathi esibelekweni, aze emva koko umntwana akhule.

src: "ekukhulelweni kweekhthophikhi, licandza lelilumbene nesidvodza lihlala ngalesingasetulu kwaleminye yemikhakha yesitfo.
tgt: "ekukhulelweni okwenzeka ngaphandle kwesibeleko, iqanda elichunyisiweyo lihlala kwezinye iindawo zomzimba.

src: etimeni letima 98%, indzawo kukhulelwa kweekhthophikhi lekwenteka kuyo kusemashubhini efallopian .
tgt: kwiziganeko ezingama98%, olu hlobo lokukhulelwa lwenzeka kwimibhobho yesibeleko.

src: tindzawo letingakavami tifaka ekhatsi iovari,emaphayiphi esibeletfo nakumsipha lobanti," kwasho dkt.
tgt: iindawo ezingaqhelekanga ziquka indawo esisiyilelomaqanda emzimbeni, emazantsi esisu, emlonyeni wesibeleko nakwisiqwanga esingaphandle kwesibeleko," utshilo ugqr mhlari.

src: uma loku kwenteka, umbungu angeke ususwe uyiswe lapho ufanele khona kantsi kucedza lokukhulelwa ngiyo kuphela indlela lesele lekufanele ikhetfwe ngumake.
tgt: xa oku kusenzeka, isihluma sembewu asinakumiliselwa kwenye indawo, into enokwenziwa inye kuphela kukuba sikhutshwe isisu eso.

src: mhlari watsi make unelitfuba lelikhulu lekukhulelwa kweekhthophikhi uma; anemafallopian tubes lamoshakele noma langa katayeleki, labangwe kutseleleka kwakudzala ngetifo temacansi noma ake wahlindvwa emashubhu; wase wakhulelwa ngeekhthophikhi ngaphambilini; angakhoni kutfola bantfwana; anebalingani betemacansi labanengi; abhema ligwayi.
tgt: ugqr mhlari uthe umntu wasetyhini unamathuba amaninzi okufumana ingxa ki yokukhulelwa okwenzeka ngaphandle kwesibeleko ukuba; unemibhobho yesibeleko eyonakeleyo okanye engaqhelekanga, enokususela kukuba wakhe wanesifo okanye usuleleko lwesifo kule mibhobho alufumene ngokwabelana ngesondo okanye ngotyando kwimibhobho; wakhe wanayo ingxa ki yokukhulelwa okwe nzeke ngaphandle kwesibeleko ngaphambili; akanayo inzala; unamaqabane okwabelana ngesondo amaninzi; utshaya imidiza.

src: "kukhulelwa kweekhthophikhi kusimo lesibeka imphilo engotini futsi kuyintfo leyimbangela lenkhulu yekushona kwabomake uma babeleka etinyangeni tekucala letintsatfu tekukhulelwa.
tgt: "ukugqabhuka kwale nwebu yambethise isihluma sembewu xa umntu enengxaki yokukhulelwa ngaphandle kwesibeleko kungambulala kwaye kungunobangela ophambili wokusweleka koomama abakhulelweyo kwiinyanga ezintathu zokuqala bekhulelwe.

src: sigameko sekukhulelwa kweekhthophikhi silinganiselwa kumaphesenti lamabili abo bonkhe bantfu," kwasho mhlari.
tgt: izehlo zokukhulelwa okwenzeka ngaphandle kwesibeleko zimalunga ne2%," utshilo ugqr mhlari.

src: timphawu tekukhulelwa kweekhthophikhingekusho kwa dkt.
tgt: iimpawu zokukhulelwa okwenzeka ngaphandle kwesibelekongokukagqr mhlari, iimpawu zibonakala kwangoko xa ukhulelwe.

src: mhlari, timphawu tivela masinyane uma kukhulelwa kucala.
tgt: ngamanye amaxesha, nangaphambi kokuba umntu wasetyhini aziqonde ukuba ukhulelwe.

src: timphawu letivamile tifaka ekhatsi: buhlungu besinye, kweciwa sikhatsi sabomake kopha esitfweni sabomake sangasese.
tgt: iimpawu eziqhelekileyo ziquka; iintlungu zamazantsi esisu, ukuphosakala kwexesha lokuya exesheni; ukopha kwilungu lobufazi.

src: "kodvwake, labanye bomake ababi netimphawu bate babone ngekudzabuka kwemashubhu efallopian .
tgt: "nangona kunjalo, abanye abantu basetyhini ababinazo iimpawu kude kugqabhuke imibhobho yesibeleko.

src: uma loku kwenteka, make angahlangabetana netinhlungu letinkhulu futsi labanye bangopha esitfweni sabo sangasese.
tgt: xa oku kusenzeka, umntu wasetyhini unokuva iintlungu eziqatseleyo kwaye abanye basenokopha kwilungu lobufazi.

src: loku kungalandzelwa kuba nesiyeti, kwehla kwemfutfo wengati, kuculeka, kushaceka nekufa uma kwelashwa kungaphutfunyiswa," washo njalo.
tgt: oku kulandelwa sisiyezi, ukuhla koxinzelelo lwegazi, ukufa isiqaqa, ukothuka kunye nokufa ukuba unyango lulibazisekile," utshilo.

src: "uma kucilonga kukhulelwa kweekhthophikhi, kwentiwa luhlolo lwengati noma lwemchamo kucinisekisa kutsi make ukhulelwe.
tgt: ukuze uxilongo luyiveze le ngxaki yokukhulelwa okwenzeka ngaphandle kwesibeleko kufuneka kwenziwe uvavanyo lokukhulelwa lwegazi okanye olomchamo ukungqina ukuba umntu wasetyhini ukhulelwe kusini na.

src: kwakha sive lesinakekela bantfwana vukuzenzele unnamed kunesaga lesivamile kumasiko lamanengi aseafrika lesitsi kungumsebenti wesigodzi sonkhe kukhulisa umntfwana.
tgt: ukwakha isizwe esikha thalele abantwana vukuzenzele unnamed kukho isaci esiqhe lekileyo kwizizwe zamaafrika ezininzi esithi umntwa na ukhuliswa aqeqeshwe sisizwe.

src: lomcondvo lona – wekutsi wonkhe ummango unemsebenti wekukhulisa, kunakekela nekuvikela umntfwana ngamunye – ufika emcondvweni wami uma ngicabanga ngelusizi nangekufa lokucasulanako kwaenock mpianzi lonemimnyaka le13 enkanjini yesikolo lesandza kubanjwa.
tgt: olu luvo – lokuba isizwe ngokubanzi sinoxanduva lokukhulisa, intlalontle kunye nokhuseleko lomntwana ngamnye – luza engqondweni yam xa ndicinga ngokusweleka kabuhlungu nakalusizi kukaenock mpianzi oneminyaka eli13 kutshanje ngethuba bekukhenketho lwesikolo.

src: lokudzabukisako kutsi, enock akusuye kuphela umntfwana lolahlekelwe yimphilo yakhe ngetizatfu lebetingavikelwa ngalokuphelele, kuphela nje uma ngabe bantfu labadzala bebente umsebenti wabo wekunakekela.
tgt: okubuhlungu kukuba uenock akukuphela komntwana ophulukene nobomi bakhe ngenxa yezinto ebezinokuthi ntelwa, ukuba nje abantu abada la bebeziqhelanise nokukhatha la nokuthatha uxanduva.

src: lomunye umuntfu angacabanga ngalomunye loneminyaka le13, keamohetswe shaun seboko, losandza kushonela echibini lekubhukusha lasesikolweni semabanga laphansi imagalie sburg, nalabantfwana lababili labashonele elekgolo primary school elimpopo ngesikhatsi iloli ishayisa lubondza lwabese luwela etukwabo.
tgt: le nto inditsho ndacinga ngomnye umntwana naye oneminyaka eli13, ukeamohetswe shaun seboko, osandula ukutshona kwidama lokuquba kwisikolo samabanga aphantsi emaga liesburg, nabanye abantwana ababini abasweleke kwisikolo ilekgolo primary elimpopo xa iloli ithe yatshayisa udonga lwabawela.

src: lomunye umuntfu futsi angacabanga ngalabanye bantfwana labanengi, labanjenganathilia pienaar, loneminyaka le6, labashona uma kudubulana emacembu emagenge asecape flats.
tgt: le ntlungu inditsho ndacinga ngabanye abantwana abaninzi, abafana nonathlia pienaar oneminyaka emi6 ubudala, owabulawa kwimfazwe yemigulukudu eyayidubulana kummandla wecape flats.

src: sikhumbula futsi lusizi lwekushona kwabomichael komape nalumka mthethwa, bobabili bashona ngekugcumukela emthoyi wemgodzi.
tgt: sikhumbula kwakhona uku sweleka kabuhlungu kukami chael komape kunye nolumka mkethwa, bobabini basweleka emva kokuba betshone kwi mingxuma yezindlu zangasese ezingagungxulwayo.

src: tonkhe letimphilo tebantfu labasha, netimphilo talabanye labanengi, bekungadzingeki kutsi tilahleke.
tgt: bonke abo bantwana, kunye nabanye abaninzi, bekungafunekanga ukuba baphulukene nobomi babo.

src: tonkhe leti nhlekelele betingavikelwa uma ngabe bekutsetfwe tinyatselo tekuvikela labantfwana kutimo letinebungoti.
tgt: zonke ezi ntlekele bezinako ukuthintelwa ukuba bekuthatyathwe amanyathelo okubagcina aba bantwana bekhuselekile.

src: kimi kubukekasengatsi, singummango, siyehluleka kunakekela bantfwana betfu.
tgt: apha kum kuyacaca ukuba, njengesizwe, siyasilela ekudlaleni indima yethu kuba ntwana bethu.

src: bantfwana labanengi kakhulu batitfola basetimeni letiyingoti, kungaba sihlenge semapula ngo/setingondvo lesakhi we ngetandla lesisemfuleni noma kubashiya babodvwa emkhukhwini nesibane saphala fini.
tgt: uninzi lwabantwana lu zifumana lukwiimeko ezi nobungozi.

src: uma bosonkontileka bashi ya imigodzi ingakavikeleki noma kunganakekeli sakhiwonchanti esikolweni noma kugcwalisa ngalokwendlulele tigitjelwa letiya esikolweni, timphilo tebantfwana tibekwa engotini.
tgt: ezinye zezo meko zifana nokubulawa nguzenzele wephenyane emlanjeni okanye basutywe kukufa kuba beshiyeke bodwa kwityotyombe elinesibane separafini.

src: kodvwa kukhona lokwe ntwako lokungetulu kweku nganakekeli kanye nekunganaki.
tgt: xa iinkampani ezakhayo zishiya imisele eziyigrumbileyo ingagqunywanga okanye izakhiwo zesikolo zinga gcinwanga kakuhle okanye izithuthi zabantwana zigcwele kakhulu, ubomi babantwana bubekwa ebungozini.

src: bantfwana labanengi bahlanga betana nalabo lababahlukume ta ngekwemacansi, emagenge etigebengu nalabo labatsengisa tidzakwamiva ngenca yekutsi bahlaseleka kalula.
tgt: kodwa ayikokungakha thali nokungahoyi kuphela okubangela le ngxaki.

src: singu mmango, kufuneka sikhulise buhlakani nekukhutsala kwetfu kuvikela bantfwana betfu kuloku nakuletinye tintfo letiyingoti.
tgt: uninzi lwabantwana lusemngciphe kweni wabantu ababaxhaphaza ngezesondo, amaqela emigulukudu kunye nabathengisi beziyobisi kanye kuba besaziwa ukuba ngabantwana abanokwenziwa izisulu lula.

src: singummango, kufanele sibe nelisiko lekuba nesibopho.
tgt: njengesizwe, kufuneka sihlale sibaze amehlo kwaye siwumele ngeenyawo umba wokukhusela abantwana bethu kwiingozi ezifana nezi.

src: kufuneka kutsi sibe nesibopho kitsi ngekwetfu, kubantfwana betfu nakulabanye.
tgt: kufuneka sizikhathalele thina, abantwana bethu kunye nabanye abantu.

src: njengoba kufuneka sicinisekise kutsi bantfwana bayakhona kukhula kusimondzawo lesiphephile, lesinakekelako nalesivuselelanako, ngakoke kufuneka sitive sinemsebenti wekuvikela nekunakekela bonkhe labo lesibatiko nalesitsantsana nabo.
tgt: njengoko kufuneka siqinisekise ukuba abantwana bethu bakhulela kwindawo ekhuselekileyo, efudumeleyo nehlaziyayo, ngokunjalo ke kufuneka sizive sinoxanduba lokukhusela nokukhathalela bonke abo sibaziyo nesinxibelelana nabo.

src: kufuneka siwuve lomsebenti wekunakekela emigwacweni.
tgt: kufuneka siwuve lo msebenzi wokukhathalela endle leni.

src: nanoma sikwemukela lokwehla kwelizinga letingoti temgwaco ngalesikhatsi semaholide, liciniso lelingatsandzeki litsi bantfu labangetulu kwe1,600 bafile emigwacweni yetfu esikhatsini lesiyinyanga nesigamu.
tgt: nangona zichulumancisa iindaba zokwehla kwenani labantu abasweleke kwiingozi zendlela kwezi holide zehlobo, intlungu embi yeyokuba bangaphezu kwe1,600 abantu abasweleke ezindleleni kwisithuba nje esiyinyanga enesiqingatha.

src: ku yaphatamisa kuva kutsi ba shayeli labangetulu kwe9,000 baboshwelwe emacala lafaka ekhatsi kushayela badzakiwe, kugijimisa nekushayela budla bha nekushayela ngekungana ki.
tgt: iyadanisa into yokuba abaqhubi zimoto abangama9,000 babanjelwe amatyala aquka ukuqhuba phantsi kweempembelelo zotywala, ukuqhuba ngesa ntya esiphezulu, nokuqhuba kakubi nangokungakhathali.

src: lisiko lekuba nesibopho lisho kutsi kufuneka sonkhe sishayele ngalokuphephile futsi sihloniphe emalungelo alabahamba ngetinyawo nalabanye basebentisi bemgwaco.
tgt: ukuthatha uxanduva kuthetha ukuba kufuneka sonke siqhube ngenkathalo futhi sihloniphe amalungelo abahambi ngee nyawo nabanye abasebenzisi bendlela.

src: bomake labanyenti bakhulisa bantfwana babodvwana, lokubeseke ku khinyabeta kutitfutfukisa kwabo nekwebantfwana babo.
tgt: ukuthatha uxanduva kuthetha ukuba ootata kufuneka babekhona ebomini baba ntwana babo.

src: lisiko lekuba nesibopho lisho kutsi bobabe kufuneka babe khona etimphilweni teba ntfwana babo.
tgt: maninzi amanina ekufuneka ezikhulisele aba ntwana babo bodwa, into leyo inciphisa amathuba abo kunye nawabantwana babo okuphumelela ebomini.

src: bomake labane ngi kakhulu kudzingeke kutsi bakhulise bantfwana babodvwa, lokuvamise kunciphisa litsemba labo nalelo lebantfwana babo.
tgt: ukuthatha uxanduva kuthetha nokuba kufuneka sizikhusele kwezesondo futhi singabezibeki thina okanye abanye esiche ngeni sokosulelwa yihiv .

src: lisiko lekuba nesibopho futsi lisho kutsi kufuneka sisebentise tindlela letiphephile tekuya eca nsini, singativuleli kutsi singen we noma sesulele labanye ngehiv .
tgt: kufu neka singaseli utywala kakhulu okanye sisebenzise iziyobisi.

src: akufuneki sinatse tjwala noma sisebentise tidzakamiva budlabha.
tgt: kufuneka sifune ukuphila ubomi obusempilweni ukwenzela ukuba siziphephe izifo ezinoku thintelwa kwaye siphile ubomi obude.

src: kufuneka sifune kuphila imphilo lenemphilo kute sivikele tifo levikelekako bese siphila imphilo lendze.
tgt: le ndlela yokuziphatha kufuneka ilandelwe ngokukodwa ngabo bonke abantu abaphe theyo kwizikhundla zegunya nabahlonitshwayo luluntu, nokuba zinkokeli zezenkolo okanye oosopolitiki, iinkokeli zemveli okanye oosaziwayo.

src: lisiko lelinjena kufuneka lemukelwe lichutjwe kakhulu ngulabo labasetikhundleni letisetulu emmangweni naletine mtselela ebantfwini, kungaba baholi betenkholo noma bosopoliti ki, baholi bendzabuko noma bo satiwako.
tgt: ngokusebenzisa nje amazwi nezenzo zabo, kufuneka bancedise kumalinge okwakha isizwe esingcono apho wonke umntu exatyisiwe kwaye ekhathalelwe.

src: ngemagama netento tabo, kufuneka bafune kwakha ummango loncono lapho khona wonkhe umuntfu atawubongwa khona futsi anakekelwe.
tgt: amagosa onyuliweyo kunye nabasebenzi bakarhulumente baphathiswe uxandauva lokuqinisekia ukhuseleko nentlalontle yabemi.

src: bantfu labakhetsiwe netisebe nti tahulumende baniketwe u msebenti wekucinisekisa kuphe pha nenhlalakahle yawonkhe umuntfu.
tgt: kufuneka aqinisekise ukuba kukho izakhiwo ezaneleyo nezikhuselekileyo ezikolweni.

src: kufuneka bacinise kise kutsi kunesakhiwonchanti lesanele nalesiphephile kuto tonkhe tikolo.
tgt: kufuneka ashukume ngokukhawuleza xa kukho uphazamiseko lwamanzi ekuhlaleni okanye xa kuchazwe izibane zesitalato ezonakeleyo.

src: kufuneka baphakame bente masinyane uma kunekuphatamiseka kwekuphakelwa kwemanti emimangweni noma uma kuletfwe umbiko ngekungasebenti kwemalambu asemgwacweni.
tgt: kufuneka baqinisekise ukuba kunya nzeliswa imigaqo yezempilo nezokhuseleko futhi nokuba umthetho awophulwa.

src: kufuneka bacinisekise kutsi imigomo yetemphilo neyekuphepha iyasetjentiswa nekutsi umtsetfo uyalandzelwa.
tgt: ukongeza kumsebenzi oqhubekayo owenzeka kurhulumente wonke, kuwo onke amanqanaba, ukuzalisekisa olu xanduva, ngamanye amaxesha kuye kufuneke sithathe ama yathelo angaqhelekanga.

src: kwengeta, kulomsebenti lochubekako kuye wonkhe hulumende, onkhe emazinga, kute kutsi lesibopho sisebente, ngalesinye sikhatsi kwadzingeka kutsi sitsatse tinyatselo letendlulele.
tgt: ukuphendula ekufeni nasekonzakaleni okubangelwa kukutshona kwabantwana emingxunyeni yezindlu za ngasese ezingagungxulwayo, sisungule iphulo lesafe lokukhawulezisa ukwakhiwa kwezindlu zangasese ezifane lekileyo kuzo zonke izikolo elizweni.

src: kuphendvula kulokufa nekulimala lokubangwe kugcumukela kwebantfwana emithoyi yemigodzi, sisungule umklamo wesafe kute siphutfumise kuniketwa kwemithoyi lefanelekile kuto tonkhe tikolo kulelive letfu.
tgt: sathumela umkhosi wokhuselo wesizwe wasemzantsi afrika kwiindawo ezithile ekapa ukuxhasa amapolisa kwiinzame zawo zokunciphisa ubundlobongela.

src: sitfumele umbutfo avelonkhe weteku vikela waseningizimu afrika kuletinye tincenye tasekapa kute usekele emaphoyisa kumitamo yawo yekunciphisa budlova bemagenge.
tgt: kutshanje, thina, kunye nemibutho yoluntu, siqalise isicwangciso sokulwa ubu ndlobongela obenziwa ku manina nabantwana.

src: muva nje, sihla ngene, netinhlangano temma ngo, sicale luhlelo lwekuphe ndvula masinyane lwekucedza budlova lobubhekiswe kubomake nakubantfwana.
tgt: nangona kunjalo, kuninzi ekufuneka sikwenzile, nje gorhulumente nanjengesizwe.

src: kungunyalo, kuyacaca kutsi kusesekunyenti lokufuneka kutsi sikwente, singuhulumende nemmango.
tgt: sibaqhwabela izandla abo bantu kunye nemibutho ethe yaluthathela kulo uxanduva lokukhathalela impilo yabanye.

src: sihalalisela labo bantfu netinhlangano letente kwaba ngumsebenti wato kunakekela labanye bantfu.
tgt: kukho aba ntu abafana noralph bou wers kunye nomark nicho lson, abaququzelela imidlalo yokuzonwabisa yabantu abasebatsha elavender hills ekapa ukuze bangaguquki babe yimigulukudu.

src: kunebantfu labafana naralph bouwers namark nicholson, labahlela imidlalo yetekukhibika yebantfu labasha baselavender hill ekapa kubavikela kutsi bangangeneli emacembu emagengi.
tgt: kukho oomama, oodade kunye neentombi abasebenza njengamavolontiya angabafundi kwioperation bobbi bear, umbutho oseamanzimtoti kwazulunatal ofunela aba ntwana abancinci abangama xhoba okuxhatshazwa iindawo zokuhlala.

src: kunabomake, bosisi nemadvodzakati labasebenta njengetitjudeni letivolontiyako kumklamo weoperation bobbi bear, lekuyinhlangano yasemanzimtoti kwazulu natal leniketa indzawo yekuhlala bantfwana labancane labahlukunyetiwe.
tgt: kukho amaqela amaninzi ezenkolo afana nesouthern african catholic bishop’s conference, endisandula ukudibana nawo andixelele malunga nomsebenzi awe nzayo ukujongana neemfuno zabantu abahluphekileyo, ukuxhasa iintsapho ukuba zikhathale kwaye zikhulise kwaye zincede abantu abasebatsha ukuba bahlangabezane nemingeni emininzi abajo ngene nayo.

src: kunetinhlangano letinengi tetenkholo letifana nenhlangano yebabhishobhi basekatholika yaseafrika lengaseningizimu, lengisandza kuhlangena nabo labangitjele ngemsebenti labawentako kuphendvula kuletidzingo talabaphuyile, kwese kela imindeni kute ikhulise lizinga lekunakekela nekusingatsa nekuncedza bantfu labasha kutsi babukane netinseyeya letinengi lababukene nato.
tgt: aba bemi basemzantsi afrika basibonisa indlela.

src: labantfu laba baseningizimu afrika basikhomba indlela.
tgt: ngemizekelo yabo, baya sikhumbuza ukuba kuthetha ukuthini ukuzithathela uxa nduva thina buqu nokuluboni sa nakwabanye.

src: imininingwane lephelele lemayelana neadhd neadd silusapho nyanda kunelusito lolukhona lwebantfwana labanekuphatamiseka lokukugula kwekweswela kunakwa kanye nekuba nemdlandla ngalokwendlulele.
tgt: ulwazi olubanzi nge adhd neadd silusapho nyanda lukhona uncedo lwabantwana abanesifo seattention deficit hyperactivity disorder.

src: uma umntfwana lophetfwe sifo sekuphatamiseka lokukugula kwekuba nemdlandla lowendlulele (iadhd) noma kupha tamiseka kwekweswela kunakwa (iadd) angala shwa, lesimo singaba ne mtselela lomubi wesikhatsi lesidze emphilweni yakhe.
tgt: ukuba umntwa na onesifo seadhd) okanye iattention deficit disor der (iadd) akanya ngwa, ezi zifo zingenza umonakalo onzulu empilweni yakhe.

src: loku kushiwo ngudkt khatija jhazbhay, lophetse iyunithi yetengcondvo yebantfwana nebantfwana lasebatfombile etownhill hospital epieterma ritzburg, kwazulunatal.
tgt: ezi zimbono zikagq khatija jhazbhay, owongamele icandelo lengqondo labantwana nabafikisayo kwisibhedlele itownhill epietermaritzburg, kwazulunatal.

src: lomake uchaze watsi njengebantfu labadzala, labantfwana laba bangahle babe sengotini lenkhulu yekungenwa nguletinye tifo tengcondvo, letifana nekukhatsateka/phaphuleka nekudzangala, kantsi futsi ba ngahle basebentise kabi tintfo letitidzakamiva.
tgt: uyacacisa ukuba njengabantu abadala, aba bantwana basenokuba semngciphekweni omkhulu wokuhlaselwa zezinye izifo zengqondo, ezinjengexhala kunye nokudakumba komphefumlo, futhi basenokusebenzisa iziyobisi.

src: iadhd neadd itsintsa inchubekalembili emsebentini wesikolo kubantfwana futsi kutiphatsa kwabo kungacasula labanye.
tgt: iadhd kunye neadd zichaphazela indlela abaqhuba ngayo abantwana kwizifundo zabo kwaye le ngxaki banayo inokubacaphukisa abanye abantu.

src: bantfwana bangahle futsi bangatsandvwa, babe se nkingeni kantsi futsi bangahle babe sengotini.
tgt: abantwana abanezi ngxaki basenokungathandwa, bangene engxakini futhi bathande ukwenza izinto eziyingozi.

src: "timo temntfwana ngamunye tehlukile futsi tiyatfutfuka, ngakoke kumcoka kutsi kwentiwe luhlolo lolugcwele kute kutsi kutfolakale letinye tintfo letingahle tibe nemtselela ekutfutfukeni kwabo, kanye nekutfutfukiswa kwetindzawo labanemandla kuto kute tibasite kutsi bafinyelele ezingeni lelisetulu lemakhono abo," kwasho dkt jhazbhay.
tgt: "iimeko zomntwana ngamnye zahlukile kwaye ziyakhula, ngoko ke kubalulekile ukwenza uvavanyo oluthe vetshe lwengqondo ukuze ubone ezinye izinto ezinokuba nefuthe kwindlela abakhula ngayo, kunye nezo ziluncedo kunokwakhelwa kuzo ukubanceda ukufikelela kubuchule babo obugcweleyo," utsho ugq jhazbhay.

src: uchaze watsi iadhd neadd kuphatamiseka kwengcondvo lokunemtselela ekutfutfukiseni emakhono etemfundvo lokwenta kutsi kube matima kukhona kutiphatsa, njengekunganaki.
tgt: uyachaza ukuba iadhd kunye neadd sisifo sokuphazamiseka kwemithamboluvo esithi sibangele ukuba umntwana aziphathe ngendlela engafanelekanga, efana nokungahoyi.

src: loku kubonakala nge: kungabi nendzaba nekwenta emaphutsa kungacedzi imisebenti kulahlekelwa tintfo kuphatamiseka kalula neku khohlwatibonelo tekubanemdlandla kakhulu noma kuvele nje utsatseke wente tintfo nga phandle kwekucabangisisa tifaka ekhatsi: kungahlaliseki/kuhlala ukhwishikhwisha kushayashaya ngetandla noma ngetinyawo phasi kungahlaliseki/kuntilantjila kuvele nje amemete asho timphendvulo aphindze asukume uma kulindzeleke kutsi uhlale.
tgt: oku kubonakala ngendlela: yokwenza iimpazamo ezingenamsebenzi yokungagqibi imisebenzi yokulahlekelwa zizinto yokuphazamiseka lula nokulibalaimizekelo yokuphazamiseka okanye yokuba sisingxami iquka: ukungqunga ukubetha izandla okanye iinyawo ukujubalaza esihlalweni sabo ukukhwaza iimpendulo nokuphakama xa kulinde leke ukuba uhlale phantsi.

src: "timphawu letibakhona etindzaweni letimbili noma leti ntsatfu – ekhaya, esikolweni, kubangani noma etihlotjeni noma uma kwentiwa leminye imisebenti – futsi tiphatamisa imisebenti yetenhlalo, yetemisebenti noma yetesikolo.
tgt: "iimpawu zibonakala kwiindawo ezahlukahlukeneyo – ekhaya, esikolweni, xa enabahlobo okanye ngexesha esenza eminye imisebenzi – kwaye ziphazamisa indlela anxibelelana ngayo ekuhlaleni, emsebenzini okanye esikolweni.

src: kukhanyiswa nekucinywa silusapho nyanda kunetintfo letinyenti letehlukene bantfu baseningizimu afrika labangatenta konga gezi futsi ngalokoke bavikele bucimicimi bagezi (kusebentisa gezi ngekwabelana).
tgt: masonge umbane ukuze ungacimi silusapho nyanda kukho izinto ezahlukileyo abemi bomzantsi afrika abanokuzenza ukonga umbane futhi bakuphephe ukucinywa kombane.

src: libamba lemphatsisite shi seeskom ima timba power station obakeng mabotja utsite kuswelakala kwemandla lafanelekile eningizimu afrika kunemtselela etimphilweni tebantfu ngenca yekutsi imisebenti leyetayelekile ayenteki ngesikhatsi sekwabelana ngagezi.
tgt: ibambelamlawuli wesitishi kwisikhululo sombane sa kwaeskom imatimba uobakeng mabotja uthi ukunqongophala kwamandla ombane owane leyo emzantsi afrika kuchaphazela iimpilo zabantu kuba imisebenzi yemihla ngemihla ayenzeki ngexesha lokucima kombane.

src: imatimba power station iselephalale, elimpopo.
tgt: isikhululo samandla ombane imatimba siselephalale, elimpopo.

src: mabotja uchaze watsi kwa belana ngagezi kwenteka uma ieskom ihluleka kukhicita gezi lowanele lotawuhambisana netidzingo talelive.
tgt: umabotja uyachaza ukuba ukucima kombane kwenzeka xa ueskom engakwazi ukuvelisa umbane owaneleyo ukuba ujongane neemfuno zelizwe.

src: ngakoke kumcoka, kutsi bonkhe bantfu baseningizimu afrika badlale tindzima tabo kute basebetise gezi lomncane.
tgt: ngoko ke kubalulekile, utsho, ukuba bonke abemi bomzantsi afrika badlale indima ekusebenziseni umbane omncinci.

src: emathiphu labuya kueskom ekusebentisa gezi kancane: cima emalumbu uma uphuma egunjini lelitsite.
tgt: iingcebiso ezivela kueskom zokusebenzisa umbane omncinci: cima izibane xa uphuma egumbini sebenzisa iibhaluphu zeled cima zonke izinto ezisebe nzisa umbane xa zingasebenzi sebenzisa amanzi abandayo kuphela, ngaphandle kokuba kukho imfuneko sebenzisa ingubo yobushushu ukugquma igiza yakho.

src: sebentisa emaglobhu eled cima emaapulayensi(tintfo letisebentisa gezi) uma ungawasebentisi.
tgt: ziliqela izinto ezinokuthi ziphazamise ukuveliswa kwamandla, kuquka ukulondolozwa, ukuvalwa okungacwangciswanga futhi, ngokucacileyo, imozulu.

src: sebentisa emanti labandzako kuphela, ngaphandle kwalapho kunesidzingo salashisako.
tgt: umabotja uthi isikhululo sakhe, ingakumbi, siyachaphazeleka ngamaqondo obushushu aphezulu.

src: sebentisa ingubo yekufu tfumeta kubhonya igiza yakho.
tgt: "ngeentsuku ezishushu kakhulu, isikhululo asikwazi ukuvelisa amandla ngokupheleleyo," utsho.

src: tintfo letimbalwa tingaphatamisa kukhicitwa kwagezi, letifaka ekhatsi kunakekelwa, kuvalwa lokungakahlelwa futsi uma kuhlolisiswa, nesimo selitulu.
tgt: isikhululo samandla ombane imatimba sisebenzisa amalahle ukuvelisa umbane, kwaye senzelwe ukuvelisa ama3990 mw.

src: bantfu labasha balikusasa lelive letfu vukuzenzele unnamed kucocisana neba ntfu labasha ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi kungishiya nginemdlandla.
tgt: abantu abatsha balikamva lelizwe lethu vukuzenzele unnamed ukufakana imilomo nabantu abatsha kusoloko kundishiya ndinodlamko.

src: kuyajabulisa kutfola lwati lolujulile lwemizabalazo yabo kanye nekuncoba kwabo kanye nemibononcha nti yabo lemayelana naloko lokungentiwa kutfutfukisa lelive.
tgt: kuyavuyisa ukuqonda iingxaki neempumelelo zalo kunye nemibono yalo ngento enokwenziwa ukuphucula eli lizwe.

src: ngeke sikuphike kutsi lusha bukhona benu bumcoka kakhulu emtsanjeni nasemoyeni wesive.
tgt: liyinene elokuba abantu aba tsha basisininzi, bangundaba mlonyeni kwaye izingqi zabo ziyavakala kwisizwe siphelo.

src: ayikho lengcondvo letsi lusha lutsatsela phasi, alunandzaba netepolitiki nome lutinake lona, lucwaningo lwemfundvo lwa lapha kulelive kanye nelwemhlaba wonkhe luveta kutsi lusha ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi lunembono lomuhle mayelana nelikusasa lalo.
tgt: umbono wokuba batyhafile, abanamdla kwezopolitiko okanye bayazingca, uyaphiki swa ziziphumo zamaphulo ophando aqhutywe apha ekhaya nakumazwe aphesheya angqina ukuba abantu abatsha kwihlabathi liphela bahlala benethemba lamathuba amahle okuphumelela ebomini.

src: ngekusho kwaloko lokutfo lwe yiipsos pulse of the people kuluklayo lolukhishwe ngabhi mbidvwane, 61% yebantfu base ningizimu afrika labaneminyaka le15 kuya kule17 banembono lomuhle mayelana nemnyaka wa2020.
tgt: ngokwakufunyaniswe kwi ipsos pulse of the people eyakhu tshwa kwinyanga yomqungu, iipesenti ezingama61 zabemi bomzantsi afrika abaneminyaka eli15 ukuya kweli17 baziva benethemba malunga nowama2020.

src: angingatsiti kutsi lomcabango lomuhle lonkhe lusha lwabelana ngawo jikelele futsi ikakhulu labo labatelwe ngesikhatsi sekungena kwenkhulunkhwanemnyaka nyalo lasebacale imphilo yabo yebudzala, labo bantfu labasha labatibita ngekutsi bangema2000.
tgt: andithandabuzi ukuba olu luluvo lwabantu abatsha ngokubanzi ingakumbi eli qela lazalwa ekuqaleni kwale nkulungwane, ekungoku nje bafika kwinqanaba lobudala, olubizwa ngokuba ngama2000.

src: bangemadvodzana nema dvodzakati latalwe ngemuva kwentsandvo yelinyenti.
tgt: ngumlisela nomthinjana owazalwa emva kokuba eli lizwe lifumene inkululekoi.

src: nanome bangazange bona babuve ngco bubi belubandlululo, bayachubeka ngekuphila nemshiyandvuku welubandlululo wekungalingani kwetinhlanga, kubete kwebulungiswa ngekwendzawo kanye nebuphuya.
tgt: nangona bengenazivubeko bona buqu zenkohlakalo yombuso wocalucalulo, bayaqhubeka nokuphila nentlungu eyashiywa ngulaa rhulumente yokungalingani ngokobuhlanga, ukubandeze lwa umhlaba kunye nentluphe ko.

src: labantfu labasha banelitsemba, bayatetsemba futsi baphuphuma inshisekelo.
tgt: olu lutsha luzithembile, lu yazithemba kwaye luyaphuphu ma ngamabhongo.

src: bayawati emalungelo abo futsi abesabi kuwafuna.
tgt: bayawazi amalungelo abo kwaye aboyiki ukuwabanga.
