src: ngalesikhatsi ucedza kucinywa umlilo ephalamende, libamba lelijaji lelikhulu raymond zondo watfula incenye yekucala yembiko wekhomishini yeluphenyo lwekubamba umbusongabhongwane.
tgt: kanye xa ucinywa umlilo epalamente, ibambela lejaji eyintloko uraymondzondo ungeniseinxalenye yokuqala yengxelo yekomishini yophando ngokuthathwa kombuso.

src: lencenye yalombiko ichaza ngekutsi kwangenwa njani kutikhungo letehlukahlukene tahulumende, taphangwa njani nekutsi tacekelwa njani phasi ngalendlela.
tgt: le nxalenye yengxelo inika iinkcukacha ngendlela amaziko oluntu amaninzi athe angenwa ngayo, aphangwa kwaye onakaliswa kakhulu.

src: loku kufaka tinkampani temabhizinisi tahulumende letifana netitfutsi tetindiza taseningizimu afrika, tetekuchumana tahulu mende netekwatisa kanye netemisebenti yetensela yaseningizimu afrika.
tgt: oku kuquka amashishini karhulumente afana neziko lomoya lomzantsi afrika, inkqubo yonxibelelwano lolwazi lukarhulumente kunye nenkonzo yerhafu yomzantsi afrika.

src: lencenye lena yalombiko inika sitfombe lesingasikahle kakhulu sekutsi tikhungo letimcoka tentsandvo yelinyenti yetfu tabekwa engotini lenga kanani nekutsi beticekelwa kanjani phasi ngenhloso yekwenta bugebengu.
tgt: le nxalenye yale ngxelo izoba umfanekiso okhathazayo kakhulu, wendlela apho amaziko abalulekileyo entando yesininzi athi afakwa engozini kwaye ajongelwa phantsi ngenjongo yolwaphulomthetho.

src: akusiko kuphela kutsi kwebiwa imali lenyenti, kodvwa letikhungo betingakhoni kwenta ngalokufanele umsebenti wato letasungulelwa wona.
tgt: akubiwanga nje izixa zemali kuphela, kodwa la maziko awakwazanga kuzalisekisa ngokufanelekileyo imisebenzi ayemiselwe yona.

src: loko lokutfolakele netincomo talekhomishini yazondo kutawusita lelive kutsi lakhe kabusha letikhungo nekutsi labo labasebenta kuto baphendvule.
tgt: iziphumo kunye nezindululo zekomishini kazondo ziza kunceda ilizwe ukuba liwakhe ngokutsha la maziko kwaye libambe abo banoxanduva lokuphendula.

src: kufuneka sicinisekise kutsi sisebentisa letincomo kuvikela letikhungo kute tingaphindzi tibanjwe ngabhongwane esikhatsini lesitako.
tgt: kufuneka siqinisekise ukuba siyazisebenzisa ukuze sikhusele la maziko nakwixesha elizayo angaphinde athinjwe.

src: kufuneka siyivikele kunoma ngabe yini nakuyo yonkhe imitamo yekululata intsandvo yelinyenti yetfu lesiyitfole matima – kungaba kutsi lemitamo itsatsa simo sekwenta inkhohlakalo kumabhizinisi ahulumende, kuvukela emaejensi etfu etemtsetfo, kucekela phasi sakhiwonchanti setfu setemnotfo, noma kuhlasela inkhululeko yetfu kanye nekubacotfo kwetebulungiswa betfu.
tgt: kufuneka sizikhusele kuzo zonke iinzame zokuthothisa intando yesininzi yethu esiyizuze nzima – nokuba ezi nzame zikwihlobo lorhwaphilizo kumashishini karhulumente, ukubhukuqa iiarhente zethu zogcinomthetho, ukonakaliswa kweziseko ezingundoqo zoqoqosho, okanye ukuhlaselwa kwenkululeko kunye nobulungisa beenkundla zethu zamatyala.

src: kufuneka sivikele umtsetfosisekelo wetfu, sive setfu sentsandvo yelinyenti kanye nenchubo yetfu yelukhetfo kuwo wonkhe umuntfu lofuna kwenta intsandvo yelinyenti yetfu ibe butsakatsaka nakulovimbela bantfu baseningizimu afrika kutsi batfole inkhululeko yabo lebayilelwa matima.
tgt: kufuneka sikhusele umgaqosiseko wethu, urhulumente wethu wentando yesininzi kunye nenkqubo yonyulo kuye nabani na ofuna ukwenza buthathaka intando yesininzi yethu; avimbe abantu bomzantsi afrika inkululeko yabo abayizuze nzima.

src: kuceceshwa netinsita temabhizinisi tamahhala kgatiso tlhakole tikhungo letintsatfu tahulumende titibophelele ekwenteni kutsi kube malula kwenta ibhizinisi eningizimu afrika kute kutfutfukiswe kukhula kwemnotfo.
tgt: uqeqesho lwasimahla kunye neenkonzo ezenzelwe amashishini kgatiso tlhakole amaqumrhu amathathu karhulumente agxile ekuncediseni ukuba kube lula ukwenza ushishino emzantsi afrika ukuze kukhule uqoqosho.

src: umhlangano wevidiyo wakamuva wevuk talks , wabanjwa teteku chumana tahulumende netekwatisa, kute kwatiswe ummango mayelana neligunya, ngetinchubomgomo nangetinsita letiphakelwa yikhomishini yekubhalisa tinkampani nebunikati bemphahla (icipc), umtimba lobukene netemacala latsite etinkampani (ict) kanye nekhomishini yekunika la bamnyama emandla labanti kutemnotfo (ibbbee).
tgt: iintetho ngeintanethi zakutshanje zevuk talks , ebezibanjwe yinkqubo yonxibelelwano lolwazi lukarhulumente, zabanjelwa ukwazisa ngesigunyaziso, imigaqonkqubo kunye neenkonzo ezinikezwa yikomishini yokubhalisa iinkampani nobugcisa bengqondo (icipc), inkundla yeenkampani (ict) kunye nekhomishini yokuxhotyiswa kwabamnyama ngokubanzi kwezoqoqosho (ibbbee).

src: ngito tonkhe leti tikhungo letingaphasi kwelitiko letekuhwebelana, letetimboni neletekuchudzelana.
tgt: onke la ngamaqumrhu esebe lezorhwebo, ushishino nokhuphiswano.

src: ngekusho kwaofentse shakung, longumphatsi wecipc kutekuticambela nekusebentisana futsi longumcondzisi weku fundza ngeinthanethi, icipc yenta imisebenti lehlukahlukene, lefaka kubhaliswa kwetinkampani, imifelandzawonye kanye nekwemalungelo emphahla yekuticambela (timphawu tekuhweba, emalungelo ebunikati, emadizayini nemalungelo ekushicilela).
tgt: ngokutshiwo nguofentse shakung, umphathi wecipc wokusungulwa kwezinto ezintsha kunye nentsebenziswano kunye nomlawuli weelearning, icipc inemisebenzi eyahlukeneyo, equka ukubhaliswa kweenkampani, umanyano lwamashishini kunye namalungelo obunini bempahla (iimpawu zorhwebo, amalungelo awodwa omenzi wempahla, uyilo kunye nelungelo lokushicilela).

src: icipc isungule inkhundla yayo ibizportal leniketa insita yekubhalisa inkampani ngeinthanethi nekwenta leminye imisebenti lemayelana naloko kute yente loluhlelo lwekubhalisa ibhizinisi lube malula nekutsi lulandzele tonkhe tidzingo.
tgt: icipc iphuhlise iqonga layo lebizportal ukuze kubhaliswe iinkampa ni kunye neenkonzo zayo kwiintanethi, oku kukwenza lula inkqubo yokubhalisa ishishini kunye nokuthobelaizinto ezifunwayo.

src: ibizportal iniketa labo labafuna kucala ibhizinisi indzawo leyodvwa yekubhalisa inkampani, yekubhalisela kukhokha intsela, yekubhalisa ligama lenkampani, yekufaka sicelo sesitifiketi sebbbee, yekubhalisa kusikhwama sekuncephetelisa nakumshwalense wekulahlekelwa ngumsebenti, neyekuvula iakhawunti yasebhange.
tgt: ibizportal inika abo bafuna ukuqalisa ishishini iqonga elipheleleyo lokubhalisa inkampani, ukubhali sela irhafu, ukubhalisa igama, ukufaka isicelo sesatifikethi sebbbee, ukubhalisa kwingxowamali yembuyekezo kunye nengxowamali yeinshurensi yokungasebenzi, kunye nokuvula iakhawunti yebhanki yeshishini.

src: "ibizportal iyinchubo lengasebentisi emaphepha futsi inkampani ibhaliseka kungakapheli sikhatsi lesimahora la24 emva kwekutfunyelwa kwesicelo.
tgt: "yinkqubo engasebenzisi maphepha kwaye inkampani iya kubhaliswa kwiiyure ezingama24 ingenisiwe.

src: siphindze futsi sangeta tinsita tegoogle tetemabhizinisi, letenta tinkampani tikhone kuba nephrofayili yebhizinisi kanye newebhusayithi letawuhlala ikhona yenkampani kugoogle mahhala," kwasho shakung.
tgt: sikwangeze iinkonzo zeshishini likagoogle, ezenza ukuba iinkampani zifumane iprofayile yeshishini kunye newebhusayithi yenkampani kugoogle simahla," utshilo ushakung.

tgt: iportal ilula ukuyiphendlaphendla kwaye ichaza ngendlela yokubhalisa ishishini.

src: kuceceshwa kwamahhala icipc futsi isandza kusungula inkhundla yayo yekuceceshwa ngeinthanethi yamahhala ilearnibiz kute kusitakale emabhizinisi lamancane, lasemkhatsini kanye nebacondzisi bemabhizinisi lasafufusa nekutsi bosomabhizinisi bakhone kutfutfukisa emakhono abo ekuphatsa ibhizinisi ngemphumelelo, babe futsi bacinisekisa kutsi balandzela tidzingo temtsetfo.
tgt: uqeqesho lwasimahla icipc isandu kuphehlelela iqonga loqeqesho lasimahla kwiintanethi ilearnibiz ukunceda abalawuli bamashishini amancinci, aphakathi kunye nasakhasayo kunye noosomashishini ukuze bakhulise izakhono zabo zokuqhuba amashishini anempumelelo, ngelixa beqinisekisa ukuba bathobela iimfuno zomthetho.

src: "lenkhundla iyinkhombandlela yekufundza lesebenta ngeinthanethi futsi ifaka tifundvo tevidiyo nesivivinyo sekutihlola saleso naleso sifundvo kuletisikhombisa," kwasho shakung.
tgt: eli qonga sisikhokelo sokufunda esidijithali kwaye sibandakanya izifundo zevidiyo kunye nokuzivavanya kwimodyuli nganye kwezi zisixhenxe," utshilo ushakung.

src: letifundvo tifaka kuceceshwa mayelana nekutsi yini inkampani nekutsi umcondzisi uyini, ngebantfu labamcoka enkampanini, ngemisebenti yemcondzisi, ngetifiso temuntfu tetetimali kanye nekugcubutana kwetifiso, kuholelwa kwebacondzisi nekwabelana ngetinzuzo kanye nangebhodi yebacondzisi.
tgt: iimodyuli zibandakanya uqeqesho lokuba yintoni inkampani kunye nomlawuli, abantu abaphambili kwinkampani, uxanduva lomlawuli, umdla wobuqu kwezezimali kunye nokungqubana kwemidla, umvuzo wabalawuli nokwabelana ngeenzuzo kunye nabalawuli bebhodi.

src: umtimba lobukene netemacala latsite etinkampaninidkt.
tgt: inkundla yeenkampani ugqr mohammed chicktay, usihlalo wect, ucacise wathi eli qumrhu linceda ngokunika isisombululo esikhawulezayo kwiimbambano zenkampani, ezinxulumene nezicelo kunye nezikhalazo ezenziwe ngokomthetho weenkampani nomb.

src: mohammed chicktay, longusihlalo wect, wachaza watsi lesikhungo sisita kuletsa sisombululo masinyane uma kunekungcubutana emkhatsini kwetinkampani, lokumayelana neticelo netinsolo letentiwe ngekulandzela umtsetfo wetetinkampani we71 wemnyaka we2008.
loku kufaka ekhatsi kungcubutana lokumayelana nemagama etinkampani, bucondzisi bato nekuvumeleka kutsi kusungulwe emakomiti etenhlalakahle newendlela lekahle yekutiphatsa.
tgt: oku kuquka iimbambano ezinxulumene namagama eenkampani, ulawulo kunye nokukhululwa ekusekeni iikomiti zentlalo kunye nezokuziphatha.

src: lomtimba uphindze ubuyekete imilayeto yetemtsetfo lekhishwe yicipc, lemayelana nekungetwa kwesikhatsi sekulungiselela kukhipha titatimende tetetimali temnyaka nekubamba imihlangano lemikhulu yemnyaka.
tgt: ikwahlola izaziso zokuthobela ezikhutshwe yicipc, ezimalunga nokwandiswa kwexesha lokulungiselela iingxelo zemali zonyaka kunye nokubiza iintlanganiso zikawonkewonke zonyaka.

src: "ict isebenta ngeticelo letehlukahlukene.
tgt: "ict ijongene nezicelo ezahlukeneyo.

src: ngesikhatsi secovid19, sibonelo, sitfole ticelo tekwelulwa kwesikhatsi sekubamba umhlangano lomkhulu letinengi," kwasho chicktay.
tgt: umzekelo, ngexesha lecovid19, sifumene izicelo ezininzi zokwandiswa komhla wokubiza intlanganiso kawonkewonke yonyaka," utshilouchicktay.

src: lenye insita yamahhala leniketwa yict kucatulula kungcubutana.
tgt: enye inkonzo yasimahla enikezwa yict kukusombululaimbambano.

src: umuntfu angatfumela indzaba yakhe kute isonjululwe ngekusebentisa kungenelela ngenhloso yekucwayisa, kubuyisana noma kulamula, njengendlela lencono kunekuya enkhantolo.
tgt: umntu angathumela umba ukuba usonjululwe ngolamlo, ngoxolelwaniso okanye ngokwahlulwa, njengenye indlelayokuya enkundleni.

src: ict isebenta njengemcumanisi emkhatsini kwemacembu laphikisanako.
tgt: ict isebenza njengomququzeleli phakathi kwamaqela.

src: "ict igcugcutela kutsi kusetjentiswe kungenelela ngenhloso yekucwayisa kute kuvikelwe kulahleka kwemisebenti, kakhulu kulesikhatsi secovid19, futsi kufuneka bantfu bacale kusebentisa lendlela kakhulu," kwasho chicktay.
tgt: "ict ikhuthaza ukulamla ukuze kugcinwe imisebenzi, ngakumbi ngelixesha lecovid19, kwaye abantu maba qale ukuyisebenzisa ngakumbi," utshilo uchicktay.

src: ikhomishini yebbbee ngekusho kwalindiwe madonsela, umphatsi lomkhulu kutekulandzela umtsetfo webbbee, ligunya lalesikhungo kungamela, kubuka nekugcugcutela kutsi umtsetfo webbbee we46 wemnyaka we2013 uyalandzelwa.
tgt: ikhomishini yebbbee ngokutshiwo ngulindiwe madonsela, umphathi omkhulu wokuthobela wekomishini yebbbee, igunya lequmrhu kukubeka esweni, ukulawula kunye nokukhuthaza ukuthotyelwa komthetho webbbee nomb.46 ka2013.

src: iphindze iphenye imikhuba yekufranta (kubeka umuntfu lomnyama embili kute uzuze emaphuzu ebbbee ngendlela lengekho emtsetfweni); ihlose kukhulisa lwatiso emmangweni mayelana nebbbee, ngekusebentisa temfundvo netindlela tekwatisa; bese iniketa teluleko emmangweni.
tgt: ikwaphanda ngezenzo zokwenza kubonakale ngongathi kuphethe abantu abantsundu; ijolise ekwandiseniulwazi kunye nokukhuthaza ukuqondisa uluntu ngebbbee, ngokuthi yenze amanyathelo okufundisa nawokuqondisa; kwaye inika isikhokelo eluntwini.

src: labente inkhohlakalo lephatselene netinsita tecovid19 babhekana nemtsetfo vukuzenzele unnamed labo nalabo kanye netinka mpani lebetitimbandzakanye enkhohlakalweni lephatselene nekutsengwa kwahulumende kwetimphahla netinsita tesifo seligciwane lekhorona (icovid19) bayatilandza ngetento tabo.
tgt: abenzi borhwaphilizo lwecovid19 baziswe ngaphambili vukuzenzele unnamed abantu kunye neenkampani ezibandakanyeka kurhwaphilizo olunxu lumene nokuthengwa kweempahla neenkonzo zentsholongwana yecorona (icovid19) zikarhu lumente bayaphenduliswa ngezenzo zabo.

src: umbiko wekugcina weyunithi lekhetsekile yeku phenya (isiu) lomayelana neluphenyo lwayo kuletinsolo letiphatselene nanome ngabe ngukuphi kungasebentisi kahle timali tecovid19, kuyo yonkhe imikhakha yahulumende nakumkhakha lotimele isandza kugunyatwa ngumengameli cyril ramaphosa kutsi iwukhiphele sive.
tgt: ingxelo yeyunithi yophando ekhethekileyo (isiu) emalunga nophando lwayo lwezityholo ezinxulumene nokusetyenziswa gwenxa kwemali yecovid19, kuwo onke amanqwanqwa karhu lumente kunye namacandelo abucala.

src: "lombiko usinyatselo lesimcoka sekulwa nenkhohlakalo nekungaphatsi ngemfanelo emikhakheni yahulumende naletimele," kusho yena.
tgt: kutsha nje umongameli ucyril ramaphosa ugunyazise ukuba ikhululelwe uluntu.

src: ngakholwane 2020, mengameli ramaphosa wagunyata isiu kutsi yente luphenyo.
tgt: le ngxelo linyathelo elibalulekileyo lokulwa u rhwaphilizo kunye nolawulo olugwenxa kumacandelo karhulumente nawabucala, utshilo umongameli.

src: ngaleso sikhatsi, wavakalisa kutinikela kwakhe watsi nangabe isiu itfole bufakazi lobutsi kunelicala lebugebengu lelentiwe, itawubopheleleka kutsi yendlulisele bufakazi kumtimba wavelonkhe wetekushushisa (inpa).
tgt: kweyekhala ngowama2020, umongameli ramaphosa wagunyazisa uphando lwesiu.

src: isiu yaphindze futsi yagunyatwa kutsi ifake tinchubo tekutsetsa macala kute kubuyiswe nome ngabe nguwaphi emademeshi nanome ngabe yini umbuso lokuwulahlekele.
tgt: ngelo xesha ke waye wazibophelela ngelithi ukuba ngaba isiu ifumene ubungqina bokuba kwenziwe ityala lolwaphulomthetho, iya kunyanzeleka ukuba idlulisele ubungqina kwigunyabantu lezotshutshiso lesizwe (inpa).

src: kubika ngalokutfoliwe isiu iphenye tinkontileka leti5 467 letaniketwa batfulinsita laba3 066, letilinganiselwa kutigidzigidzi letir14.3.
tgt: kwakhona isiu yaphinda yagunyaziswa ukuba ithathe amanyathelo ezomthetho ukuze kubuyiselwe nawuphi na umonakalo okanye ilahleko eyenziwe ngurhu lumente.

src: luphenyo lwetinkontileka leti4 549 seluphotfuliwe, kantsi leti2 803 titfolakale kutsi atiniketwa ngekwemtsetfo.
tgt: ingxelo yeziphumo isiu iphande iikhontrakthi ezingama5 467 ezinikwe ababonelelinkonzo aba ngama3 066, ezixabisa ir14.3 yeebhiliyoni zizonke.

src: loku kulingana ne62% yeluphenyo loselu photfuliwe.
tgt: uphando kwiikhontrakthi ezingama4 549 sele luqukunjelwe, kwaye ezingama 2 803 kuzo zafunyanwa zingekho mgaqweni.

src: "loluphenyo belucondziswe kulowo nalowo kanye nakutikhungo lokukholelwa kutsi tisebentise kabi lesikhatsi sive sinekuhlaseleka kakhulu kutsi batinjingise bona kanye nalabo lababambisene nabo ekusebentiseni kabi imitfombolusito yahulumende," kwasho yena njalo mengameli.
tgt: umongameli uthe, "olu phando lujolise kubantu kunye namaziko akholelwa ukuba angasebenzisa ixeshana lokuba semngciphekweni kwesizwe ukuze bazityebise kunye nabo bathe basebenzisana nabo ukusebenzisa kakubi izixhobo zoluntu."

src: wangeta ngekutsi akwemukeleki sanhlobo nje kutsi tinkontileka letinengi kangaka lebekuhloswe ngato kutsi tisindzise timphilo kanye nekuvikela kulahlekelwa tindlela tekutiphilisa betingekho emtsetfweni, betentiwe ngekungala ndzeli umtsetfo nome betinekukhwabanisa.
tgt: wongeza ngelithi akwamkelekanga kwaphela ukuba iikhontrakthi ezininzi ezinxulunyaniswa nokusindisa ubomi kunye nokukhusela iindlela zokuziphilisa kwabantu zazingekho mgangathweni, zingekho mthethweni okanye zinobuqhophololo.

src: "loluphenyo lukhombisa kutimisela kwetfu ekusephuleni inkhohlakalo kanye nekubukana ngco nalabo labenta loko kanye nekubatsatsela tinyatselo," kwasho yena njalo mengameli ramaphosa.
tgt: "olu phando lubonakalisa ukuzimisela kwethu ekuncothuleni neengcambu urhwaphilizo kwanokujongana nabenzi bobubi," utshilo umongameli ramaphosa.

src: lombiko wekugcina uchaza imininingwane yetindzaba isiu letendlulisele kunpa, kumatiko kanye nakutikhungo kumkhakha wahulumende kanye nakulamanye emacembu.
tgt: ingxelo yokugqibela inika iinkcukacha ngemiba esele isiu iyigqithisele kwinpa, amasebe namaqumrhu kwicandelo likarhulumente nakwamanye amaqela.

src: inpa itawuphotfula inchubo yekuboshwa kwalabo labangakenti kahle kanye nekulungisa butsakatsaka lobutfolwe luphenyo lwesiu, kwachaza yena njalo mengameli.
tgt: umongameli ucacise wathi, inpa iza kuqukumbela inkqubo yokuzisa abenzi bobubi entolongweni kunye nokujongana nobuthakathaka obuqatshelwe luphando lwesiu.

src: sinyatselo lesitsatsiwe kusukela lwacala loluphenyo, isiu, ngekusebentisana nalamanye emaejensi, yenta lenchubekelembili lelandzelako: emacala lange45, lanesamba sesihlangene selinani letigidzigidzi ler2.1, sewafakwe kumkhandlu lokhetsekile wetenkhohlakalo, kukhwabanisa nekuhanjiswa kwemali ngendlela lengekho emtsetfweni.
tgt: inyathelo elithatyathiweyo oko luqalile uphando, isiu, isebenzisana nezinye iiarhente, yenze le nkqubela ilandelayo: imiba engama45, enexabiso elidityanisiweyo ler2.1 yeebhiliyoni, iye yabhaliswa kwinkundla eyodwa yorhwaphilizo, ubuqhophololo kunye nokuhamba kweemali ngokungekho mthethweni.

src: lomkhandlu lokhetsekile uneligunyakwenta lemtsetfo lekubuyisa timali tahulumende letebiwe ngenkhohlakalo, ngekukhwabanisa kanye nangekuhanjiswa kwemali ngalokungekho emtsetfweni, kanye nekutsatsela labente loko sinyatselo semtsetfo; emacala lange224 andluliselwe ekucondzisweni kwetigwegwe kwetiphatsimandla letisematikweni nome etikhungweni tahulumende; emacala lange386 andluliselwe kunpa, kantsi lamatsatfu andluliselwe kutsi mengameli atsatse tinyatselo; emacala lange330 wona andluliselwa kutsi atsatselwe sinyatselo setekuphatsa, lokufaka ekhatsi kuvinjelwa kusebenta (bangaphindzi basebentele hulumende).
tgt: inkundla ekhethekileyo inegunya elisemthethweni lokubuyisela iimali zoluntu ezibiwe ngorhwaphilizo, ubuqhetseba kunye nokuhamba kwemali ngokungekho mthethweni, kwaye ithathele amanyathelo omthetho kubaphulimthetho; amatyala angama224 athunyelwe ukuze kuthathwe amanyathelo oluleko ngakumagosa kumasebe okanye amaqumrhu karhulumente; amatyala angama386 athunyelwe kwinpa, kwaze amatha thu agqithiswa ukuze umongameli athathwe amanyathelo; amatyala angama330 agqithiselwe kumanyathelo olawulo, aquka ukufakwa kuluhlu lwabantu bangesokuze baphinde benze umsebenzi kurhulumente.

src: ngekusho kwalombiko, samba sesisonkhe setigidzi lenger551.5 (linani lakheshi netimphahla) titawubuyiswa, bese kutsi tigidzi letinger34.2 setibuyisiwe kute kube ngulamuhla.
tgt: ngokwengxelo, yir551.5 yezigidi zeerandi (ixabiso lemali nempahla) eza kubuyiswa, ngelixa ir34.2 yezigidi sele ibuyisiwe ukuza kuthi ga ngoku.

src: loluphenyo luvikele kulahleka kwetigidzi letir114.2, kanye netinkontileka letibekelwe eceleni telinani letigidzi ler170.4.
tgt: olu phando luthintele ilahleko yer114.2 yezigidi zeerandi, laze labekela bucala izivumelwano ezixabisa ir170.4 yezigidi.

src: isiu ilindzele kutsi letindzaba tiphotfulwe emkhatsini wendlovulenkhulu namabasa 2022, ngembikwekungeniswa kumengameli kwembiko lowengetelelako ekupheleni kwenyanga yenhlaba.
tgt: isiu ilindele ukuba le miba igqitywe phakathi kwenyanga yenkwindla nekatshazimpuzi kowama2022, phambi kokuba kungeniswe ingxelo eyongezelelweyo kumongameli ekupheleni kwenyanga yesilimela.

src: icach ichumanisa titjudeni nematfuba ekufundza silusapho nyanda bantfu labasha labasengakayitfoli indzawo yekufundza etikhungweni temfundvo lephakeme bangachumana neluhlelo lwesikhungo sekunika lusito ngeticelo letifakiwe (icach) kute batfole lusito.
tgt: icach idibanisa abafundi namathuba okufunda silusapho nyanda abantu abatsha abangekazifumani iindawo zokufunda kumaziko emfundo ephakamileyo bangakwazi ukufaka izicelo kwinkqubo yecentral application clearing house (icach) ukuze bafumane uncedo.

src: icach yinsita yeinthanethi yahulumende lelawulwa litiko letemfundvo lephakeme nekucecesha (idhet).
tgt: icach yinkonzo karhulumente efunyanwa kwiintanethi elawulwa lisebe lemfundo ephakamileyo noqeqesho (idhet).

src: leluhlelo lusita labo labadzinga kufinyelela enyuvesi, emakolishi elwatitsite nemfundvo yemisebenti nekucecesha (itvet) nematfuba ekutfutfukisa emakhono.
tgt: le nkonzo inceda abo bafuna ukufikelela kwiiyunivesithi, iikholeji zemfundo yobugcisa noqeqesho (itvet) kwakunye nokufikelela kumathuba ophuhliso lwezakhono.

src: "tinsita tecach betiso lomane tikhona kusukela mhla tinge24 bhimbidvwane nga2022, futsi titawuvalwa mhla tinge31 indlovulenkhulu kusita labo labadzinga kutfola imfundvo ngemuva kwamatekuletjeni kodvwa lababukene netinsayeya tekutfola indzawo," kusho indvuna yetemfundvo lephakeme nekucecesha dkt.
tgt: "iinkonzo zecach sele ziqalile ukufumaneka ukususela ngomhla wama24 kweyomqungu 2022, kwaye ziza kuvalwa ngomhla wama31 kweyokwindla, ngelokunceda abo bafuna ukungena kumaziko emfundo enomsila kodwa bajongane nemiceli mngeni yokufumana indawo," utshilo umphathiswa wemfundo ephakamileyo noqeqesho ugqirha ublade nzimande.

src: icach ingasita labo labafake ngesikhatsi ticelo tekwemukelwa enyuvesi nome ekolishi nga2021 kodvwa abazange banikwe sikhala sekufundza kulolo hlelo lwekufundza lwabalukhetsile.
tgt: icach ingakwazi ukunceda abo abangakhange banikwe ndawo kwizifundo ebebezikhethile, nangona bebefake izicelo zabo zokwamkelwa eyunivesithi okanye ekholejini kwangethuba kunyaka ophelileyo ka2021.

src: idhet ichaze kutsi loku kuvamise kutsi kwenteke nangabe lowo lofake sicelo akahlangabetani netincabekelwane letidzingekako nomake leso sikhungo suke sesifinyelele kumkhawulo welinani letitjudeni lekumele kutsi sititsatse.
tgt: idhet icacise yathi oku kudla ngokwenzeka xa umfakisicelo engazifezekisi iimfuno ezibalulekileyo zokufaka isicelo okanye xa iziko lifikelele kumda walo othile wenani labafundi elinokubabhalisa.

src: icach ingaphindza futsi isite labo labafake ticelo tabo etikhungweni temfundvo lephakeme futsi bamukelwa, kodvwa nyalo sebafuna kuntjintja ticu tabo temfundvo tabo.
tgt: kwakhona icach ingakwazi nokunceda nabo babefake izicelo kumaziko emfundo ephakamileyo baza bamkelwa, kodwa ngoku bafuna ukutshintsha izifundo zabo.

src: icach itawendlulisela lowo nalowo kutinsita tekutfutfukisa imisebenti futsi nangabe kwenteka, ibanike litfuba lekutsi babekelwe tikhala tekufundza emanyuvesi nangabe tisekhona kanye nasemakolishi etvet nome kutinhlelo tekufundzela emsebentini kumtimba wemkhakha wemfundvo nekucecesha (iseta), ngaphandle kwe kutsi badzimate baye nome ngabe ngukusiphi sikhungo.
tgt: icach iza kuthumela abantu kwiinkonzo zophuhliso lwamakhono omsebenzi, ukanti xa kunokwenzeka ingabanika nezithuba ezisafumanekayo kwiiyunivesithi nakwiikholeji zetvet okanye uqeqeshelomsebenzi kwicandelo lemfundo noqeqesho (iseta), nga phandle kokuba umfakisicelo ade axhamleke aye ngeenyawo kulo naliphi na iziko.

src: onkhe emanyuvesi ahulumende, emakolishi etvet kanye neseta angafi nyelela kudatabase yecach kufuna labo labahlangabetana netincabekelwane tetikhala tekufundza letisasekhona.
tgt: zonke iiyunivesithi zikarhulumente, iikholeji zetvet kwakunye neeseta zizakukwazi ukufikelela kwiziko ledatabase yecach zikhangela abantu abahlangabezana nemilinganiselo yezithuba ezisafumanekayo.

src: imitsetfo lemisha lecinisa kulwa negbv vukuzenzele unnamed kulomnyaka lophelile nasewuyawuphela, ngatfola incwadzi levela elicenjini letakhamuti letikhatsatekile ticela kutsi hulumende avikele bomake nebantfwana balelive ebudloveni.
tgt: imithetho emitsha izakuqinisa amasolotya edabi lokuchasana negbv vukuzenzele unnamed ngasekupheleni konyaka ophelileyo, ndafumana ileta esuka kwiqela la bemi abaxhalabileyo becela urhulumente ukuba akhusele amanina nabantwana beli lizwe ebundlobongeleni.

src: tikhomba kwenyuka kwelizinga lekudlwengulwa nekuhlaselwa ngekwemacansi babhale njengaboma ke labaphila njalo ngekwesaba; sebalahlekelwa kuwetsemba umtsetfo.
tgt: kule leta babecacisa ngokwanda kodlwengulo nokuxhatshazwa ngokwesini, babhala ukuba njengamabhinqa basaqhubeka bephila ngoloyiko; nokulahlekelwa lithemba kwabo kwezomthetho.

src: ngitsintseke kakhulu futsi ngeva buhlungu ngendlela labachaze ngayo kwesaba kwabo bomake balelive lababukana nako malanga onkhe.
tgt: ndachukumiseka kakhulu ke kukuva amanina eli lizwe lethu ekhala ngoloyiko lwawo ngenxa yokuphathwa gadalala mihla le.

src: kuphendvula kulokuhlupheka kwabomake nebantfwana lababukana nako, sesiphasise imitsetfo lokuhloswe ngayo kutsi ibavikele.
tgt: ngenzame ke zokusabela kwiimbandezelo abafazi nabantwana aba phantsi kwazo siye sawisa imithetho eyenzelwe ukubakhusela.

src: kodvwa ngaphandle kwekutsi kususwe labo labenta lobudlova emmangweni, bomake nebantfwana bayachubeka nekuhlupheka futsi bayafa.
tgt: nangona kukhona izohlwayo zokushenxisa abenzi bobubi eluntwini, amabhinqa nabantwana basaqhubeka bebandezeleka yaye besifa.

src: ngisandza kusayina leminye imitsetfo lemi tsatfu kutsi isale isebenta ngekwemtsetfo legcina setsembiso setfu sekucinisa luhlelo lwetebulungiswa kutebugebengu, kugcu gcutela kutilandza kumbuso wonkhe kanye nekwesekela labo labasindze kulobudlova ngayo yonkhe imitamo yetfu.
tgt: kutshanje ndiye ndatyikitya iziqendwana ezintathu zomthetho ezihlonipha izithembiso zethu zokuqinisa inkqubo yobulungisa kulwaphulomthetho, ukukhuthaza ukuphendula kurhulumente wonke, kwa kunye nokubeka phambili inkxaso kumaxhoba kuzo zonke iinzame zethu zokukhusela abasetyhini nabantwana.

src: lomtsetfo lomusha wekuchibela tebugebengu netindzaba letiphatselene nabo uvikela labo labahlaseleka kalula kutsi bangahlukumeteki kwesibili ngekuvumela tinkantolo kutsi tikhetse balamuli labatakuba khona uma bantfwana labancane, umuntfu lophila nekukhu bateka nome losakhulile kakhulu bebutwa mibuto enkantolo.
tgt: umthethosihlomelo omtsha wolwaphulomthetho kunye nemiba enxulumene nawo ukhu sela abo basesichengeni sokuxhatshazwa okwesibini ngokuvumela iinkundla ukuba zinyule abameli apho umntwana osemncinane, abantu abakhubazekileyo okanye abolupheleyo behlolwa ngelixa kusaqhuba ityala.

src: uphindze futsi uvumele kusetjentiswa lokwengetiwe kwebufakazi ngekusebentisa bucwepheshe bekukhuluma ngevidiyo.
tgt: lo mthetho ukwavumela ukusetyenziswa okwandisiweyo kobungqina ngokusebenzisa iteknolojiyokuthetha ngevidiyo.

src: loku kusita ekuvikeleni fakazi kutsi angalinyatwa, kuvikela kubambeleleka lokungenasizatfu futsi konga tindleko tetinchubo.
tgt: oku kunceda ukukhusela amangqina kwingozi, ukuthintela ukulibaziseka okungafanelekanga kunye nokugcina iindleko zetyala.

src: lomtsetfo lomusha uphindze futsi ucinise tinhlelo tetfu tekufuna ibheyili.
tgt: umthetho omtsha ukwaluqinisa kakhulu ulawulo lwethu lwebheyile.

src: umshushisi longakaphikisi ibheyili emacaleni lakhetsekile kufanele kutsi babeke tizatfu tabo letisitatimende lesisemtsetfweni.
tgt: umtshutshisi ongayichasiyo ibheyile kumatyala athile amiselweyo kufuneka izizathu zakhe zibhalwe phantsi.

src: inkantolo kufanele kutsi ibuke nome ngabe ngukuphi kwesatjiswa ngebudlova lobentiwa kulofake sikhalo kanye nekubuka kuphepha kwalofake sikhalo.
tgt: ingoko ke kuzakufuneka inkundla ithathele ingqalelo naziphi na izigrogriso zobundlobongela ezenziwa ngummangalelwa kummangali kunye nezimvo zommangali ngokhuseleko lwakhe.

src: ngaphandleke nangabe inkantolo iyanetiseka kutsi kunetimo letingetulu kwekwenta letingenta kutsi kukhishwe ibheyili, ibheyili kufanele kutsi incatjelwe.
tgt: ngaphandle kokuba ke inkundla yanelisekile ukuba kukho iimeko ezizodwa ezibangela ukuba kukhululwe ummangalelwa ngebheyile, ibheyile kufuneka ingamkelwa.

src: lomtsetfo lomusha wekuchibela tebugebengu (emacala etemacansi neti ndzaba letiphatselene nawo) wenta kutsi kube licala kuhluku nyetwa ngekwemacansi kanye nekutenta umngani nebantfu laba khubatekile ngekwengcondvo ngenhloso yekubasebentisa kabi, nekwenta kutsi emacala etemacansi lentiwa kubantfu labakhubatekile ngekwengcondvo kufanele kutsi abhaliswe kurejista yavelonkhe yebantfu labente emacala etema cansi (inrso).
tgt: umthethosihlomelo omtsha womthetho wolwaphulomthetho (ulwaphulomthetho lwezesondo kunye nemiba enxulumene noko) uyakukhaba ukuxhatshazwa ngokwesondo kunye nokuncwaswa kwabantu abakhubazeke ngengqondo, kwaye ubonelela ngokuba izenzo zolwaphulomthetho ngokwesondo ngakubantu abakhubazeke ngokwasengqondweni mazibhalwe kwirejista yesizwe yabaphulimthetho ngokwesondo (inrso).

src: sesitiphendvulile ticelo letitsi asicinise lulawulo lwenrso.
tgt: siye sali sabela ke ikhwelo lokuqinisa ulawulo lwenrso.

src: labo labanemacala ebugebengu betemacansi labawente kubantfwana nome kubantfu labaphila nekukhubateka kwengcondvo, banekuboshwa kwaphambilini kuloku, futsi bagwetjwa sikhatsi lesingetulu kwetinyanga leti18 bangafaka sicelo sekutsi emagama abo asuswe kurejista ngemuva kweminyaka lenge20.
tgt: abo bakhe babanjelwa izenzo zolwaphulomthetho ngokwesondo kubantwana okanye abantu abakhubazeke ngokwasengqondweni, kwaye babegwetywe ixesha elingaphezu kweenyanga ezili18 bangade bakwazi ukufaka isicelo sokuba amagama abo asuswe kwirejista emva kweminyaka engama20.

src: lomtsetfo uphindze futsi uchubeke ulawule umsebenti wekubika kwalabo bantfu labawabonako emacala etemacansi lentiwe kubantfu labahlaseleka lula.
tgt: lo mthetho ukwalawula umsebenzi wokunika ingxelo wabantu abaziyo ukuba izenzo zolwaphulomthetho ngokwesondo zenziwe kubantu abase sichengeni.

src: lomtsetfo lomusha wekuchibela tebudlova lobentiwa emakhaya ubuka naletinye tinkimbonkimbo tebudlelwano basekhaya lobunebudlova.
tgt: umthethosihlomelo omtsha wobundlobongela basekhaya ukwathathela ingqalelo ezinye zeengxaki kubudlelwane basekhaya obunobundlobongela.

src: sesiyicinisile inchubo yekutfola imiyalo yenkantolo yekuvikeleka, futsi sangeta netimo tekutsi sicelo sayo ingafakwa ngaphasi kwatiphi timo.
tgt: siyiqinisile ke nenkqubo yokufumana isithintelo nemiyalelo yokhuseleko, sikwazandisile neemeko zokufaka isicelo somyalelo wokhuseleko.

src: sesiyilungisile indzaba yabomake kanye neba ntfwana labahlukunyetwako nanome sebanawo umyalo wenkantolo wekubavikela, nome basasekuleyo nchubo yekufaka sicelo salowo myalo wenkantolo wekubavikela.
tgt: nalo mcimbi wabasetyhini nabantwana abaxhatshazwayo nangona kukho, okanye bekwinkqubo yokufaka isicelo somyalelo wokhuseleko siwuso mbulile.

src: nangabe inkantolo ikholwa kutsi lofake sicelo usengotini lengenteka nome kunini, ingawukhipha ngekushesha umyalo wekuvikeleka ngaphandle kwesidzingo sekunika lowo lekumele kutsi aphendvule, satiso setinchubo.
tgt: ukuba ngaba inkundla ikholelwa ukubeni ummangali ukufutshane nengozi, inkundla ingakwaziukukhupha umyalelo wokhuseleko ngokukhawuleza ngaphandle kokuba inike ummangalelwa isaziso senkqubo yokuthintela ubudlelwane bakhe nommangali.

src: ngalokusemcoka, nangabe inkantolo ikhulula umuntfu lobekwe licala lebudlova basekhaya ngebheyili longakanikwa umyalo wenkantolo wekuvikeleka, inkantolo kufanele kutsi ikhiphe munye umyalo wenkantolo wekuvikeleka ngemuva kwekenta luphenyo.
tgt: into ebalulekileyo kwakhona, kukuba ngaba inkundla iyamkhulula u mntu otyholwa ngobundlobongela basekhaya ngebheyile engenawo umyalelo wokhuseleko awunikiweyo, inkundla kufuneka iwukhuphe emva kokuchotshelwa kophando.

src: nangabe inkantolo ikhipha umyalo wenka ntolo wekuvikeleka, kufanele kutsi ngesikhatsi lesifananako igunyate sigunyato sekuboshwa, lesimisiwe, sicondziswe kutemisebenti yemaphoyisa aseningizimu afrika (isaps).
tgt: xa inkundla ikhupha umyalelo wokhuseleko kufuneka kwangaxeshanye ikugunyazise ukukhutshwa kwencwadi egunyazisa ukubanjwa, enqunyanyisiwe, myalelo lowo ekufuneka unikezelwe kwinkonzo yamapolisa omzantsi afrika (isaps).

src: nangabe lilunga lesaps lisola kutsi lofake sikhalo usengotini ngenca yekwephulwa kwemyalo, kufanele kutsi bambophe ngekushesha lowo lekumele kutsi aphendvule.
tgt: ukuba ngaba ilungu lesaps likrokrela ukuba ummangali usengozini ngenxa yokwaphulwa komyalelo, ummangalelwa makabanjwe ngoko nangoko.

src: lomtsetfo nyalo sewubavikela ngalokungafihli bantfu lasebakhulile kunome ngabe nguluphi luhlobo lwebudlova basekhaya, uphindze futsi uvumele labafaka sikhalo kutsi bafake sicelo semyalo wekuvikeleka ngeinthanethi, kute bonge sikhatsi netindleko tekuhamba.
tgt: ngoku lo mthetho ubakhusela ngokucacileyo abantu abadala kuzo zonke iintlobo zobundlobongela basekhaya, kwaye ukwavumela abamangali ukuba bafake izicelo zokhuseleko kwiintanethi, ukonga ixesha kunye neendleko zokuhamba.

src: kuvikela labafake sikhalo kutsi bangachubeki bahlukunyetwe, inkantolo ingakhipha satiso sekukwelusa kuphepha isafety monitoring notice lesitawudzinga kutsi lilunga lesaps lichumane njalo nalofake sikhalo ngaphandle kwelwati lwemhlukubeti.
tgt: ukukhusela abamangali kwimpathogadalala eyongezelelekileyo, inkundla ingakhupha isaziso sokujonga ukhuseleko isafety monitoring notice esiya kufuna ukuba ilungu lesaps lisoloko linxibelelana nommangali ngaphandle kolwazi lo mxhaphazi.

src: labasindze ekuhlukumetekeni ngegbv bakhala njalo ngekungaphatfwa kahle nome ngekunganakwa kwetikhalo tabo nabafaka tikhalo etiteshini temaphoyisa.
tgt: amaxhoba egbv asoloko ekhalazela ukuphathwa kakubi okanye ukungahoywa kweenkxalabo zawo xa efaka izikhalazo kwizikhululo zamapolisa.

src: emalunga esaps lahluleka kuhambisana naletibopho ngaphasi walomtsetfo lomusha atawuba nelicala lekungatiphatsi kahle.
tgt: phantsi kwalo mthetho mtsha amalungu esaps asilelayo ukuthobela izibophelelo zawo ayakuba netyala lokuziphatha kakubi.

src: bonkhe bantfu labadzala labanelwati nome labasola kutsi kunebudlova lobentiwa emntfwaneni, kumuntfu lophila nekukhubateka kwengcondvo nome umuntfu losakhulile baphocelekile kutsi batibike tento letinjalo kusonhlalakahle nome emaphoyiseni.
tgt: bonke abantu abadala abanolwazi okanye abakro krela ukuba ubundlobongela basekhaya benziwa emntaneni, umntu okhubazeke ngokwengqondo okanye umntu osele ekhulile banyanzelekile ukuba baxele izenzo ezinjalo kunontlalontle okanye emapoliseni.

src: kungenti njalo kulicala lebugebengu.
tgt: ukusilela ukwenza oko kuzakuba lityala lolwaphulomthetho.

src: isona 2022: kwenta ncono timphilo tebantfu netindlela tabo tekutiphilisa vukuzenzele unnamed hulumende utibophelele ekucaliseni bantfu embili, futsi utinikete tinsuku leti100 kutsi acedzele luhlelo lekukhulisa umnotfo waseningizimu afrika loluta wufaka yonkhe imikhakha yemmango, lolutawuvula ematfuba emisebenti nalolutawucedza indlala.
tgt: isona ka2022: ukwenza ubomi neendlela zokuziphilisa ngcono vukuzenzele unnamed urhulumente uzibophelele ukuqinisekisa ukuba abantu baba yeyona nto ibalulekileyo, kwaye uzinike iintsuki ezili100 ukugqibezela isicwangciso esibandakanya onke amacandelo asekuhlaleni ukukhulisa uqoqosho lomzantsi afrika, ukudala imisebenzi nokulwa indlala.

src: loku kugcizelelwe ngumengameli cyril ramaphosa kunkhulumo yamengameli yebunjalo belive yemnyaka we2022.
tgt: oku kuye kwagxininiswa ngumongameli cyril ramaphosa kwintetho yakhe engobume besizwe ka2022.

src: "lomsebenti utawentiwa usukele kulesisekelo saloluhlelo lwekakhiwa kabusha nelekusimamisa umnotfo, lokutawuhlala kuluhlelo lwetfu lolujwayelekile lekwakha kabusha umnotfo," usho njalo.
tgt: "lo msebenzi uza kukwakha isiseko sesicwangciso sokwakhiwa ngokutsha nokuvuselelwa koqoqosho, nto leyo eseyinkqubo yethu sonke yokwakha kwakhona uqoqosho," utshilo.

src: mengameli utsite lokucaliswa embili nguhulumende kuncoba lobhubhane wesifo sekho rona (icovid19), kwakha sakhiwonchanti, kukhulisa imikhicito yalelive, kwakha ematfuba emisebenti kanye nekubukana nalenhlekelele yetemandla agezi.
tgt: umongameli uthe izinto eziphambili kurhulumente kukoyisa ubhubhane wesifo sentsholongwane yecorona (icovid19), ukwakha amaseko, ukonyusa iimveliso zeli, ukudala imisebenzi nokulungisa ingxaki yamandla ombane.

src: "uma ngabe kunentfo leyodvwa lesivumelana ngayo sonkhe, ngukutsi kulesikhatsi lesikuso nyalo – sekukhula kwebuphuya, sekuswelakala kwemisebenti kanye nesekungalingani – asikavumeleki futsi asinakusimama."
tgt: "ukuba kukho into enye esivumelana ngayo sonke, kukuba le meko ikhoyo ngoku – yentlupheko enzulu, intswelangqesho nokungalingani – ayamkelekanga kwaye ayinakho ukuhlala inje."

src: kwakha ematfuba emisebenti lomnyaka lophelile, lizinga lekungasebenti lafinyelela emazingeni lasetulu kakhulu lema34.9% kwikota yesitsatfu, ngenca yalokucekelwa phasi kwemnotfo lokwabangwa yi covid19.
tgt: ukudala imisebenzi kulo nyaka uphelileyo, izinga lentswelangqesho liye lafikelela kwelona nqanaba liphezulu elakhe labonwa lama34.9% kwikota yesithathu, emveni kwentshabalalo ebangelwe yicovid19.

src: "siyati sonkhe kutsi hulumende akakhi imisebenti.
tgt: "sonke siyazi ukuba urhulumente akadali misebenzi.

src: emabhizinisi ngiwo lakha imisebenti.
tgt: ngamashishini adala imisebenzi.

src: umsebenti lomcoka wahulumende kwakha simo lesitawenta imikhakha letimele – yomibili lomkhulu nalomncane – kutsi ihlangane, ikhule, ifinyelele etimakethe letinsha, yakhe imikhicito lemisha, nekutsi ikhulise lizinga lekucasha basebenti," usho njalo.
tgt: owona msebenzi karhulumente ubalulekileyo kukudala iimeko eziza kwenza ukuba icandelo labucala – elincinci nelikhulu – livele, likhule, likwazi ukungena kwiimarike ezintsha, livelise iimveliso ezintsha, nokuba liqeshe abantu abongezelelekileyo," utshilo.

src: bacishe babe80% bantfu labasebentako labacashwe ngumkhakha lotimele.
tgt: malunga ne80% yabantu abaqeshiweyo basebenza kwicandelo labucala.

src: mengameli utse hulumende utawutfula luhlelo lolusha lwesicinisekiso semalimboleko kute kululame emabhizinisi lamancane.
tgt: umongameli uthe urhulumente uza kukwazisa inkqubo entsha yokuqinisekisa imalimboleko ukunceda amashishini amancinci ukuba achache kwakhona.

src: luhlelo lwamengameli lwekugcugcutela kucashwa, loseluvele lusekele ematfuba ekucashwa la850 000, lutawukhuliswa.
tgt: inkqubo yoburhulumente yovuselelo lwengqesho, esele ixhase ngaphaya kwamathuba engqesho angama850 000, iza konyuswa.

src: linyenti lalabo labazuzile bekubantfu labasha; bomake labangetulu kwe60%.
tgt: uninzi lwabaxhamli ibingabantu abancinci; ngaphaya kwe60% ngamanina.

src: loluhlelo lwekugcugcutela kucashwa lutawenta kutsi litiko letasekhaya likhone kucasha lusha lolungasebenti lolu10 000 lolutawusebenta kwenta emarekhodi emaphe pha abe dijithali, futsi sikhwama sekucashwa kwemmango sitawakha lamanye ematfuba emisebenti la50 000. litiko letemfundvo lephakeme netekucecesha litawufaka bantfu labangasebenti labaneticu tebuchwepheshe netemisebenti yetandla neyetekucecesha laba10 000 etindzaweni tekusebenta kusuka ngamabasa 2022. lenkhundla isayouth.
tgt: uvuselelo lwengqesho luza kwenza ukuba isebe lemicimbi yekhaya lifune abantu abatsha abangama10 000 abangaqeshwanga ukuba basebenze ukwenza iingxelo esisemaphepheni zibe dijithali, ingxowamali yentswelangqesho yoluntu iza kudala amanye amathuba omsebenzi angama50 000. isebe lemfundo ephakamileyo noqeqesho liza kufaka abantu abangama10 000 abangaphangeliyo abaphumelele imfundo yobugcisa nemisebenzi yezandla kunye nezithwalandwe zoqeqesho kwiindawo zokusebenza ukususela kwekatshazimpuzi 2022. iqonga lesayouth.

src: mobi lesita bantfu labasha labafuna kufinyelela kumatfuba emisebenti nekwesekelwa nyalo seyibhalise bantfu labasha labangetulu kwetigidzi leti2.3.
tgt: mobi elinceda ulutsha olukhangela imisebenzi lukwazi ukufikelela kumathuba ngoku linolutsha olungaphaya kwezigidi eziyi2.3 olubhalisiweyo.

src: kulaba, labangetulu kwe600 000 sebafakiwe etindzaweni letinematfuba ekusebenta.
tgt: kwaba, ngaphaya kwama600 000 sele befakwe emisebenzini.

src: "luphiko lwelusha lwavelonkhe loluvuselelwe kabusha lutawucasha licembu lalo lekucala lebantfu labasha laba50 000 kulomnyaka lotako [wa2023], ngekuvula ematfuba ekutsi bantfu labasha bahlanganyele nemimango yabo, batfutfukise emakhono abo nangekutsi bakhulise ematfuba ekutsi bacasheke.
tgt: "inkonzo yesizwe yolutsha evuselelweyo iza kukhangela iqela layo lokuqala labantu abatsha abangama50 000 kulo nyaka uzayo [ku2023], ibe idalela abantu abatsha amathuba okuba negalelo kwiindawo abahlala kuzo, ukuphuhlisa izakhono zabo nokukhulisa ukuqesheka kwabo."

src: sibonelelo sesrd siyachubeka sibonelelo sahulumende sekucedza kukhatsateka lokubangwe yicovid19, lesincedze bantfu labangasebenti labangetulu kwetigidzi leti10, selulelwe sikhatsi lesingulomunye umnyaka – sitawuchubeka kute kube kusekupheleni kwendlovulenkhulu 2023. kwengeta, hulumende nebalingani bakhe batawubuka tindlela tekuchubeka kusekela bantfu labakhatsatekile ngekwetimali ngendlela lengakhonakala kulelive yesikhatsi lesidze.
tgt: isibonelelo sesrd siyaqhubeka isibonelelo sesiqabu senkxwaleko (isrd) secovid19, esele sincede ngaphaya kwezigidi ezili10 zabantu abangaphangeliyo, sandisiwe ngomnye unyaka – de kube sekupheleni kweyokwindla 2023. ngaphaya koko, urhulumente nabo asebenza nabo baza kukhangela iindlela zokuqhubeka nokuxhasa abantu abaphantsi koxinzelelo lwenkxwaleko ngendlela engazi kuxabisa ilizwe kakhulu kwixesha elide elizayo.

src: kufinyelela ekutfolakaleni kwemhlaba hulumende uyachubeka netingucuko temhlaba futsi ulindzele kutsi umtsetfosivivinywa wekubuyiselwa kwemhlaba uphasiswe kulomnyaka.
tgt: ukufikelela kumhlaba urhulumente uyaqhubeka nohlaziyo lomhlaba kwaye ulindele ukuba umthetho oyilwayo wokoxhuthwa komhlaba upasiswe kulo nyaka.

src: kusungulwa kweejensi yekutfutfukisa tekulima neyetingucuko temhlaba nako kutawuce dzelwa kulomnyaka.
tgt: ukusekwa kwearhente yohlaziyo nophuhliso lolimo nomhlaba nako kuza kugqitywa kulo nyaka.

src: "litiko letemisebenti yahulumende nelesakhi wonchanti litawuphotfula kundluliswa kwemahektha emhlaba wahulumende la14 000 uye kuejensi yekutfu tfukiswa kwetindlu," usho njalo mengameli.
tgt: "isebe lemisebenzi yoluntu namaseko liza kugqiba ukutshintshelwa kweehektare ezingama14 000 zomhlaba karhulumente uye kwiarhente yophuhliso lwezindlu," utshilo umongameli.

src: ungete ngekutsi kunemhlaba wekulima lowanele longakhona kusekela tigidzi tebalimi labancane labafuna kungena kutekukhulisa tinkhukhu, kutekufuya tilwane, kutekutjala titselo nemifino.
tgt: wongeze ngelithi kukho umhlaba owaneleyo olimekayo ukuxhasa izigidi zabalimi abakwizinga elincinci beenkukhu, imfuyo, iziqhamo nemifuno.

src: sevele, bawatfolile balimi labangetulu kwe100 000 emavawusha ekukhulisa imikhicito yabo futsi loluhlelo lutawukhuliswa lufinyelele nakulabanye balimi.
tgt: sele kukho ngaphaya kwabalimi abangama100 000 abafumene iivawutsha zeembewu ukwandisa iimveliso zabo kwaye le nkqubo iza kongezwa ukuba ifikelele kubalimi abongezelelekileyo.

src: inkohlakalo nebugebengu kusuka ekusungulweni kwekhomishini yeluphenyo lwekubamba umbuso ngabhongwane, kuya kuluphenyo lwetinkhontileka letimayelana necovid19, mengameli ramaphosa akashiyi lutfo uma kufika endzabeni yekucedza inkohlakalo.
tgt: urhwaphilizo nolwaphulomthetho ukususela ekusekeni ikomishoni yophando ejonge ukubanjwa kwelizwe, ukuya ekuphandeni izivumelwano zokuthengwa kwezinto ezoyamene necovid19, umongameli ramaphosa uguqulula yonke into xa kufikelelwa ekupheliseni urhwaphilizo.

src: "ayikho imitamo yetfu yekuvuselela umnotfo lengaphumelela uma singalwi nalomkhuba wenkohlakalo uze uphele," usho njalo mengameli.
tgt: "akho nanye kwiinzame zethu zokuvuselela uqoqosho eliza kuphumelela ukuba asilwi esi sibetho sorhwaphilizo kube kanye," utshilo umongameli.

src: kungakendluli lusuku lwamhla ti30 inyoni, mengameli utawetfula luhlelo lolutawulandzelwa lolutawuphendvula kuletincomo tekhomishini.
tgt: ungagqithanga umhla wama30 kweyesilimela, uza kuhambisa isicwangciso sentshukumo njengempendulo yeengcebiso zekomishoni.

src: uchazile kutsi emaejensi lahlukene ahulumende bewasebentisana kubona labo labangenti kahle, kubajezisa, nekubuyisela emuva imali yahulumende leyebiwe.
tgt: ucacise ukuba iiarhente ezahlukeneyo zikarhulumente bezisebenzisana ukuchonga abenzi bobubi, ukubohlwaya, nokuze benze kubuyiswe imali karhulumente ethe yebiwa.

src: tekuvikela netekuphepha titawuniketwa emandla ngekucashwa kwemaphoyisa la12 000 nangekwakha kabusha tinkhundla tetemaphoyisa temmango.
tgt: ukhuselo nokhuseleko luza komelezwa ngokukhangelwa kwabasebenzi bamapolisa abangama12 000 nokusekwa kwakhona kwamaqonga obupolisa asekuhlaleni.

src: kulwa negbvf hulumende utawuphindza futsi achubeke kucinisa kulwa nebudlova lobucondziswe kubulili lobutsite nekubulawa kwebesifazane (igbvf) kulomnyaka, ngekusebentisa luhlelo lwendlelalisu yavelonkhe kutegbvf.
tgt: ukulwa igbvf urhulumente uza kuphinda aqhubeke nokuqinisa umlo ngakubundlobongela obusekelwe kwisini nokubulawa kwabasetyini (igbvf) kulo nyaka, ngokumiselwa kwesicwangciso sesizwe secebo esingegbvf.

src: kunemitsetfo lemitsatfu lemisha lesevele isebenta kunika emandla loluhlelo lwetebulungiswa kutebugebengu nekusekela labo labasindzile.
tgt: imithetho emithathu emitsha sele isebenza ukomeleza inkqubo yobulungisa yolwaphulomthetho ixhase abo basindileyo.

src: "kusetjentiswa kwalomtsetfo kutawusita kakhulu kucinisekisa kutsi emacala ashushiswa ngemphumelelo, kutsi labo labasindzile bavikeleke nekutsi kunetintfo letingetiwe letisebenta kancono letibekiwe tekubavikela."
tgt: "ukumiselwa kwalo mthetho kuza kuhamba umgama omde ekuqinisekiseni ukuba izehlo zitshutshiswa ngokuyimpumelelo, ukuba abo basindileyo bayakhuselwa nokuba kumiselwa izithintelo ezisebenzayo.

src: lomunye walemitsetfo mengameli bekakhuluma ngawo ngumtsetfo wekuchibiyela tindzaba tetebugebengu naloku phatselene naloko lovikela labo labasengotini kutsi bangahlukumeteki kwesibili.
tgt: "omnye wale mithetho mitsha athetha ngayo umongameli ramaphosa ububhekise kumthethosilungiso wabophulimthetho nemiba eyoyamene nayo okhusela abo basengozini ekubeni ngamaxhoba okwesibini.

src: lomtsetfo lona uvumela tinkhantolo kutsi tikhetse bangeneleli labangenta luhlolo emntfwaneni lomncane, emuntfwini lonekukhubateka noma emuntfwini losekagugile ngesikhatsi licala lisachubeka.
tgt: lo mthetho uvumela iinkundla ukuba zichonge abalamli ukuba abangathi abantwana abancinci, abantu abakhubazekileyo okanye abantu abolupheleyo bangahlolwa ngayo ngethuba kuqhutywa iinkqubo zenkundla.

src: mengameli bekakhuluma futsi ngalomtsetfo wekuchibiyela umtsetfo wetebugebengu (emacala etemacansi nalokuphatselene naloko) lomusha lowenta kube licala kucashatwa ngekwelicansi nekufundzisa temacansi bantfu labagula ngekwengcondvo.
tgt: umongameli ebekwathetha ngomthethosilungiso omtsha wolwaphulomthetho (amatyala ezesondo kunye nemiba eyoyamene nawo) okhupha emthethweni ukusetyenziswa ngokwesondo nokuncwasa abantu abakhubazeke ngokwengqondo.

src: lomtsetfo uphindze ubeke kutsi emacala etemacansi lentiwa ebantfwini labagula ngekwengcondvo kufuneka abhalwe kurejista yave lonkhe yetaphula mtsetfo tetemacansi.
tgt: lo mthetho ukwaxela ukuba amatyala ezesondo ngakubantu abakhubazeke ngokwengqondo kufuneka bafakwe kumqulu wesizwe waboni bezesondo.

src: sesisondzele sikhatsi sekuphela kwesimo senhlekele esa vukuzenzele unnamed mengameli cyril ramaphosa usandza kumemetela enkhulumeni yebunjalo besive (isona) yakhe yemnyaka we2022 kutsi hulumende uhlele kususa lesimo savelonkhe senhlekelele njengoba lelive lingena kusigaba lesisha sekulawula lobhubhane wesifo seligciwa ne lekhorona (ico vid19).
tgt: ukuphela kwemeko yentlekele kusondele emzantsi afrika vukuzenzele unnamed umongameli cyril ramaphosa usandula ukubhengeza kwintetho yakhe engobume besizwe (isona) ka2022 ukuba urhulumente uceba ukuphelisa imeko yentlekele yesizwe njengokuba ilizwe lingena kwisigaba esitsha solawulo lobhubhane wesifo sentsholongwane yecorona (icovid19).

src: "kuyinhloso yetfu kucedza simo senhlekelele yavelonkhe masinyane uma sesivumelene ngaletinye tindlela letingaphasi kwemtsetfo wavelonkhe wetemphilo kanye naleminye imitsetfo yekulawula lobhubhane," kusho mengameli.
tgt: "yinjongo yethu uku phelisa imeko yentlekele yesizwe ngokukhawuleza sakube sigqibe amanye amanyathelo phantsi komthetho wempilo wesizwe neminye imithetho ukulawula lo bhubhane," utshilo umongameli.

src: mhla ti15 indlovulenkhulu 2020, mengameli ramaphosa wamemetela lesimo senhlekelele yavelonkhe ngekulandzela umtsetfo wekulawula inhlekelele futsi wamemetela tindlela letehlukahlukene tekuvikela kucubuka kwecovid19.
tgt: ngomhla we15 kweyokwindla 2020, umongameli ramaphosa wabhengeza imeko yentlekele yesizwe ngokwemimiselo yomthetho wolawulo lwentlekele waze wazisa uluhlu lwamanyathelo okunqanda ukwanda koqhambuko lwecovid19.

src: mengameli ramaphosa utse cishe yonkhe imibandzela lemayelana netemnotfo netenhlalo sevele isusiwe, ikakhulu ngenca yalokwetfulwa kwaloluhlelo lwekuphakelwa kwemitsi yekugoma.
tgt: umongameli ramaphosa uthe phantse zonke izithintelo ezikwiintshukumo zoqoqosho nezasekuhlaleni sele zisusiwe, kwaye uninzi lwazo ngenxa yokuqhutywa kwenkqubo yokugonya.

src: ukhumbute bantfu kutsi imitsi yekugoma iyincenye lencono yekuvikela kugula, kufa necovid19, lesevele itsetse imiphefumulo yebantfu lecishe ibe100 000 eveni letfu.
tgt: ukhumbuze abemi beli ukuba amachiza okugonya ayeyona ndlela ihamba phambili yokuzikhusela ngasekuguleni, ekufeni nakwicovid19, esele ithathe ubomi babantu abaphantse bafikelele kuma100 000 kweli.

src: "bengisolo ngisho ngekubona kwami kutsi, uma ngabe bengingakagomi, ngengongoni ngesikhatsi ngibanjwa yicovid19, ngiyatsemba kutsi ngabe akusimi lome lapha," wabeka njalo.
tgt: "oko ndatsho ukuba ngokubona kwam, ukuba bendingagonyanga, ngeyomnga ukufumana kwam icovid19, mhlawumbi ngendingemanga apha ngoku," utshilo ecinga emva.

src: mengameli utsatse lesikhatsi kuncusa bantfu baseningizimu afrika kutsi batfole lomtsamo losindzisa imphilo futsi bachubeke nekulandzela tindlela tetemphilo letisisekelo nekutsi bahlale bacaphele njalo.
tgt: umongameli uthabathe ithuba ukubongoza abemi bomzantsi afrika ukuba bafumane isitofu esisindisa ubomi nokuba baqhubeke nokulandela amanyathelo ezempilo asisiseko nokuba bahlale bethe qwa.

src: "sitawukhona kuchubeka ngetimphilo tetfu, nanoma ngabe leligciwane lisemkhatsini kwetfu," usho njalo, wangeta ngekutsi leligciwane likhulise ligeba lelisemkhatsini kwalabo labasebentako nalabo labangasebenti.
tgt: "siza kukwazi ukuqhubeka nobomi bethu, nokuba le ntsholongwane isephakathi kwethu," utshilo, esongeza ngelithi lo bhubhane wenze mandundu iyantlukwano phakathi kwabo baqeshiweyo nabo bangenamisebenzi.

src: sikhwama sekubumbana mengameli ramaphosa wamemetela kutsi lesikhwama sekubumbana sitfole emabhiliyoni lar3.4 lavela ebantfwini baseningizimu afrika nakutinkhapani, ngaleso sikhatsi bantfu labangetulu kwe400 netinkhapani leti100 bavolontiya ngesikhatsi sabo nangetinsita tabo.
tgt: ingxowamali yomanyano umongameli ramaphosa ubhengeze ukuba ingxowamali yomanyano sele iqokelele ir3.4 yeebhiliyoni kubemi bomzantsi afrika neenkampani, ngethuba ngaphaya kwama400 abantu neenkampani ezili100 zizinikele ngexesha neenkonzo zazo.

src: "lesikhwama sadlala indzima lenkhulu kusekela kumphendvulo yetemphilo tavelonkhe nasekucedzeni lenhlekelele lebukene nelive letfu kanye nebantfu bakitsi."
tgt: "le ngxowamali idlale indima engundoqo ekuxhaseni impendulo yesizwe yempilo nokunciphisa ingxaki yoluntu eliye lajongana nayo ilizwe nabantu."

src: ubonge wonkhe umuntfu lonikelile kulesikhwama, lokufaka ekhatsi emalunga ephalamende kanye naletinye tindlela tekusekela labo labatsintsekile ngalobhubhane.
tgt: ubulele wonke umntu oye wafaka isandla kule ngxowamali, kuquka namalungu epalamente kunye namanye amaphulo ukuxhasa abo bachatshazelwe ngulo bhubhane.

src: mengameli uphindze watfula sigcoko kuletisebenti tetemphilo letinengi naletinye tisebenti letenta umsebenti lobucayi etikhungweni tetemphilo letidlale indzima lenkhulu ekulweni necovid19.
tgt: umongameli ukwanike imbeko kubasebenzi abaninzi bezempilo abasebenza nabantu bedlala indima ebalulekileyo kumlo onxamnye necovid19.

src: "sive kufuneka sibonge kakhulu kuletisebenti tetemphilo ngekutibophelela kwato nakuleto letenta umsebenti lobucayi ngekutidzela ngemphilo yato nangekubeka imphilo yato engotini kute tinakekele labagulako nalabo lababutsakatsaka ngalekhatsi," usho njalo.
tgt: "isizwe sityala umbulelo omkhulu kubasebenzi bezempilo abazinikeleyo nakwabanye abantu abasebenza phambili ababeke iimpilo zabo nobomi babo emngciphekweni ukukhathalela abo bagulayo nababuthathaka ngeli xesha," utshilo.

src: – sanews.
tgt: – sanews.

src: gov.
tgt: gov.

src: hulumende nemkhakha lotimele bamcoka ekukhuliseni umnotfo vukuzenzele unnamed njengoba sisebenta kukhulisa umnotfo wetfu nekwakha ematfuba emsebenti, kunekucocisana lokubanti lokumayelana netindzima letehlukene lekumele tidlalwe nguhulumende nabosomabhizinisi kute kufinyelelwe kuletinhloso.
tgt: amacandelo karhulumente nelabucala abalulekile ekukhuleni koqoqosho vukuzenzele unnamed njengokuba sisebenzela ukukhulisa uqoqosho lwethu nokudala imisebenzi, kukho iingxoxo ezininzi malunga nokoyamana kwendima yombuso neyamashishini ekufezekiseni ezi njongo.

src: labanye bantfu babona kutsi kufuneka sikhetse emkhatsini, kulolunye luhlangotsi, sive lesisatfutfuka lesidlala indzima lemcoka kutingucuko temnotfo nakutenhlalo, kantsi, kulolunye, kufuneka kufakwe umfutfo, ekukhuliseni umkhakha lotimele lohamba embili ekukhuliseni umnotfo nasekuvuleni ematfuba emsebenti.
tgt: abanye abantu bacebise ukuba kufuneka sikhethe phakathi kombuso wophuhliso odlala indima ebalulekileyo kwinguqu yoqoqosho nasekuhlaleni kwelinye icala kunye necandelo labucala elikhulayo elidlamkileyo neliqhuba ukukhula nengqesho kwelinye icala.

src: liciniso litsi sikudzinga kokubili loku.
tgt: eneneni sizidinga zombini.

src: sidzinga sive lesikhona kutfutfuka kanye nemkhakha lotimele losebenta kahle nalosheshisako.
tgt: sidinga umbuso wophuhliso onobuchule kunye necandelo labucala elinamandla nelikhawulezayo.

src: kudzingeka kutsi yomibili imikhakha isebentisane futsi ihambisane.
tgt: sidinga ukuba asebenzisane ancedisane apho elinye lisilela khona.

src: lomcondvo lona awusimusha.
tgt: lo mbono awukho mtsha.

src: eminyakeni lemashumi lamatsatfu leyengca, ngemnyaka we1992, iafrican national congress yavumelana ngaledokhumenti lenesihloko lesitsi ‘ready to govern’.
tgt: kwiminyaka engamashumi amathathu eyagqithayo, ngo1992, iafrican national congress yamkela njengeyalo uxwebhu olunesihloko esithi ‘ready to govern’.

src: ledokhumenti iniketa tinkhombandlela teningizimu afrika yentsandvoyelinyenti futsi, kuleminyaka lemashumi lamatsatfu, ibe nemtselela ekukhombeni kutsi kufuneka kuphatfwe ngekulandzela intsandvoyelinyenti nangekunikana ematfuba.
tgt: olu xwebhu lwaluqulethe izikhokelo zomgaqonkqubo womzantsi afrika wenta ndo yesininzi kwaye kwiminyaka engaphaya kwamashumi amathathu sele ube nempembelelo kwindlela ethathwa ngumgaqonkqubo wolawulo lwentando yesininzi olulandelelanayo.

src: ledokhumenti letsi ‘ready to govern’ beyihlose kutsi kube nahulumende wentsandvoyelinyenti lotawusebenta kuchumanisa, kuhlela kanye nekukhomba indlela yekutfutfukisa umnotfo lotawuba nephethini yekukhula kwemnotfo lotawuletsa kusimama nekubambisana nembutfo wetinyonyane tebasebenti, emabhizinisi kanye naletinye tinhlaka temmango.
tgt: uxwebhu oluthi ‘ready to govern’ lalinombono wombuso wentando yesininzi onoxanduva olupheleleyo ‘lokuququzelela, ukucwangcisa nokukhokela uphuhliso loqoqosho luhambe ngendlela yokukhula ezinzileyo’ lusebenzisana nentshukumo yeemanyano zorhwebo, amashishini kunye namanye amalungu oluntu.

src: ledokhumenti beyikhuluma ngesidzingo sekutsi kube nenchubomgomo yetemnotfo letawuletsa intsandvoyelinyenti kutemnotfo bese yakha ematfuba emisebenti letawunika bantfu baseningizimu afrika imiholo lesezingeni lekutiphilisa.
tgt: luquka nemfuneko yokubakho komgaqonkqubo woqoqosho owenza uqoqosho lube yintando yesininzi nodala amathuba engqesho aphuhlisayo apho bonke abemi bomzantsi afrika bafumana umvuzo olungele ukuphila.

src: ledokhumenti futsi beyihlose kutsi kube ‘nemkhakha lotimele loshukumako, lotawusebentisa emakhono nekuhlakanipha kwawo wonkhe umuntfu waseningizimu afrika …nekutsi emabhizinisi asebente ngendlela lefaka ligalelo lelikhulu ekwakheni ematfuba emisebenti, lokutawuhlala kukhutsatwa njalo.’ kulenkhulumo yamenga meli lemayelana nebunjalo belive yakamuva, ngichazile kutsi kufuneka hulumende, emabhizinisi nebasebenti basebentisane njani, kube nguloyo naloyo asebentise likhono lakhe lelingakavami, kwakha ematfuba emsebenti.
tgt: olu xwebhu lukwanombono ‘wecandelo labucala elinamandla, elisebenzisa zonke izakhono nobukrelekrele babo bonke abemi bomzantsi afrika… nalapho izenzo zoshishino olunegalelo elikhulu ekudaleni imisebenzi zikhuthazwayo.’kwintetho engobume besizwe esandula ukubakho, ndiye ndenza amagqabantshintshi malunga nendlela ekumelwe ukuba urhulumente, amashishini nabasebenzi basebenze kunye ngayo, inye isebenzisa izakhono zayo ezikhethekileyo ukudala imisebenzi.

src: lenye yetintfo letihamba embili ekukhuliseni umnotfo nekucashwa kwebantfu ngilamabhizinisi ahulumende (emasoe).
tgt: enye yezona zinto ezibalulekileyo eziqhuba ukukhula nengqesho ngamashishini karhulumente (iisoe).

src: akhicita gezi, alawula emacweba, akha imigwaco futsi aphakela emanti ladzingwa ngumnotfo kute ukhone kusebenta.
tgt: avelisa umbane, alawula amazibuko, akha iindlela kwaye azisa amanzi adingwa luqoqosho ukuze lusebenze.

src: kusukela kwafika intsa ndvoyelinyenti, lamasoe akhulise kukhulu kufinyelela kutinsita letisisekelo kulabo labaphuyile.
tgt: oko kwathi kwaqala intando yesininzi, ezi soe sele zandise ukufikeleleka kweenkonzo ezisisiseko ebantwini abahlelelekileyo ngendlela ebonakalayo.

src: kungako incenye lebucayi yeluhlelo lwetfu kukukhulisa emabhizinisi ahulumende, kuwabuyisele esimeni semnotfo lesikahle, kutfutfukisa kusebenta kwawo nekutsi siwente kutsi adlale indzima lemcoka kakhulu naletawuletsa inzuzo kutemnotfo.
tgt: yiyo le nto inxalenye eba lulekileyo yenkqubo yethu ikukomeleza amashishini karhulumente, ukuvuselela impilo yawo yezezimali, ukuphucula indlela asebenza ngayo nokuwenza akwazi ukudlala indima ebonakala nangakumbi nenegalelo eliluncedo kuqoqosho.

src: kuliciniso loko lokuhloswe ‘yiready to govern’, hulumende uhola kokubili kukhula kwemnotfo netingucuko ngekusebentisa tintfo letifana netinchubomgomo tekucudzelana, tibonelelo tekufukulwa lokubanti kwebantfu labamnyama kutemnotfo kanye nemitsetfo yetekulingana emsebentini, nangekuchumanisa kuniketwa kwemalayisensi lahlukahlukene kute asebente yonkhe indzawo kanye netibopho tekunikwa emandla.
tgt: ngokuhambelana nendima engumbono we‘ready to govern’, umbuso ukhokela ukukhula nenguqu usebenzisa izixhobo ezifana nomgaqonkqubo wokhuphiswano, izibonelelo zokuxhotyiswa ngokubanzi ngokwezoqoqosho kwabamnyama kunye nemithetho yolingano, nangokudibanisa ukunikwa kwamaphephamvume ohlukeneyo kwiinkonzo jikelele nezibophelelo zokuxhobisa.

src: hulumende futsi uyatsintseka ngco ekukhiciteni ematfuba ekucashwa ngetulu kwalawo alabo labasebenta kuhulumende.
tgt: urhulumente ukwachaphazeleka ngqo ekudalweni kwemisebenzi engeyiyo eyabantu abaqeshwe ngurhulumente.

src: loluhlelo lwemisebenti yahulumende lolululiwe, lolwacala kusebenta kusukela ngemnyaka we2003, selukhicite ematfuba emisebenti ebantfwini labatigidzi.
tgt: inkqubo eyandisiweyo yemisebenzi yoluntu, eyasungulwa ngo2003, sele inike amathuba emisebenzi kwizigidi zabantu.

src: esikhatsini lesisandza kwendlula, aphendvula kulomtselela lomubi walobhubhane wecovid19, lohulumende lona ungamele kukhula lokumcoka kakhulu kwekucashwa nguhulumende emlandvweni walelive.
tgt: kutsha nje, njengempendulo yentshabalalo yefuthe lobhubhane wecovid19, lo rhulumente uye wongamela okona kwandiswa kubalulekileyo kokuqeshwa koluntu kwimvelaphi yelizwe lethu.

src: luhlelo lwamengameli lwekugcugcutela kucashwa lisekele ematfuba emisebenti langetulu kwe85 000 etinyangeni leti16 kuphela.
tgt: uvuselelo lwengqesho lukamongameli luxhase ngaphaya kwamathuba angama850 000 ngeenyanga nje ezili16.

src: kungeta kulokukhula kwekucashwa nguhulumende, sisite bantfu labasha labangasebenti kute sibalungiselele kusebenta, sibente bacasheke kanye nekubachumanisa nematfuba.
tgt: ngaphaya kokwandisa ingqesho yoluntu, lunika inkxaso kulutsha olungasebenziyo ukululungiselela umsebenzi, ukulwenza luqesheke nokuludibanisa namathuba.

src: kunaletinye tindlela letinengi hulumende langafaka ngato ligalelo ngco ekuvuleni ematfuba emsebenti, lokufaka ekhatsi kusisa kakhulu kusakhiwonchanti, kusungula tindzawo letikhetsekile tetemnotfo nangekusekela timboni leticasha bantfu ngebunengi.
tgt: zininzi ezinye iindlela urhulumente angaba negalelo ngqo ngazo ekudaleni imisebenzi, kuquka notyalomali olubanzi kumaseko, ukusekwa kwemida ekhethekileyo yoqoqosho nangokuxhasa ukukhula okusebenza nzima kwamashishini.

src: kulomnyaka sigcile kakhulu kumabhizinisi lamancane, lasafufusa, kutinhlangano temabhizinisi nakumkhakha longakahleleki.
tgt: siza kugxila ngokukodwa kulo nyaka kumashishini amancinci, aphakathi namancinci kakhulu, kumashishini ajolise ekunikeni inkonzo ethile nakwicandelo elingekho sesikweni.

src: ngalokuhlela kabusha sicinisekiso semalimboleko lesatfulwa ngasekucaleni kwetinyanga tekubhedvuka kwabhubhane wecovid19, senta kutsi imali ‘longaphindza uyibolekwe’ itfolakale kalula kumabhizinisi lamancane.
tgt: ngokuyilwa kwakhona kwenkqubo yesiqinisekiso semalimboleko esiyazise kwiinyanga zokuqala zobhubhane wecovid19, senza inkxasomali yokuchacha kwakhona ifikeleleke lulana kumashi shini amancinci.

src: sikhulisa lesikhutsati sekuncishicelwa intsela futsi sibuka letinye tingucuko tekulawula letehlukahlukene kute sente kuba malula kutsi emabhizinisi lamancane akhone kucasha bantfu labanengi.
tgt: sandisa inkuthazo yerhafu yengqesho kwaye sijonga olunye uluhlu lotshintsho lolawulo ukwenza kube lula ukuba amashishini amancinci aqeshe abantu abongezelelekileyo.

src: njengoba ngishilo kunkhulumo yamengameli yebunjalo belive, leti ngule tinye tetindlela lesititsatsako njengahulumende "kwenta simo lesitawenta umkhakha lotimele usebente – yomibili umkhakha lomkhulu nalomncane – kugcama, kukhula, kufinyelela etimakethe, kwakha imikhicito lemisha nekungeta kucashwa kwebasebenti. "
tgt: njengokuba benditshilo kwintetho engobume besizwe, ezi ziphakathi kwamanyathelo esiwathabathayo njengorhulumente "ukudala iimeko eziza kwenza icandelo labucala – elikhulu nelincinci – livele, likhule, lingene kwiimarike ezintsha, ukudala iimveliso ezintsha nokuqesha abasebenzi abongezelelekileyo.

src: umkhakha lotimele ucasha emakota lamatsatfu ebasebenti baseningizimu afrika futsi ubukene nekusisa lokungetulu kwesigamu lesingulokubili kulokutsatsu kanye netindleko teluphenyo netekutfutfukisa.
tgt: "icandelo labucala liqesha isithathu kwisine sabasebenzi bomzantsi afrika kwaye lingunobangela wesibini kwisithathu lwenkcitho yotyalomali kunye nophando nophuhliso.

src: edvute nesive lesinelikhono nalesisatfutfuka, live letfu lidzinga umkhakha lotimele lokhulako losisa kumakhono ekukhicita.
tgt: ndawonye nombuso onobuchule nophuhliso, ilizwe lethu lidinga icandelo labucala elichachayo elityala imali kwimveliso.

src: njengoba umkhakha wangasese ukhula, tindlela tebantfu labanengi tekuphila tiyasekelwa futsi tiyasimama.
tgt: njengokuba ingqesho isanda kwicandelo labucala, kuxhaswa kwaye kugcinwa iindlela zokuziphiilisa ezongezelelekileyo.

src: imphahla netinsita tiyaphakelwa ngebunyenti futsi nahulumende wentsandvoyelinyenti uyakhona kugcogca ngalokungetiwe intsela kute kutfutfukiswe tenhlalo.
tgt: izinto neenkonzo zihanjiswa ngezinga elingaphezulu kwaye umbuso wentando yesininzi uyakwazi ukuqokelela ingeniso eyongezelelekileyo ukuphuhlisa uluntu.

src: inkhundla yetebulungiswa lekhetsekile ikhombisa kutsi bugebengu abunambuyiselo allison cooper kulembizo yeli hhovisi lamengameli lesandza kwenteka emahikeng, takhamuti letinyenti tikhombise kukhatsateka mayelana nelitubane lekulwa nenkhohlakalo.
tgt: inkundla ekhethekileyo ibonisa ukuba ulwaphulomthetho alubhatali allison cooper ngexesha lembizo kamongameli yakutshanje emahikeng, abemmi abaninzi bavakalise iinkxalabo malunga nesantya sokulwa urhwaphilizo.

src: bangitjele tintfo lengiti vile nakuleminye imimango kulo lonkhe lelive: kutsi lababhebhetseli baletento letinjena bayatiwa, ngoba babukisa ngenzuzo yebugebengu babo.
tgt: bandi xelele into endiyivileyo kwezinye iindawo zokuhlala kwilizwe liphela: ukuba abenzi bezenzo ezinje bayaziwa, kuba baqhayisela ngeenzuzo zolwaphulomthetho lwabo.

src: kodvwa sandla semtsetfo sidze.
tgt: kodwa ingalo yomthetho inde.

src: labo labantjontjele umbuso bangakholelwa ekutseni baphunyulile.
tgt: abo babileyo kurhu lumente banokukholelwa ukuba babhungcile.

src: kodvwake ekugcineni tento tabo titawubabamba, noma ngabe bangubobani, nanoma ngusiphi sikhundla labakuso.
tgt: kodwa izenzo zabo ekugqibeleni ziza kubafumana, nokuba bangoobani na, nakwesiphi na isikhundla abakuso.

src: batawufundza kutsi bugebengu abunambuyiselo.
tgt: baza kufunda ukuba ulwaphulomthetho alubhatali.

src: mayelana naloku, sinye setikhali tetfu lesinemandla kakhulu kutsi silwe nenkhohlakalo nekubanjwa kwembuso ngabhongwane inkhundla yetebulungiswa lekhetsekile yeluphiko lwetekuphenya lolu khetsekile (isiu), lenga yisungula nga2019.
tgt: ngokubhekiselele koku, esinye sezona zixhobo zethu zisebenzayo eku lweni urhwaphilizo kunye nokubanjwa ngobhongwane kombuso yinkundla ekhethekileyo yecandelo lophando elikhethekileyo (isiu), endaliseka ngowama2019.

src: yehlulela ngetindzaba letisungulwe yisiu kute kutekwe emacala embango ngemuva kwekuphotfula luphenyo lwayo.
tgt: igweba kwimiba ethi isiu iyisungulele ama tyala oluntu emva kokuba iluqukumbele uphando lwayo.

src: inkhundla yetebulungiswa lekhe tsekile yasungulelwa kutsi kusheshiswe kutekwa kwemacala.
tgt: inkundla ekhethekileyo yamiselwa ukuba kukhawuleziswe ukuxoxwa kwamatyala.

src: lendlela seye nte kwakhona kutsi timali kanye nemphahla yembuso lebeyilahlekile ngekwetizatfu tetento tenkhohlakalo kutsi titfolwe masinyane, kugwenywe kubambeleleka etinkantolo letiphakeme, lapho isiu ifanele kutsi ilindzele litfuba layo ikanye nalabanye bamangali.
tgt: le ndlela yenze ukuba imali karhulumente kunye neempahla zikarhulumente ezithe zalahleka kwizenzo zorhwaphilizo zibuyiselwe ngokukhawuleza, kuthi ntelwe ukulibaziseka kwii nkundla eziphakamileyo, apho isiu bekunyanzeleke ukuba ilinde ithuba layo kunye nabanye abamangali.

src: isiu ingacela imiyalelo yekulondvolota kanye nekubanjwa kwemphahla kute kutsi kuvinjelwe lokunye kulahlekelwa umbuso longahlangabeta nako.
tgt: isiu inokucela imiyalelo yogcino kunye nokuthintelwa kokusetyenziswa kwempahla ukuthintela ilahleko eyongezelelweyo kurhulumente.

src: loku kubalulekile uma kucutjungulwa kutsi benti balokubi labasuke basoleka bavamise kuhambahamba, babhace noma balahle imali labayitfole ngenkhohlakalo.
tgt: oku kubalulekile xa kuqwalaselwa ukuba abenzi bobubi abarhanelwayo badla ngokwenza inzame ezi nkulu zokuhambisa, bafihle okanye balahle iinzuzo zorhwaphilizo.

src: akungabateki kutsi inkhundla yetebulungiswa lekhetsekile itishintjile tintfo.
tgt: akukho mathandabuzo ukuba inkundla ekhethekileyo iye yaguqula izinto.

src: kusukelwa yasungu lwa, lenkhundla sivumbulule tigidzigidzi leticishe tibe ngur8.6 kumakontileka langekho emtsetfweni.
tgt: ukususela ekusekweni kwayo, inkundla yama tyala iye yafumana malunga ner8.6 yeebhiliyoni zeerandi kwiikhontrakthi ezingekho mthethweni.

src: nanoma ngukuphi kulwa nenkhohlakalo lokutsiwa kube yimphumelelo, akweneli kutsi babhebhetseli bashushiwe.
tgt: ukuze nawuphi na umlo ochasene norhwaphilizo ubonakale unempumelelo, akwanelanga ukuba abenzi bobubi batshutshiswe.

src: loko labakuzuze kubugebengu babo kufanele kutfolwe kutsatfwe.
tgt: iinzuzo zolwaphulomthe tho lwabo kufuneka zibu yiselwe.

src: lemali lena yetakhamuti futsi ifanele kutsi isetjentiselwe kuhlangabetana netidzingo tabo.
tgt: le mali yeyabemmi kwaye kufuneka isetyenziselwe ukuhlangabezana neemfuno zabo.

src: lenkhundla yetebulungi swa lekhetsekile isandza kuyalela tinkampane tekwakha letimbili kutsi tibuyise intalo letitfole kumakontileka etigidzi letinger40 ekufaka fenisi emnyeleni ebeit bridge.
tgt: inkundla ekhethekileyo kutsha nje iyalele iinkampani ezimbini zokwakha ukuba zibuyise iingeniso eziyifumene kumar40 ezigidi zeekontrakthi zokwakha ucingo lomda webeit bridge.

src: loku kulandzela luphenyo lolwentiwa yisiu leyatfola lokunyenti lokungahambi kahle, lokufaka ekhatsi inkhokhelophambilini yaletinkampani leyentiwa litiko letemisebenti yahulumende nesakhiwo nchanti.
tgt: oku kula ndela uphando olwenziwa yisiu oluthe lwafumanisa izinto ezininzi ezitenxileyo, eziquka ukuhlawulwa kwangaphambili kwiinkampani lisebe lemisebenzi karhulumente neziseko ezingundoqo.

src: kulamaviki lambalwa lengcilenje kuphela, lenkhundla yetebulu ngiswa ibuyekete yaphindze yabeka eceleni emakontileka emali lengetulu kwetigidzi letingetulu kwer100 langahambi kahle nalangekho emtsetfweni lavele ekutsengweni kwetintfo letiphatselene necovid19.
tgt: kwezi veki zimbalwa zidlulileyo zizodwa, inkundla yamatyala iye yaphonononga kwaye yabekela bucala ngaphezulu kwer100 lezigidi zeekhontrakthi ezingafanelekanga nezingekho mthethweni ezivela kwiinkqubo zokufumana abanikizinkonzo ezinxulumene necovid19.

src: lenkhundla yetebu lungiswa lekhetsekile iphindze futsi yaphumelela ekutfoleni imali kulabakhulu besigungu lesiphetse kutinkampani tembuso labachuba tebhizinisi letingahambi kahle.
tgt: inkundla ekhethekileyo iye yabanempumelelo ekufumaneni imali kubaphathi abaphezulu abakumashishini karhulumente abaqhube imisebenzi engafanelekanga yoshishino.

src: sibonelonje, kulomnya ka lowendlulile loyo bekasikhulu sakatransnet wayalelwa kutsi akhokhe tigidzi letinger26 lati tfola njengemninimasheya enkampanini yebunjingalwati betebunjiniyela labanikwa ikontileka yetransnet abe asasebenta njengesisebenti lesicashwe ngalokuphelele.
tgt: umzekelo, kulo nyaka uphelileyo owayesakuba sisigqeba sakwatransnet wayalelwa ukuba ahlawule amar26 ezigidi zeerandi awazifumanayo njengo mninizabelo kwishishini leenjineli zabacebisi ngokuthi abengumcebisi wakwatransnet ngethuba wayengumsebenzi wesi gxina.

src: isiu emacaleni lama nyentana icele inkhundla yetebulungiswa kutsi ibambelele kukhokhwa kwetinzuzo tetemphesheni, lapho kusalindvwe umphumela weluphenyo lwayo, kubasebenti bahulumende labatsintseka ekutiphatseni ngalokungakalungi kwetimali noma kusetjentiswa kwemali lokungenasidzi ngo nalokusaphata imali.
tgt: isiu iye kwinkundla yamatyala ngenxa yamatyala amaninzi ukulibazisa ukuhlawulwa kwezibonelelo zomhlalaphantsi, kusalindwe iziphumo zo phando lwayo, kubasebenzi bakarhulumente abachaphazeleka kwizitenxo zemali okanye kwiinkcitho ezingenanzuzo neziyilahleko.

src: emacala lasembi kwe nkhundla yetebulungiswa lekhetsekile akhombisa kutsi usesemkhulu umsebenti lokusamele wentiwe kucinisa kwengamela imisebenti yahulumende nekuphatsa kuto tonkhe tinhlaka tembuso.
tgt: amatyala aphambi kwenkundla ekhethekileyo abonisa ukuba usemninzi umsebenzi ekusafuneka wenziwe ukuqinisa ula wulo lukarhulumente kunye nolawulo kuwo onke amasebe karhulumente.

src: akhomba kungaphumeleli lokukhulu kwetikhulu letiphendvulako kanye nekwehluleka kuhambisana nemitsetfo nemitsetfomgomo lelawula kutsengwa kwemphahla.
tgt: bachaza ukusilela okumandla kwicala lamagosa anika ingxelo kunye nokusilela ekuthobeleni imithetho nemigaqo elawula iinkqubo zokufumana abanikizinkonzo.

src: ngike ngasho phambilini kutsi kuncoba imphi yenkhohlakalo kutawuba matima, futsi kutawutsatsa sikhatsi kudzalula lentfu mbeleta leseyijulile.
tgt: ndakhe ndatsho ngaphambili ukuba ukuphumelela umlo worhwaphilizo kuza kuba nzima, kwaye kuza kutha tha ixesha ukucombulula intaphane yamagunya alawula ukuqeshwa kwabantu esele imiliselwe.

src: ngikugcizelele nekutsi kumele silwe nenkhohlakalo etinkampanini letitimele ngemandla lalinganako, ngoba kuwo wonkhe umsebenti wemkhakha wahulumende lotimisele ngekufumbatsiswa, kunasomabhizinisi lotimisele ngekufumbatsisa.
tgt: ndikwayigcinile into yokuba kufuneka silwe urhwaphilizo lwecandelo labucala ngamandla alinganayo, kuba kuye wonke umsebenzi wecandelo likarhulumente ozimiseleyo ukunyotywa, kukho usomashishini ozimiseleyo ukunyoba.

src: lobudlelwane lobu khohlakele sebumoshe bukhoni bembuso kutsi isebente ngekuya kweligunyakwenta layo.
tgt: obu budlelwane borhwaphilizo buye baphazamisa amandla karhulumente okuphumeza igunya lakhe.

src: bubuyisele emuva imitamo yembuso yekunika sive tinsita tekunakekelwa ngetekwelashwa letisezingeni lelifanele, kuphakelwa emanti lahlantekile, kanye nekucinisekisa kutfolakala kwagezi lokungenamnca muko emimangweni nakumabhizinisi.
tgt: baye babuyisela umva iinzame zombuso zokunikezela ngokhathalelo lwezempilo olundilisekileyo, ukuhambisa amanzi acocekileyo, kunye nokuqinisekisa ngonikezelo lwamandla ombane olungaguqukiyo kuluntu nakumashishini.

src: kodvwake, njengobe lenkhundla yetebulungi swa lekhetsekile seyi khombisile, siyatigucula tintfo kancanekancane.
tgt: kodwa, njengoko inkundla ekhethekileyo ibonisile, sithe chu siguqula imeko.

src: konkhe lodzinga kukwati mayelana nesitfutfwane vukuzenzele unnamed bantfu labanyenti labanesitfutfwane bangatiphilela imphilo letayelekile uma ngabe banatsa imitsi yabo baphindze futsi balawule simo sabo kahle.
tgt: konke okufuneka ukwazi malunga nesathuthwane vukuzenzele unnamed abantu abaninzi abanesathu thwane banokuphila ubomi obuqhelekileyo ukuba basela amayeza abo kwaye imeko ilawulwa kakuhle.

src: ngekusho kwadkt.

src: nhlakanipho gumede, umphatsi wetinsita tetekwelashwa esibhedlela sesigodzi iharry gwala epietermaritzburg, sitfu tfwane akusiko kungasebenti kahle kwengcondvo, sifo noma kugula, kantsi futsi asitselelwana.
tgt: uchaza ukuba isathu thwane kukuphazamiseka kwemithamboluvo okubonakaliswa zizehlo eziphindaphindanayo zesiquphe zokuphazamiseka kweemvakalelo, ukulahlekelwa yingqondo okanye ukuxhuzula, okunxulumene nomsebenzi wombane ongaqhelekanga engqondweni.

src: uchaze watsi sitfutfwa ne kungasebenti kahle kwemiva lokubonakala ngetehlakalo tekuphatamiseka kwemiva letivelenje tenteke njalonjalo, kucaleka noma kunklinklita uchwishe, lokuhambisana netenteko tagezi engco ndvweni letingakatayeleki.
tgt: "ingqondo yenziwa ziibhiliyoni zeeseli zemi thamboluvo (iineuron) ezinxibelelana ngeempawu zombane kunye nemichiza.

src: "ingcondvo inetigidzi gidzi tetinhlayinhlayi temiva (emaneurons) lachumana ngetinkhomba tagezi nemakhemikhali.
tgt: xa kukho ukukhutshwa kombane okugqithisileyo ngokukhawuleza okuphazamisa umsebenzi oqhelekileyo weeseli zemithamboluvo, kunokubangela ukuxhuzula.

src: uma ngabe kwenteka kukhululeka gezi longetulu kwelizinga lelifanele lophatamisa kusebenta lokwetayelekile kwetinhlayinhlayi temiva, umuntfu angacaleka.
tgt: "ukuxhuzula nje kube kanye akuthethi ukuba unesathuthwane.

src: "kucaleka kanye akusho kutsi unesitfutfwane.
tgt: ukuxilongwa ngugqirha kufuneka kuqini sekise oku," utshilo.

src: ngekuya kwesikhungo setesitfutfwane saseningizimu afrika, ema80% webantfu labanesitfutfwane batawukhona kulawula kucaleka kwabo ngekusebentisa umutsi.
tgt: iimbangela kunye nokuxhuzula unobangela wesathu thwane kubantu abathandathu kwabalishumi awukaziwa.

src: timbangela kanye nekucaleka timbangela tesitfutfwane kubantfu labasitfupha kulabalishumi atatiwa.
tgt: kubantu abangama40%, sinokubangelwa kukwenzakala kwentloko, ukwenzakala ngexesha lokubeleka, ukusetyenziswa kakubi kotywala kunye neziyobisi, ukuguga okanye ukuphazamiseka okanye ukungalingani ekwakhekeni komzimba okanye iikhemikhali emzimbeni.

src: kulabanye labangema40%, singabangelwa kulimala kwenhloko, kulimala nawubelekwa, tjwala nekusebentisa tidzakamiva budlabha, kuguga noma kugayeka kwekudla kube ngemandla emtimbeni nomake kuphatamiseka noma inchubo yemakhemikhali emtimbeni nekungasimami kweluhlelo lwemtimba.
tgt: ugqr gumede uthi iimpawu zesathuthwane ziyahluka, kwaye zinokubonakala ngeendlela ezahlukeneyo, kuquka ukuxhuzula okubizwa ngegeneralised absence seizures (ipetit mal), xa umntu ebonakala ngathi uhanjelwe ingqondo kwaye ethe phuhlu amehlo; ukuxhuzula okubizwa ngetonicclonic seizures (igrand mal), edla ngokuqala ngokuqina komzimba, ngaphambi kokuba umntu awe phantsi aze abeneentshukumo zokuxhuzula; kunye noku xhuzula okuyicomplex partial seizures, okuchaphazela icala lengqondo.

src: gumede utsi timphawu netinkhomba tesitfutfwane tiyehlukahlukana, kantsi futsi tingatetfula ngetindlela letinyenti letehlukahlukene, kufaka ekhatsi kucaleka lokubitwa ngeabsence seizures (ipetit mal), umuntfu abukeka alahlekile ngekwengcondvo abuke ndzawonye; kucaleka lokubitwa ngetonicclonic (igrand mal), lokucala ngekoma nekucina kwemtimba, ngembi kwekutsi umuntfu awe bese uyanklinklita; kanye nekucaleka lokubitwa ngecomplex partial seizures, lokutsikameta incenye yengcondvo.
tgt: ukuxhuzula okubizwa ngepetit mal kuthatha imizuzwana embalwa, kwaye umntu usenokungazi ukuba unako.

src: kucaleka kweluhlobo lwepetit mal kutsatsa emasekhondi lambalwa, kantsi futsi loyo muntfu logulako kungenteka angacapheli nekucaphela kutsi uhlaselekile.
tgt: ngexesha lokuxhuzula okubizwa ngegrand mal, umntu unokuba nombala oluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka emlonyeni wakhe, othi uphele xa ukuphefumla okuqhelekileyo kuqalisa kwakhona.

src: ngesikhatsi sekucaleka kwegrand mal, loyo muntfu lohlaselekile angaba nembala losasibhakabhaka kutungeleta umlomo wakhe, lobese kuyaphela uma acala kuphefumula ngalokwetayelekile.
tgt: ukuxhuzula kwegrand mal kudla ngokuthatha imizuzu embalwa.

src: luhlelo lwekudla esikolweni lucinisekisa kutsi bantfwana abalambi vukuzenzele unnamed bantfwana labangetulu kwetigidzi letiyimfica batfola kudla lokunemsoco esikolweni ngenca yeluhlelo lwahulumende lekudla etikolweni tavelonkhe (insnp), lolwacala kusebenta ngemnyaka we1994.
tgt: inkqubo yesondlo esikolweni iqinisekisa ukuba abantwana abalambi vukuzenzele unnamed bangaphezu kwezigidi ezilithoba abantwana abafumana ukutya okunesondlo ezikolweni ngenxa karhulumente ngenkqubo yesizwe yesondlo ezikolweni (insnp), eyaqaliswa ngo1994.

src: loluhlelo luhlose kutfutfukisa likhono lebantfwana lekufundza, ngekunciphisa indlala nekungondleki kahle naseku khuliseni kuta esikoleni, kakhulu etikolweni lebetincishwe ema tfuba.
tgt: le nkqubo ijolise ekuphuculeni uhlobo abantwana abafunda ngalo, ngokuthi inciphise ukungondleki, indlala kunye nehlobo abahamba ngalo isikolo, ingakumbi kwizikolo ezihlelelekileyo.

src: "loluhlelo lumcoka ekuchubekiseni emalungelo ebafundzi lakumtsetfosisekelo ekutfola kudla lokusisekelo newekutfola imfundvo lesisekelo," kuchaza lisekela lendvuna yemfundvo lesisekelo dkt reginah mhaule.
tgt: le nkqubo ibalulekile ekuqhubeleni phambili amalungelo abafundi akumgaqosiseko esondlo esisiseko kunye nemfundo esisiseko," ucacise watsho usekela mphathiswa wemfundo esisiseko ugq reginah mhaule.

src: ngenca yalensnp, banyenti bantfwana labaya ngesikhatsi esikolweni futsi labaya njalo esikolweni, futsi kugcila kwengcondvo etifundvweni kuyatfutfuka.
tgt: ngenxa yensnp, abantwana abaninzi bafika esikolweni ngexesha kwaye baya rhoqo, futhi ukuzikisa ingqondo kwabo eklasini kuye kwaphucuka.
