tgt: baphantse babe ngama3 000 oosomashishini ababhinqileyo bomzantsi afrika abasele bebhalisiwe kwiziko leshetradesza kwaye bafumana imfundo kubuxhakaxhaka be intanethi simahla kwakunye nokuxhotyiswa ngeza khono.

src: leshetradesza itawuphindza futsi yente ncono kutsi kube nekufinyelela lokuncono kulutjalomali kwemabhizinisi laphetfwe bomake kanye nekugcu gcutela ematfuba etemabhi zinisi.
tgt: ishetradesza hub iza kuphucula ukufikelela kutyalomali kumashishini aphethwe ngabasetyhini kunye nokukhuthaza amathuba oshishino.

src: singakhona futsi sitawusebenta ngemandla kute sicedze kucishwa kwagezi vukuzenzele unnamed kulamaviki lamba lwa lengcile, ku cishwa kwakhulu kwagezi ngenhloso yekuwonga kutsikamete u mnotfo wetfu futsi kwa banga bulukhuni lobu khulu kubantfu bonkhe baseningizimu afrika.
tgt: sinako kwaye singakwazi kwenza ngakumbi ukuphelisa ukucinywa kombane vukuzenzele unnamed ukunkinkishwa kombane ukusu sela kwezi veki zimbalwa zigqithileyo, kuye kwaluphazamisa uqoqosho lwethu kana njalo kwabangela ubunzi ma obugqithisileyo kubo bonke abemi bomzantsi afrika.

src: sigaba se6 sekucishwa kwagezi ngenhloso yekuwonga kwabangelwa kulahleka kwemamegawatts (emamw) langetulu kwe18 000 emandla ekuphehla ngenca yekwephuka kwemayunithi kanye nesiteleka sebasebenti bakaeskom lesingekho emtsetfweni.
tgt: inqanaba lesi6 lokunki nkishwa kombane libangelwe yilahleko engaphezulu kwe18 000 yeemegawathi (iimw) zomthamo wokuvelisa umbane, ezi megawathi zilahleke ngenxa yokuqhawuka kweeyunithi kunye nogwayimbo olungekho semthethweni lwabasebenzi bakwaeskom.

src: ngemuva kweminyaka lelishumi kunekushoda kwagezi, bantfu baseningizimu afrika bafanele kutfukutsela nekukhatsateka.
tgt: emva kweminyaka engaphezu kweshumi yokunqongophala kombane, abemi bomzantsi afrika banelungelo lokuziva bedandathekile kwaye benawo nomsindo.

src: ngetikhatsi letifanana naleti, kuvakala shengatsi lentfo ngeke ite iphele nyalo nanyalo.
tgt: kuba kaloku ngamaxesha anje, intlantsi yethemba lokuba siyakuze siphume kule ngxaki iyaphela.

src: nanome kucishwa kwagezi ngenhloso yekuwonga kubonakala shengatsi sekubi kakhulu, liciniso litsi sesitsatse tincumo letinyenti naletibalulekile tekulungisa lokushoda kwekuphakelwa kwagezi.
tgt: nangona ke kodwa imeko yokunkinkishwa kombane ibonakala iya ibambi, inyaniso yeyokuba sele sithabathe amanyathelo abalulekileyo okulungisa ukusilela ekuboneleleni ngombane.

src: lesikubeke embili lesitawucala ngako kutsi sikwente, kusimamisa luhlelo lwekuphakelwa kwagezi.
tgt: eyona nto iphambili kuthi ngoku kukuzinzisa inkqubo yombane.

src: njengaloku loluhlelo seluvuka nekuphehlwa kwagezi sekubuyela esimeni, eskom utawukhona kutsi anciphise kucishwa kwagezi ngenhloso yekuwonga kube setigabeni letiphasi.
tgt: xa inkqubo iphucuka nomthamo wokuvelisa ubuyiselwa kwimeko encumisayo, ueskom uza kukwazi ukucutha ukucinywa kombane ukuya kutsho kumanqanaba asezantsi.

src: lesivumelwane lokufinyelelwe kuso emkhatsini waeskom netinyonyana tebasebenti sitakwenta kutsi kukhonwe kulungisa loko lokumcoka kanye nekubuyisela esimeni kusebenta kwemayunithi langentiwe.
tgt: isivumelwano ekufikelelwe kuso phakathi kukaeskom nemibutho yabasebenzi siza kwenza ukuba kuqaliswe ukulu ngiswa kwaye kubuyiselwe iiyunithi ezongezelelweyo.

src: kuhanjiswa kwagezi lokusuka ecohora bassa emazambiki sekubuyiselwe esimeni futsi, lokwenta kutsi kungenteke 600 mw kugridi kanye neyunithi ye6 yasemedupi seyiyasebenta kusukela ngemgcibelo, lokukwengete lamanye ema720 mw.
tgt: intambo yothumelo esuka ecahora bassa emoza mbique sele ibuyiselwe, yongeza i600 mw kwigridi, kananjalo ngomgqibelo iyunithi 6 yasemedupi ibuyele kwakhona iyasebenza, yona yongeza enye i720 mw.

src: emayunithi langentiwe kulindzeleke kutsi asebente futsi, lokuyintfo letakwehlisa kakhulu umtfwalo wekushoda kwagezi lokukhona kwanyalo.
tgt: ezinye iiyunithi ezongezelelweyo kulindeleke ukuba nazo zibuyele , olu longezelelo luzakunceda ngakumbi ekunciphiseni lo cimicimi esijongene naye.

src: ngesikhatsi lesifanako, emaejensi ekucinisekisa kugcinwa kwemtsetfo asebenta kamatima ekulweni nekucekelwa phasi, kweba nekukhwabanisa lokwenteka kaeskom ngenhloso yekulungisa lobungoti eluhlelweni lwagezi lobubangwa nguletento tebugebengu.
tgt: kwangaxeshanye, iiarhente zogcinomthetho zisebenza nzima ukulwa nokonakaliswa, ubusela nobuqhophololo kwaeskom ukuze zizisiphule neengcambu zazo izenzo zolwaphulomthetho kwinkqubo yombane.

src: ekugcineni, lokumcoka kutsi sidzinga kutsi singete kakhulu likhono lekwenta kugridi.
tgt: ekugqibeleni kosuku, kufuneka songeze umthamo ongaphezulu kwigridi.

src: loku kutawudala kutsi eskom akhone kutsi atfole litfuba lekugcineka asesimeni lesibalulekile lesisebentako kanye nekwandzisa kwetsembeka kwetisetjentiswa takhe.
tgt: oku kuzakunika ueskom ixesha lokwenza ulungiso olubalulekileyo nokwandisa ukuthembeka kwezixhobo zakhe.

src: loko kutawuphindza futsi kwakhe sivikelo sekutsi nanome emayunithi lamanyenti angephuka ngesikhatsi sinye, leminye imitfombolusito ingasetjentiswa.
tgt: kwakhona oku kuzakwenza isithinteli esizakusebenza nokuba iiyunithi ezininzi zophuke ngexesha elinye, kodwa eminye imithombo ikwazi ukusetyenziswa.

src: lesinye setinyatselo lengasitsatsa ngemnyaka wa2018 kwaba kuvusetela luhlelo lwekutsenga emandla lavusetelelwako.
tgt: elinye lamanyathelo okuqala endawathathayo ngo2018 yayikukuvuselela inkqubo yokufumana amandla ombane ahlaziyekayo.

src: kwengeta kulokutsengwa kwemandla lamasha ekuphehla ngekusebentisa loluhlelo, kwenyuka kwemkhawulo wemvume yemiklamo yekuphehla kwafinyelela kuma100 mw kusho kutsi batjalitimali labatimele imvume kute bakhe tisetjentiswa kute tifinyelele kulobungaka.
tgt: ngale nkqubo, yokongeza ukufumana amandla ombane ahlaziyekayo, ukonyuka kobume belayisenisi yeeprojekthi zokuvelisa kabutsha ukuya kwi100 mw kuthetha ukuba akuzubakho mfuneko yamaphephamvume kubatyalizimali babucala xa befuna ukwakha amaziko okuvelisa umbane ukuya kutsho kobu bukhulu buzi 100 mw.

src: letingucuko letilula tivule emandla lamakhulu labegcinekile letako elutjalomali.
tgt: ithi ke lento, oku kuxegiswa kwamasolotya kuvula amathuba okungena kotyalo mali olukhulu .

src: eskom wente kutsi kube nemhlaba edvute netiteshi takhe temandla kute kutsi kube nelutjalomali lolutimele kumiklamo yemandla lavusetelelwako.
tgt: ueskom wenze ukuba kufumaneke umhlaba ecaleni kwezikhululo zombane ezikhoyo.

src: tindlela temadizayini setivele tiphotfuliwe kute kutsi kwentiwe ncono kusebenta kwemayunithi 1, 2 na3 asemedupi kantsi asachubeka kumayunithi 5 na6.
tgt: oku ukwenzela ukuvulela amathuba otyalomali lwabucala kwiiprojekthi zamandla ombane ahlaziyekayo.

src: nanome lolokwentiwako kubalulekile futsi kutawutsela titselo kuletinyanga letitako, akukaneli kutsi kulungiseke lenkinga lesibukene nayo.
tgt: uhlengahle ngiso loyilo lugqityiwe ukuze kuphuculwe ukusebenza kweeyunithi zemedupi 1, 2 kunye neye3 kwaye sele luqhubeka kwiyunithi 5 neye6.

src: lokukhonjiswe ngulamaviki lambalwa lengcile kutsi sidzinga kutsi sente kakhulu futsi loko sikwente ngekuphutfuma.
tgt: ngelixa lama nyathelo ebalulekile, kwaye ezakuvelisa iziqhamo kwezi nyanga zizayo, kusabonakala noko ukuba akonelanga ngokupheleleyo ukumelana nengxubakaxaka esijongene nayo.

src: asikho sizatfu sekutsi kungani live lelifanana naleletfu – lelinemakhono, emandla ekwenta kanye nemitfombolusito lesinawo – kufanele kutsi libe nekushoda kwagezi.
tgt: okubonakaliswe kwiiveki ezimbalwa ezigqithileyo kukuba kufuneka senze nangakumbi kwaye sikwenze oko ngokungxamisekileyo.

src: kulamaviki lengcile, besisebenta netindvuna letifanele kanye netikhulu mayelana netinyatselo letengetiwe kutsi sente ngekushesha yonkhe imitamo yekutsi sandzise kuphakelwa kwetfu kwagezi.
tgt: akukho sizathu sokuba ilizwe elifana nelethu – elinezakhono, amandla kunye nezibonelelo esinazo – kodwa lizifumane likwimeko yokuthwaxwa kukunqongophala kombane.

src: kufuneka sente lokutsite nyalo futsi sibambisane kucedza ludlame lolucondziswe kubomake vukuzenzele unnamed icale ngendlela lebuhlungu inyanga yabomake.
tgt: ngoku kufuneka sithathe amanyathelo sikunye ukuze siphelise ubundlobongela obujoliswe kwabasetyhini vukuzenzele unnamed ibe sisiqalo esibi kwi nyanga yabasetyhini.

src: sesiphindze sabukana nebumnyama lobubi emmangweni wetfu.
tgt: siphinde sakhunju zwa ngenkohlakalo embi egqubayo kwisizwe sakuthi.

src: kulenyanga leyengcile, licembu lemadvodza kanye nelabomake lebebatsatsa titfombe tevidiyo yemculo endzaweni leyimayini lengasasebenti edvute nase krugersdorp bahlaselwa bahlaseli labebahlomile lebahlanganyela badlengula bomake labasiphohlongo.
tgt: kwinyanga ephelileyo, iqela lamadoda nabasetyhini ababefota ividiyo yomculo kumgodi ongasasetyenziswayo kufutshane nekrugersdorp baye bahlaselwa nga bahlaseli abaxhobileyo abathi badlwengula aba basetyhini abasibhozo.

src: letentfo letimbi telunya tibukela phasi emalungelo abomake nemantfomba tane tekutsi baphile futsi basebente ngekukhululeka nangendlela levikelekile.
tgt: ezi zenzo zoyikekayo zenkohlakalo ziyindelelo kwilungelo labasetyhini nakumantombazana ukuba bahlale kwaye basebenze ngokukhululekileyo nango kukhuselekileyo.

src: ngalesikhatsi basafuna labasolwa balelicala.
tgt: ngelixa belandela abarhanelwa kolu lwa phulomthetho, inkonzo yamapolisa omzantsi afrika kufuneka inike ingqwalasela ngoko nangoko kwiinkxalabo zabahlali basewest village, apho kwenzeke khona esi sehlo, abathi bangcungcu thekiswe ngamaqela emi gulukudu exhobileyo kulo mmandla.

src: luphiko lemaphoyisa ase ningizimu afrika kufuneka lunake letikhalo temma ngo wasewest village, lapho lesigameko senteke khona, lotsi ungaphasi kwekuvinjetelwa macembu emagenge lahlomile laku lendzawo.
tgt: sihlaba ikhwelo kuluntu ukuba lusebenzisane namapolisa ukuqinisekisa ukuba aba baphulimthetho bayabanjwa kwaye batshu tshiswe.

src: badlenguli abanayo indzawo emangweni wetfu.
tgt: abantu bakuthi akufuneki bakhusele abaphulimthetho abahlala phakathi kwabo.

src: ngaso sonkhe sikha tsi kukhona umuntfu emangweni wetfu lowati lokutsite, love lokutsite noma lobone lokutsite.
tgt: kuhlala kukho umntu owaziyo into kwiindawo zethu, oyivileyo into okanye okhe wayibona into ethile.

src: inkhinga kutsi linyenti letfu likhetsa kubindza ngoba lolobhebhetsekisa ludlame ungumngani, umlingani noma umuntfu lesisebenta naye.
tgt: ingxaki kukuba uninzi lwethu lukhetha ukuthula kuba umenzi wobubi engumhlobo, eli qabane okanye engumntu osebenza naye.

src: noma simane siyasaba kutsi sitawentakaliswa.
tgt: okanye soyika nje ukwenziwa amaxhoba.

src: ku mcoka kukhumbula kutsi onkhe emathiphu latfolwe sikhungo sekulwa nebu gebengu sesaps agcinwa ayimfihlo.
tgt: kubalulekile ukukhumbula ukuba zonke iinkcukacha eziyimfihlo ezifunyenwe liziko loqha gamshelwano lesaps crime stop ziphathwa ngemfihlo.

src: ngicela wonkhe umuntfu lonelwatiso mayelana nalelicala kutsi alibike kubaphatsi kute kuboshwe labo labagangile.
tgt: ndihlaba ikhwelo kuye nabani na onolwazi ngolu lwaphulomthetho ukuba axele kwabasemagunyeni ukuze babanjwe abenzi bobubi.

src: ngenca yekukhula kwa lenkhinga kulelive lakitsi, akusakhonakali kutsi singawunaki umsebenti wetfu wekubika emacala lamayelana netemacansi.
tgt: xa kujongwa ubungaka nani bale ngxaki kwilizwe lethu, akusekho ukuphepha uxanduva lokuxela izenzo zolwaphulomthetho lokwabelana ngesondo.

src: ngekuya kwetibonelelo temtsetfo letisandza kucala kusebenta, letingeta kulokutibophelela kwe kutiphatsa kwetfu, nyalo sonkhe sinemsebenti losemtsetfweni wekubika kubaphatsi uma sinelwa tiso, sinenkholelo noma sinetinsolo letivakalako tekutsi kunelicala letema cansi lelentiwe lelibhekiswe emuntfwini lobutsakatsaka.
tgt: ngokomthetho omtsha okhoyo ngoku sonke sinoxanduva ngoko mthetho, ukongeza kweli lokuvakalelwa kwethu njengabantu, lokuchaza kwabasemagunyeni xa sinolwazi, urhano okanye sikrokrela ukuba ityala lokuxhatshazwa ngo kwesondo olenziwe kumntu osesichengeni.

src: nyalo sekulicala kungabiki lolo luhlobo lelicala letema cansi.
tgt: ngoku kukwaphulo umthetho ukungaxeli kwabasemagunyeni ityala lokuxhatshazwa ngokwe sondo komnye umntu.

src: lena ngulenye incenye yemitsetfo lemitsatfu lephasiswe ekucaleni kwa lomnyaka lekhulisa kulwa neludlame lwetebulili futsi lenika kusekela lokukhulu nekuvikeleka kulabo labasindzile kulokuhluku meteka.
tgt: lo mthetho uyinxalenye yeminye emithathu endithe ndayityikitya ekuqaleni kwalo nyaka eqinisa idabi lokulwa ubundlobongela obusekelwe kwisini kwaye unika inkxaso nokhuseleko olukhulu kumaxhoba.

src: kulokunye, lemitse tfo ikhulisa lobubanti berejista yavelonkhe yetephulamtsetfo tema cala etemacansi, ikhulisa lenchubo yekuhlola tephu lamtsetfo, kanye nekufaka letinye tinhlobo temacala etemacansi.
tgt: phakathi kwezinye izinto, imithetho yandisa umda werejista yesizwe yabaphulimthetho bokuxhaphaza nge sondo, yomeleza inkqubo yokuhlola, kwaye yazisa iindidi ezongezelelweyo zamatyala okuxhaphaza ngokwesondo.

src: tinchubo tekwenta lemitsetfo kutsi isebente tisendleleni.
tgt: iinkqubo ziyaqhubeka ukuze le mithetho isebenze.

src: loku kufaka kuceceshwa kwebashu shisi nabomantji, kunika bonkhe basebenti besaps ticondziso tekunika ibhe yili, kanye nekubuyeketa kweluhlu lwemacala kute akhone kufaka emacala lamasha lasandza kusu ngulwa.
tgt: oku kuquka uqeqesho lwabatshutshisi kunye noomantyi, ukukhutshwa kwemiyalelo ngebheyile kuwo onke amagosa esaps, nokuhlaziya amaphepha okubeka ityala ukuze aquke nezi ntlobo zintsha zamatyala.

src: siyatsemba kakhulu kutsi tonkhe letindlela time ngemumo kute basebenti bakitsi betemtsetfo neti nkhantolo bakhone kuphenya futsi bashushise ngemphumelelo lenkhulu emacala lamayelana nelu dlame lwetebulili.
tgt: sizimisele ukuba zonke ezintsika zibekhona ukuze iiarhente zeli zogcinomthetho kunye neenkundla zibenokuphanda kwaye zitshutshise ngempumelelo enkulu ubundlobongela obusekelwe kwisini.

src: ludlame lolubhekiswe kubulili lobutsite neku bulawa kwabomake kuyinkhinga lenkhulu lejule netimbandze emimangweni yetfu.
tgt: ubundlobongela obu sekelwe kwisini kunye nokubulawa kwabasetyhini yingxaki enzulu yentlalo.

src: akukaneli kutsi labo labalubhebhetselisako baboshwe, bashushiswe, balahlwe licala bese baya gwetjwa.
tgt: akwanelanga ukuba abenzi bobubi babanjwe, balaliswe eziseleni, bafu nyaniswe benetyaka baze bagwetywe.

src: kufuneka sisebentisane kute sibukane naloko loku banga ludlame lwetebulili emimangweni yetfu, lefaka ekhatsi indlela yekutiphatsa kanye nalenemikhuba leyenta emadvodza abukele phasi labasikati.
tgt: kufuneka sisebenzisane ukulwa ezi zinto ziphe mbelela ubundlobongela obusekelwe kwisini kwii ndawo esihlala kuzo, kuquka iingcinga kunye nezenzo ezikhokelisa phambili iimfuno zama doda.

src: kucedza ludlame lwe tebulili kudzinga kutsi sisebentisane sibantfu.
tgt: ukuphelisa ubundlobo ngela obusekelwe kwisini kufuna ukuba sisebenze kunye njengabantu.

src: loku kusho kutsi kufu neka sigcugcutele tindlela tekutiphatsa letikahle mayelana nekulingana kutebulili emimangweni, emasontfweni kanye nasemakhaya etfu.
tgt: oku kuthetha ukukhu thaza iingcinga ezintle malunga nokulingana ngo kwesini kwiindawo esihlala kuzo, kwiindawo zethu zonqulo nakumakhaya ethu.

src: nje ngemadvodza, kufuneka sikhombise kungakuvumeli kubandlulula ngekwebulili, singawuvumeli umcondvo wekubukela phasi labasi kati kanye neludlame lolumayelana netebulili ngendlela lesiphatsa ngayo balingani betfu, labo lesise benta nabo, bomake, bosesi kanye nemadvodzakati etfu.
tgt: njengamadoda, kufuneka sibonise uku nganyamezeli kwethu ucalucalulo ngokwesini, umkhuba wokukhoke lisa phambili iimfuno zamadoda kunye nobu ndlobongela obusekelwe kwisini kwindlela esi phatha ngayo amaqa bane ethu, oogxa bethu, oomama, oodade kunye neentombi zethu.

src: kungaba muntfu nga munye, noma tinhlangano, emabhizinisi noma bacashi, kufuneka sibe yincenye yemitamo yavelonkhe ngayo yonkhe indlela lesingakhona ngayo, kungaba kuvolontiya esikhungweni sekuhlalisa labaswele, singasekela emacembu emmango lasebentisana nemaphoyisa noma ngekuhlanganyela kumikhankaso yemicimbi letsite etikolweni takitsi.
tgt: nokuba kungabantu ngabanye, yimibutho, ngamashishini okanye abaqeshi, kufuneka sibe yinxalenye yeenzame zesizwe ngazo zonke iindlela esinokuba nazo, nokuba kukuvolontiya kwindawo yokuhlala, sixhasa amaqonga amapo lisa asekuhlaleni okanye sizibandakanye namaphulo okufundisa ezikolweni zethu.

src: ematfuba emfundzate kubantfu labasha kgaogelo letsebe sonia malinga (23) wasepiet retief empumalanga utsi kutfola umfundzate lovela kushoprite group kucinisekise kutsi utawu ba nelikusasa lelitsembi sako.
tgt: amathuba enkxasomali yemfundo kubantu abatsha kgaogelo letsebe usonia malinga (23) wasepiet retief empu malanga uthi ukubangu mxhamli wenkxasomali yemfundo yakwashopri te group kuqinisekise ikamva eliqaqambileyo kuyeumalinga wafumana inkxasomali yemfundo kumthengisi wasemza ntsi afrika ngowama 2018. wafaka isicelo senkxasomali yemfundo emva kokugqiba amaba nga esikolo esiphakami leyo ehoërskool piet retief.

src: malinga utfole lomfu ndzate kulesitolo se kutsengisa saseningi zimu afrika ngemnyaka we2018.
tgt: "ekukhuleni kwam, ndandifuna ukuba ngugqirha, kodwa kamva ndaqalisa ukuhlola ezi nye iindlela.

src: ufake sicelo salomfundzate emva kwekuphotfula imfundvo yemabanga lasetulu ehoerskool piet retief.
tgt: ndifunde malunga nokulandelelana kweenkqubo ezibanda kanyekayo ekuvelisweni nasekuhanjisweni kwe mpahla yorhwebo kwaye ndaphantse ndatsaleleka ngoko nangoko kuyo.

src: "ngisakhula, ngacala ngafuna kuba ngudo kotela, kodvwa kamuva ngacala kubuka letinye tintfo.
tgt: ndikhumbula ukuba ndandidla ngokuhlala ndibukele iilori zingena ziphuma kwidolophu yasekhaya kwaye ndi zibuza ukuba ngubani owayeqinisekisa ukuba umgangatho kunye nobu ninzi beempahla zicha nekile kwanokuba zifika kwindawo yokuhanjiswa echanekileyo kusini na.

src: kungaleso sikhatsi lapho ngacala kuba nelutsandvo lalo msebenti," kusho ma linga.
tgt: kulapho ndafumana khona uthando lwam," utshilo umalinga.

src: malinga watfola ticu tebcom honours kute kulawula kuhanjiswa kwemphahla enyuni vesi yasejohannesburg wabese ucala kusebenta eshoprite njengemphatsi wesikhungo losafundza abe aceceshwa ngendlo vana 2021. nyalo losesi usandza kukhushulelwa esikhundleni sekuba ngumhlatiyi weku gcwaliswa kabusha kwe mphahla.
tgt: umalinga ufumene isidanga sebcom ho nours kwilogistics ma nagement kwiyunivesithi yasejohannesburg waza waqala umsebenzi wakhe kwashoprite njengoma nejala oqeqeshwayo kwi ziko lokuhanjiswa kwe mpahla kweyomdumba wama2021.

src: kuba yincenye yeshoprite group kukhulise lwati lamalinga kule mboni yetekutsengisa.
tgt: kutshanje uye wanyuselwa ukuba abe ngumhlalutyi wola wulo nohanjiso lwarhoqo lwempahla.

src: "kungifundzisile kakhulu futsi nangalokungetiwe mayelana netekulawula kuhanjiswa kwemphahla nangekungenta kutsi ngichubeke nekutfu tfukisa emakhono ami nangekutsi ngikhule emsebentini wami," usho njalo losesi.
tgt: ukuba yinxalenye yeshoprite group kulwenze banzi ulwazi lukamali nga ngeshishini loku thengisa.

src: usifaka njani sicelo kufaka ticelo teluhlelo lwemfundzate lofaka konkhe weshoprite group kuvuliwe kumnya ka wekufundza we2023.
tgt: "kundifundise nangakumbi ngolawulo lokuhanjiswa kwempahla kwaye kundenze ukuba ndiqhubeke ndiphuhlisa izakhono zam kwaye ndi qhubele phambili nomse benzi wam," utshilo.

src: indlela lensha yekulwa nenkhohlakalo itfola imiphumela lemihle vukuzenzele unnmaed kulwa nenkhohlakalo kudzinga sandla setepolitiki lesicinile kanye netikhungo, letitimele, letikhonako kulwa nebugebengu.
tgt: indlela entsha yokulwa urhwaphilizo ifumana iziphumo vukuzenzele unnamed umlo wokulwa urhwaphilizo ufuna zombini intando eqinileyo yezo politiko kunye namaziko azimeleyo anako ukulwa ulwaphulomthetho.

src: enkhulumeni yami yekucala yebunjalo belive, nga2018, ngenta sifungo sekutinikela kutsi ngigucule simo setenkhohlakalo eti khungweni tetfu ngiphi ndze futsi ngilwe neku khwabanisa nekubambisana ngenhloso lembi emkhakhe ni lotimele ngemandla ne nhloso lefananako.
tgt: kwintetho yobume besizwe yam yokuqala, ngowama2018, ndenza isibophelelo sokuguqula imeko ngokuchasene no rhwaphilizo kumaziko ethu oluntu kunye nokulwa ubuqhophololo kunye nentsebenziswano kwicandelo labucala ngendlela eqatha nene njongo efanayo.

src: kusukela ngaleso sikhatsi, siloku sisebenta ngeku tikhandla kute sicinise siphindze futsi sisekele emaejensi etfu nalaha mbisana nawo lacinisekisa kutfotjelwa kwemtsetfo.
tgt: ukusukela ngoko, besi sebenza nzima ukomeleza kunye nokuxhasa ukutho tyelwa komthetho kunye neearhente ezinxulume neyo.

src: sakhe luphiko lwete kuphenya kumtimba wavelonkhe wetekushu shisa kute kutsi libukane nenkhohlakalo lenemandla nekutsi inkantolo lekhetse kile yente luphiko lwete kuphenya lolukhetsekile (isiu) ikhone kuvumbulula kakhulu futsi kalula timali letintjontjiwe.
tgt: siye saseka ulawulo lwegunya lotshutshiso lwesizwe ukuze lujongane norhwaphilizo olunobu zaza kunye nenkundla yamatyala ekhethekileyo ukuze icandelo lophando elikhethekileyo (isiu) likwazi ukubuyisa kwa khona iimali ezibiweyo.

src: siphindze futsi sasita ngekwesekela nekunika imitfombolusito imitimba lebalulekile lelwa nebugebengu njengelu phiko lwekudla imphahla, luphiko lolukhetsekile lwetebugebengu beteku tsengisa kanye neluphiko lwekuphenya bugebengu lobuhamba embili, lolubitwa ngekutsi ngemahawks .
tgt: sikwanikezele ngenkxaso kunye nezibonelelo kwamanye amaqumrhu abalulekileyo okulwa ulwaphulomthetho afana necandelo lokuthinjwa kwempahla, icandelo lolwaphulomthetho elikhethekileyo lwezo rhwebo kunye necandelo lophando lolwaphulomthetho eliphakamileyo, elaziwa ngokuba ngoo khetshe.

src: lemitamo inemiphumela lemihle.
tgt: ezi nzame zivelisa izi phumo.

src: ngekusebentisana netinhlaka letibalulekile eluhlelweni lwetebulu ngiswa kutebugebengu, luphiko lwetekuphenya selubhalise emacala enkhohlakalo langetulu kwalange20 kulomnyakati mali lophelile kwaphindze futsi kwaboshwa basolwa labange65.
tgt: ngentsebenziswano namaqumrhu aphambili kwinkqubo yobulungisa kulwaphulomthetho, icandelo lophando libhalise ngaphezulu kwamatyala orhwaphilizo angama20 kunyakamali odlulileyo kwaye aba tyholwa abangama65 baye bamangalelwa.

src: loku kufaka ekhatsi emacala lamanyenti 'ekubanjwa kwembuso ngabhongwane' kanye nalamanye emacala enkho hlakalo lamatima.
tgt: ezi zinto ziquka 'ukubanjwa kombuso ngobhongwane' kunye namanye amatyala orhwaphilizo anobuzaza.

src: kulomnyakatimali lophe lile, luphiko lwekudla imphahla lwatfola imiyalelo yekuvala emaakhawunti lalinganiselwa kutigidzi gidzi letir5.4 letiphatselene nemacala enkhohlakalo, kwatsi tigidzi letinger70 tafakwa esikhwameni semphahla yebugebengu levunjululiwe.
tgt: kulo nyakamali uphelileyo, icandelo lo kuthinjwa kwempahla lifumene imiyalelo yo kuthintelwa ekusetye nzisweni kwempahla exabisa iibhiliyoni zeerandi eziyi5.4 ezinxulumene namatyala olwaphulomthetho, apho izigidi zeerandi ezingama70 zihlawulwe kwingxowamali yokubuyisa impahla yolwaphulomthetho.

src: kuleminyaka lesipho hlongo leyendlulile, isiu ivumbulule timali nempha hla leyenta tigidzigidzi letir2.6 yaphindze futsi yancamula emakontileka lenta tigidzigidzi letir18.
tgt: kule minyaka isibhozo idlulileyo, isiu iye yafu mana inkxasomali kunye neempahla ezixabisa ibhiliyoni zeerandi eziyi2.6 yaza yabekela bucala iikhontrakthi ezixabisa ibhiliyoni zeerandi ezili18.

src: isiu seyibhalise enkantolo lekhetsekile linani lemacala la119 lenta ngetulu kweti gidzigidzi letir13.
tgt: amatyala ali119 ewonke axabisa ngaphezulu kweebhiliyoni zeerandi ezili13 abhaliswe kwisiu kwinkundla yamatyala ekhethekileyo.

src: inkhohlakalo licala lelima tima kakhulu kulishushisa.
tgt: urhwaphilizo lulwaphulomthetho oluntsonkothileyo ekufu neka lutshutshiswe.

src: babhebhetseli batikha ndla ngalokukhetsekile ekuvaleni imikhondvo yabo.
tgt: abenzi bobubi benza imigudu emangalisayo yokugquma imikhondo yabo.

src: bavula tinkampani letingasebenti tekutsi bafihle kuto imisebenti yabo lesolisako, njalonje bahambisa imali emkhatsini wemaakhawunti lama nyenti, betfule kubemtselo imalingena lengasiyo, futsi, basebenti bahulumende, basebentisa bangani nema lunga emndeni kutsi bafake ticelo temathenda kute kutsi bafihle kubandzakanyeka kwabo.
tgt: baseka iinkampani ezisemthethweni nezi ngasebenziyo ukufihla iintengiselwano ezingalu nganga, bethubelezisa iimali ngokukhawuleza phakathi kweeakhawunti ezininzi, ezibonakalisa ingeniso ngendlela enge yiyo kumagunya erhafu, kwaye, kwimeko yabase benzi bakarhulumente, basebenzisa izihlobo nezalamane ukufaka izicelo zeethenda ukufihla uku bandakanyeka kwabo.

src: lokuke kusho kutsi kuphendvula kwetiphatsi mandla nako kufanele kutsi kube ngulokushubile.
tgt: oku kuthetha ukuba impendulo yabasema gunyeni kufuneka ibe nobugocigoci.

src: nga2020, sasungula sikhungo ifusion centre lesimkhakhaminyenti saba sikhungo sekusebentela kute kutsi kubukwane nemacala ebugebengu lahamba embili, kufaka ekhatsi inkhohlakalo.
tgt: ngowama2020, siseke iziko ifusion centre eline zinto ezininzi enjengeziko lokusebenzela ukulungi sa ulwaphulomthetho oluphambili kwezemali, kuquka urhwaphilizo.

src: lesikhungo sihlanganisa emakhono ekuphenya etinhlaka tahulumende tekuvimbela bugebengu kanye netekuphepha kanye nalawo esikhungo sebunhloli kutetimali, lesi tfutfukisa tebunhloli kute kutsi tikhungo temtsetfo tiyisebentise eluphenyweni lwato.
tgt: eli ziko lidibanisa ndawonye amandla ophando othintelo lolwaphulomthetho kunye namaqumrhu okhuseleko karhulumente kunye nalawo eziko lezobuntlola bezezimali, eliphuhlisa ubuntlola ukuze iiarhente zogcinomthetho zibuse benzise kuphando lwazo.

src: eminyakeni lemibili kusukela kwasungulwa ifusion centre , indlela yaso lemkhakhaminyenti ‘yekulandzela imali’ ibe nemiphumela lemihle lemikhulu kakhulu.
tgt: iminyaka emibini ukususela ekusekweni kwefusion centre , indlela yalo ebandakanya abantu abavela kwiintlobo ezahlukeneyo zomsebenzi ‘yokulandela imali’ iye yavelisa iziphumo ezibalu lekileyo.

src: kulomnyakatimali lophe lile, umsebenti wefusion centre usekele luphenyo lwenkhohlakalo neku khwabanisa lolunge276.
tgt: kulo nyakamali upheli leyo, umsebenzi wefusion centre uxhase uphando lobuqhophololo norhwa philizo olungama276.

src: tigidzi letilinganiselwa kuletinger659 tabuyi selwa kuhulumende ngekusebentisa kulondvo lota nekuvumbulula inzuzo yebugebengu.
tgt: malunga nezigidi zeerandi ezingama659 zabuyiselwa kurhulumente ngendlela yokulondoloza kunye nokubuyiswa kwengeniso yolwaphulomthetho.

src: kulinganiselwa kutigidzi letinger613 letavalwa lekusolwa kutsi tinzuzo tebugebengu.
tgt: malunga nezigidi zeerandi ezingama613 eziyinge niso yolwaphulomthetho olurhanelwayo ziye zathi ntelwa ekusetyenzisweni.

src: ifusion centre ekucaleni kwayo yasungulelwa kuphenya inkhohlakalo lephatselene nekutsengwa kwetintfo tecovid19 .
tgt: ifusion centre ekuqaleni yamiselwa ukuphanda urhwaphilizo olumalunga nenkqubo yokufumana abanikizinkonzo enxu lumene necovid19 .

src: manje umsebenti wayo sewukhulisiwe kute kutsi ufake ekhatsi kuphenya kushushunjiswa kwemali, kukhwabanisa, kulawula budlabha, kwesekela nge timali emaphekula kanye nalamanye emacala ebuge bengu labucayi.
tgt: umyalelo wayo ngoku uyandiswa ukuze uquke ukuthutyeleziswa kwemali, ubuqhophololo, ulawulo olugwenxa, inkxasomali yabanqolobi kunye nolunye ulwaphulomthetho lwezemali olunobuzaza.

src: emahawks asandza kwendlala letinye tinchube kelembili letentiwe licembu lelilwa nenkhohlakalo, ifusion centre lebe yincenye yako.
tgt: ookhetshe kutsha nje bachaze enye yenkqubelaphambili esele yenziwe liqela lokulwa urhwa philizo, apho ifusion centre iba yinxalenye yalo.

src: emkhatsini wemnya katimali wanga2019 nanga2022, kuboshwe basolwa labange554 baboshelwa inkhohlakalo, kwatsi laba142 babo balahlwa licala.
tgt: phakathi konyakamali wama2019 kunye nowama2022, abarha nelwa abangama554 babanjelwa urhwaphilizo, apho abali142 kubo baye bagwetywa.

src: lelinye lithulusi lebunhloli lelibalulekile kulucwa ningo lwendlela yekuphila lolwentiwe luphiko lwe kugcogcwa kwemtselo lwaseningizimu (yisars).
tgt: esinye isixhobo esi balulekileyo sobuntlola kwezemali luphicothozi ncwadi lwendlela yoku phila olwenziwa yinkonzo yerhafu yomzantsi afrika (isars).

src: kulomnyaka lophelile, isars iphotfule lucwa ningo lwendlela yekuphila lolunge25 lolowenta tigidzi letinger450 kusombulula emagebe emkhatsini wemali lengenako ledzalulwako nendlela yekuphila yemuntfu.
tgt: kulo nyaka uphelileyo, isars igqibe uphicothozincwadi lwendlela yokuphila olungama25 oluxabisa ngaphezulu kwezigidi zeerandi ezingama450 ukusombulula ukunga ngqinelani phakathi kwengeniso echaziweyo kunye nendlela yokuphila yomntu.

src: kuyacaca kutsi letinyatselo letitsetfwe ngulolulawulo kubuyisela emandla, likhono nekuncomeka kwetikhungo letilwa nekhohlakalo tinemphu mela lobonakalako lomuhle kakhulu.
tgt: kucacile ukuba amanya thelo esiwathathileyo njengolu lawulo lokubu yisela amandla okwenza, ubuchule kunye nokuthe mbeka kwamaziko aba ndakanyekayo kumlo wokulwa norhwaphilizo zinempembelelo ebona kalayo.

src: lomsebenti lohlanga nisiwe wawo onkhe lamaejensi lacinisekisa kutfotjelwa kwemtsetfo ubamba tigebengu lapho titincane ngakhona: emakhikhini ato.
tgt: umsebenzi olungele lanisiweyo wazo zonke iiarhente zokunyanze liswa komthetho ubetha abaphulimthetho apho kubuhlungu kakhulu khona: kwiipokotho zabo.

src: timali tahulumende letaphangwa tabese tihanjiswa ngaletinye tindlela tiyavunjululwa kantsi futsi labo labatsintse kako mayelana naleto tento bashushiswa tinkantolo.
tgt: iimali zoluntu ebezityhu thuliwe zaza zajikiselwa kwelinye icala ziyabuyiswa kwaye abo banoxanduva lwezi zenzo bayatshutshi swa ziinkundla zethu zamatyala.

src: caphela timphawu letisheshe tivele tamdlavuta wasebuntfwaneni more matshediso kungacapheli mdlavuta wase buntfwaneni kanye netinkhomba tawo kusho kutsi bantfwana labanyenti baseningizimu afrika ngesikhatsi batfolakala kutsi banalesifo sisuke sesisezi ngeni leliphakeme.
tgt: jonga iimpawu zokuqala zomhlaza wasebuntwaneni more matshediso ukunqongophala kolwazi ngomhlaza wasebuntwaneni kunye neempawu zawo kuthetha ukuba abantwana abaninzi basemzantsi afrika baxilongwa xa isifo sikwi nqanaba eliphezulu.

src: uma ngabe mdlavuta usheshe watfolakala wabese uyelashwa, ematfuba ekwelulama ngalokuphelele abasetulu.
tgt: umhlaza osaqalayo uyaxi longwa kwaye unyangwe, liphezulu ithuba lokuchacha ngokupheleleyo.

src: umchumanisi wenhlangano yaseningi zimu afrika yamdlavuta wasebuntfwaneni (ichoc) taryn seegers utsi ngekwati timphawu tamdlavuta kubantfu labancane, unga sita usindzise imphilo.
tgt: umququzeleli wonxi belelwano lwechildhood cancer foundation south africa (ichoc) utaryn seegers uthi ngokwazi iimpawu ezixhaphakileyo zomhlaza kulutsha, kunganceda ukusindisa ubomi.

src: "timphawu netinkhomba kungaba matima kutibona emkhatsini wemaguludla, imitfubulela, timila kanye nekuntjintjantjintja kwemiva.
tgt: "iimpawu kunye nemi qondiso kunokuba nzima ukuzibona phakathi kwa maqhuma aqhelekileyo, imigruzuko, ukukhula ngokukhawuleza kunye nokuguquguquka kwesi mo sengqondo.

src: nanoma kunjalo, kutfolakala kwato kubalule kile kakhulu," kusho yena.
tgt: nangona kunjalo, ukufunyaniswa kwangethuba kubalulekile," utshilo.

src: ngekuya kwenhlangano yaseningizimu afrika yetamdlavuta (icansa), njalo ngemnyaka bantfwana baseningizimu afrika labatfolakala banamdla vuta basemkhatsini walabange800 kuya kulaba 1 000. nanoma kunjalo, lenhlangano ilinganisela ekutsini ihhafu yalaba ntfwana eningizimu afrika abatfolwa.
tgt: ngokwengxelo yecancer association of south africa (icansa), baphakathi kwama800 ukuya kwi 1 000 abantwana base mzantsi afrika abaxilo ngelwa umhlaza kunyaka ngamnye.

src: kwenta siciniseko sekutsi mdlavuta ubonwa masinyane, ichoc yenta tinhlelo tekucaphelisa emimangweni, itjela batali nebantfwana ngetimphawu letisheshe tibekhona teku caphelisa labafanele kutsi baticaphele.
tgt: nangona kunjalo, lo mbutho uqikelela ukuba isiqingatha sabantwana aba nomhlaza emzantsi afrika abazange baxilongwa.

src: lenhlangano yesekela bantfwana nebantfu labasha labanamdlavuta noma tifo tengati letisongela imphilo kanye nemindeni yabo.
tgt: ukunceda ukuqinisekisa ukuba umhlaza ubonwe ngokukhawuleza, ichoc iqhuba iinkqubo zokwa zisa uluntu, ixelela abazali nabantwana ngeempawu ezilumkisa kwangethuba ekufuneka baziqaphele.

src: "sihlose kusheshe sisi bone lesifo bese siselapha ngemphumelelo.
tgt: eliziko lixhasa abantwa na kunye nolutsha olunomhlaza okanye olu nokuphazamiseka kwegazi okusongela ubomi kunye neentsapho zabo.

src: nanoma ngunini, ichoc ingana kekela bantfwana nebantfu labasha labangetulu kwalaba1 500, ibe futsi yesekela ngekwetengcondvo nangekwetenhlalo imindeni lengetulu kwale1 500," kusho seegers.
tgt: "sijonge ukuphucula ukufunyaniswa kwange thuba kwaye siququzelele unyango olusebenzayo.

src: kulomnyakatimali lophe lile, seegers utsi ichoc yakhona kutfula tinsita kubantfwana laba1 724, bantfu labasha laba553 kanye nebantfu labadzala laba2 232 ngetinhlelo tayo letingumgogodla.
tgt: nangaliphi na ixesha, ichoc inokuba nabantwa na abangaphezulu kwe 1 500 kunye nolutsha kukhathalelo lwayo, ngelixa inika inkxaso ngokwasengqondweni nangokwasentlalweni kwiintsapho ezingaphe zulu kwe1 500," utshilo useegers.

src: "tinsita tetfu tifaka ekhatsi kwesekelwa ngekwemiva ngesikhatsi basesebukene namdlavuta, kudvudvutwa, kunakekelwa kwaseku pheleni kwemphilo kanye nekwesekelwa uma sewu shonelwe," kusho seegers.
tgt: kunyakamali ophelileyo, useegers uthi ichoc ikwazile ukunceda aba ntwana abali1 724, ulutsha olungama553 kunye nabantu abadala abangama2 232 ngee nkqubo zayo ezingundoqo.

src: timphawu tast siluan tamdlavuta wasebuntfwaneni s – funa lusito lwetekwe lashwa kusenesikhatsi lwetinkhomba letichube kako.
tgt: "iinkonzo zethu ziquka inkxaso yeemvakalelo ngendlela yohambo lwabo lomhlaza, intuthuzelo, ukhathalelo lokuphela kobomi kunye nenkxaso yokuzila," utshilo useegers.

src: i – licashata lelimhlo phe esweni, kufica liso lokusha, kungaboni emehlweni lokuvelenje kwenteke ngekushesha noma kukhukhumuka kwendvumbu yeliso.
tgt: iimpawu zomhlaza wasebuntwaneni zest siluan s – funa uncedo lwe zonyango kwangethuba ngeempawu eziqhube kayo.

src: l – sigadla esiswini, engculwini, enhloko, emkhonweni, emile nteni, emasendzeni noma emandlaleni.
tgt: i ibala elimhlophe elisweni, ukufifithekisa, ukungaboni ngequbu liso, ikhozo lweliso elithe phuhlu.

src: kutfutfukiswa kwen3 kutfutfukisa bantfu baseningizimu afrika owen mngadi mduduzi jijana longumnikati wenhlangano letfutfukisa labaphila nekukhubateka, lekungulenye yetinkapani letizuzako nyalo kula mabhiliyoni lar26 ekutfutfukisa umgwaco lomkhulu in3 emkhatsini kwemgungundlovu nasethekwini kwazulunatali.
tgt: uphuculo lwen3 luxhobisa abemi bomzantsi afrikaezempilo owen mngadi umduduzi jijana ongumnini wombutho wokuxho tyiswa kwabakhubazekileyo, sithetha nje inkampani yakhe ingenye yeenkampani ezixhamlayo kolu phuculo oluxabisa ir26 yeebhiliyoni olwenziwa kuhola wendlela un3 pha kathi komgungundlovu nasethekwini kwiphondo lakwakwazulunatal.

src: lomklamo, loholwa yisouth afri can national road agency soc limited (isanral), icinisekisa kutsi bosomabhizinisi labafana najijana abagcini kuphela ngekuzuza kodvwa baphindze bavulele labanye ematfuba emsebenti.
tgt: eli phulo, nelikhokelwa yisouth afri can national road agency soc limited (isanral), liqinisekisa ukuba oosomashishini abafana nojijana abaxhamli nje kuphela kodwa bakwadala amathuba emisebenzi eluntwini.

src: jijana, lophila nekukhubateka, utsi inkapani yakhe isebenta kufaka timphawu temgwaco emkhatsini kwasehilton nasemgungundlovu.
tgt: ujijana, nophila nokukhubazeka, uthi umsebenzi wenkampani yakhe kukufaka iimpawu zendlela phakathi kwehilton ukuya emgungundlovu.

src: ucashe bantfu laba13 futsi utsi lomklamo sewutiguculile timpilo tabo.
tgt: uqeshe abantu abalishumi eline sithathu kwaye uthi le projekthi ibutshintshile ubomi babo.

src: "njengebantfu lesiphila nekukhubateka, sikhombisile kutsi natsi sinelikhono.
tgt: "njengabantu abaphila nenkubazeko, sizibonakalisile ukuba nathi siyakwazi ukusebenza njengamntu wonke.

src: senta umsebenti wangemphela," kusho jijana.
tgt: asisaxhomekekanga kwizibonelelo nje kwaphela," utshilo ujijana.

src: umphatsi waloluhlelo lwesanral n3 tshepo matekane utsi inkapani yakhe icinisekisile kutsi umse benti lo30% waniketwa tinkapani tendzawo letinelikhono lekwenta imisebenti letitsite.
tgt: umphathi wenkqubo yakwasanral n3 utshepo matekane uthi usanral uye waqinisekisa ukuba umsebenzi okumyinge wama30% wabelwe iinkampani zasekuhlaleni ezikwaziyo ukunika iinkonzo ezahlukeneyo.

src: loku kwavula ematfuba lamanengi kumabhizinisi lamancane laphetfwe lusha, bantfu lebebacindzetelekile kanye nabomake.
tgt: oku kudale amathuba amaninzi kumashishini amancinci aphantsi kolutsha, abantu ababesaziwa njengabahleleleki leyo kwilixa langaphambili kwakunye nabasetyhini.

src: "kunemabhizinisi la108 lamancane, lasemkhatsini nalasafufusa kungunyalo lasebenta kumiklamo lehlukahlukene," usho njalo.
tgt: "kungoku nje kukho amashishini amancinci, aphakathi kwakunye nalawo aqhutywa ngumntu omnye alinani la108 asebenza kwiiprojekthi ezahlukeneyo," uqhube watsho.

src: nokuthula zondi weingqalabutho yamalinda multipurpose trading waniketwa inkontileka yekuphakela umhlaba nekufaka emaphayiphi ekuhambisa emanti.
tgt: unokuthula zondi weingqalabutho yamalinda multipurpose trading wanikwa umsebenzi wokunikezela ngomhlaba kunye nokufakela imibhobho yokufunxa amanzi.

src: utsi inkapani yakhe icashe bantfu laba8 labanemakhono, labafaka ekhatsi bashayeli.
tgt: uthi inkampani yakhe iqeshe abase benzi abasibhozo abanezakhono, kuquka nabaqhubi.

src: zondi ungete watsi bomake nabo banelikhono njengabo babe futsi inkapani yakhe inemlandvo lomuhle wekwenta umsebenti.
tgt: uzondi wongeza ngelithi, abasetyhini nabo banabo ubuchule njengamadoda kwaye inkampani yakhe izakhele igama elihle ngokunikezela ngeenkonzo.

src: "siyakuvisisa lokubaluleka kwesikhatsi nekugcina sikhatsi lesibekiwe kute sicinisekise kutsi umklamo uhamba kahle ngalokufanelekile.
tgt: "siyakuqonda ukubaluleka kwexesha kwaye sihlangabezana nayo yonke imimiselo esiyinikiweyo eqinisekisa ukuba iprojekthi iqhuba ngokufanele kileyo.

src: sibonga kutfola lelitfuba futsi sitsemba kutsi kukhulu lesitakutfola kute sikhulise inkapani yetfu ihambi sane nemazinga etekwakha," wangeta ngekusho njalo lomake.
tgt: siyalivuyela eli thuba kwaye sinethemba lokuba kusekuninzi okuzayo, ukuze inkampani yethu nayo ikwazi ukukhula ngokwamanqanaba okwakha," wongeze watsho.

src: imiklamo lemcoka yahu lumende wavelonkhe matekane utsi lomklamo wekutfutfu kisa lobitwa ngekutsi yidurbanfree state logistics and industrial corridor unesilinganiso sesabelotimali lesitigidzigidzi ler26 futsi ungu lomunye wemiklamo lomcoka wendlelalisu lehlangene yahulu mende wavelonkhe.
tgt: iiprojekthi ezingundoqo zikarhulumente wesizwe umatekane uthi uphuhliso lwedurbanfree stategauteng logistics and industrial corridor lunohlahlo lwabiwomali oluqikelelwa kwiibhili yoni zeerandi ezingama26 kwaye yenye yeeprojekthi zobuchule ezingundoqo ezihlanganisiweyo zikarhulumente.

src: watiwa ngekutsi yisip2.
tgt: le projekthi ke ibizwa ngokuba yisip2.

src: lo mklamo utawuvula umgwaco in3 kutsi ube naleminye imizila eluhlangotsini ngalunye.
tgt: le projekthi izakwandisa in3 nge minye imizila kwicala ngalinye.

src: uphindze umbandzakanye kuguculwa kwe kuchumana kwemigwaco lemikhulu kute kutfutfukiswe kuhamba kahle kwetigitjelwa nangekukhululeka.
tgt: kwaye izakutshintsha iindlela zokungenelela ezinkulu ukuze kuphuculwe uxinano ekuhambeni kwezithuthi.

src: sigaba lesitsintsekako semgwaco in3 kuleminyaka leyengcile besine kumphintjana kwetigitjelwa, kakhulu ngetikhatsi letiphitsitelako ngoba linyenti letitfutsi temitfwalo lemikhulu letichamuka elugwini lasethekwini tisebentisa lomgwaco kuya egauteng nakuletinye tifundza letisemkhatsini kwalelive.
tgt: kwiminyaka egqithileyo icandelo elichaphazelekayo kun3 belino kuxinana kwezithuthi, ingakumbi ngexesha leeyure apho wonke umntu esendleleni, oku kungenxa yokuba uninzi lwelori zemithwalo ezisuka kwizibuko lasethekwini zisebenzisa uhola wendlela oya egauteng nakwa manye amaphondo angaphakathi elizweni.

src: futsi bekuba netingoti temgwaco letinengi letibangwa bashayeli betitfutsi temtfwalo ngenca yekunganakekeli uma bahamba lapho kune majika lamakhulu.
tgt: kukwakho nenani elikhulu leengozi ezindleleni ezibangelwa kukungak hathali kwabaqhubi belori ezithwele imithwalo xa beqhuba kuma jikojiko endlela.

src: "akusiko kuphela kugcwala kwetitfutsi kwamalanga onkhe lokwenta kutsi tigitjelwa tihambe kahle lokusunjululiwe nga lokwakha imizila lengetiwe, kutfutfukiswa kwen3 kutawenta kutsi kwenyuke tekuphepha.
tgt: "ngaphandle kokusombu lula uxinzelelo lokuxinana olwenziwa zizithuthi ngokuthi kongezwe eminye imizila, ukuphu culwa kwen3 kukwazisa nokwanda kokhuseleko.

src: emajika lama khulu lasabekako atawu suswa.
tgt: amajikojiko ayingozi azakuqondiswa.

src: timphambano mgwaco letingakaphephi titawuhlelwa kabusha," kusho matekane.
tgt: iindlela ezingakhuselekanga ziza kuhlengahlengiswa," utshilo umatekane.

src: isanral inikete tinkhontileka letintsatfu kulekota leyengcile yemnyaka we2021 umsebenti wacala kwentiwa emkhatsini kwabhimbi dvwane namabasa.
tgt: kwikota yokugqibela ka2021, isanral inikezele ngeekhontrakthi ezinta thu, kwaye umsebenzi wokwakha waqala phakathi kwenyanga yomqungu nekatshazimpunzi.

src: tincenye letitfutfukiswako nyalo sigaba semgwaco lomakhi lomitha (km) la19 losuka ecato ridge ufike edarda nelles, lowatiwa ngekutsi ngumgwaco iumlaas; sigaba semgwaco lesi20.6 km losuka edardanelles inter change kuya elynnfield park; kanye nesigaba semgwaco lesi30km losuka elynnfield park uye eashburton inter change.
tgt: ama candelo alungiswayo ngoku yi19 yeekhilomitha (km) ukusuka ecato ridge ukuya edardanelles, eyaziwa ngokuba yiumlaas road; icandelo leekhilomitha ezingama26.6 ukusuka kudardanelles interchange ukuya elynnfield park; kunye neekhilomitha ezingama30 ukusuka elynnfield park ukuya kwiashburton interchange.

src: matekane utsi isip2 itawukhulisa lomgwaco weti gitjelwa newetekutfutswa kwemphahla losemkhatsini kwemahabhu etimboni la mcoka aseningizimu afrika, itawutfutfukisa kufinyelela kutinsita tekuhanjiswa nekunge niswa kwemphahla letisethekwini futsi itawu khuphula lizinga lekusebenta ngendlela lekahle kule phaseji.
tgt: umatekane ucacisa uthi isip2 iza kuqinisa ukuthuthwa kweempahla kunye nendlela yezothutho ephakathi kweendawo eziphambili zemizimveliso yasemzantsi afrika, kananjalo iphucule ukufikelela kuncedo lokuthunyelwa kwempahla kumazwe angaphandle ethekwini kunye noku nyusa ukusebenza kakuhle kwale ndlela.

src: ungete ngekutsi lomklamo uyincenye yeluhlelo lwavelonkhe lwentfu tfuko lwemnyaka we2030 neluhlelo lolukhulu letekutfutsa lwemnyaka we2050 futsi usekela luhlelo lwahulumende lwekwakha kabusha nele kuvuselela umnotfo.
tgt: wongeza ngelithi le projekthi iyinxalenye yesicwangciso sophuhliso sesizwe sika2030 kunye nesicwangciso esiphambili sezothutho sika2050 kwaye ixhasa isicwangciso sikarhulumente sokwakha ngokutsha nokuvuselela uqoqosho.

src: kute kube ngunyalo, hulumende uhlose kutfu tfukisa luhlelo lwetekutfutsa lolutawuhambisana neti dzinga tangemphela tebantfu labahlala eni ngizimu afrika futsi lutawu bonelela bantfu labanemali lencane lebayisebentisela kukhokhela tindleko teku hamba.
tgt: ukuza kuthi ga ngoku, urhulumente uzimisele ukuphuhlisa inkqubo yezothutho ehambelana neemfuno zokwenyani zabantu abahlala emzantsi afrika kwaye ikwazi uku bonelela abantu abanemali encinci bakwazi ukuhamba ngeendleko ezincinci ezindleleni.

src: matekane utsi lokutfu tfukiswa kwalomgwaco kutawutsatsa iminyaka lesemkhatsini kwesi phohlongo ne10 kodvwa kuvalwa kwemigwaco kutawugcinwa kusezingeni leliphasi.
tgt: umatekane uthi ukugqi tywa kolu phuculo kuza kuthatha iminyaka ephakathi kwesibhozo ukuya kwelishumi, kwaye ukuvalwa kweendlela kuza kugcinwa kungekho kukhulu.

src: ungete nge kutsi bashayeli betimoto batawuhlala batiswa njalo ngekubambeleleka loku tawuba emgwaceni futsi baphatsi bakwazulunatali lababukene netekuhamba kwetimoto batawusita kulawula timoto emgwaceni.
tgt: uhambisa athi abaqhubi bazokwaziswa xa kuzakubakho ulibaziseko endleleni kwaye abezendlela abasemagunyeni kwazulunatal bazakuncedisa ukugcina ulawulo lwendlela.

src: tjwala bungalimata imphilo yemntfwana wakho asengakatalwa vukuzenzele unnamed bomake labakhulelwe banemsebenti weku tivikela banganatsi tjwala ngoba bungabanga sifo lesitsikameta kukhula kwemntfwana.
tgt: utywala bungayonakalisa impilo yomntwana wakho ongekazalwa vukuzenzele unnamed abasetyhini abakhulelweyo banoxanduva lokungaseli kuba utywala bunokubangela imeko echaphazela ukukhula komntwana ngelixa esese siswini.

src: loku kushiwo lisekela lendvuna yetekufutfukisa tenhlalo, hendrietta bogo panezulu, losandza kucala luhlelo lwekulwa nesifo i999 foetal alcohol spectrum disorder (ifasd).
tgt: oku kuthethwe nguse kela mphathiswa wesebe lophuhliso loluntu, uhendrietta bogopanezulu, osandul' ukuphehlelela inkqubo exhasa ukulwa ne999 foetal alco hol spectrum disorder (ifasd).

src: inhloso yalomkhankhaso kugcugcutela imimango kutsi isite kuvikela bantfwana lebasengakabelekwa ngekufundzisa bantfu, kakhulu bomake labasakhona kubeleka, mayelana nebu ngoti bekunatsa tjwala ube ukhulelwe noma usamu nyisa.
tgt: iinjongo zeli phulo kukukhuthaza nokufundisa uluntu ukuba luncedise ekukhuseleni iintsana ezingekazalwa, ingakumbi abasetyhini abakwiminyaka yokuzala, libafundisa ngo bungozi bokusela utywala ngethuba bekhulelwe okanye bencancisa.

src: "kumcoka kutsi bonkhe bomake labakhulelwe nalabo labanesifiso sekutala bantfwana labaphile kahle bayekele kunatsa tjwala.
tgt: "kubalulekile ukuba onke amanina akhulelweyo kunye nabo banqwenela ukubeleka abantwana abasempilweni bangaseli tywala.

src: umonakalo lobangwa yifasd uba wemphilo yonkhe futsi awubuyiseleki emuva, futsi bantfwana labatalwa nalokugula baba netinkinga tasemtimbeni netasengco ndvweni," kwasho lisekela lendvuna bogopanezulu emcimbini wekwetfulwa kwaloluhlelo.
tgt: umonakalo owenziwe yifasd usisigxina kwaye awubuyiseleki mva, abantwana abazelwe bekule meko baneengxaki ngokwa semzimbeni nasengqondweni," utshilo usekela mphathiswa ubogopanezulu kumsitho wokuphehlelela eli phulo.

src: wangeta ngekutsi iningi zimu afrika yatiwa ngekuba nenkinga yekunatsa tjwala, lelive libalwa njengalamanye lamabi lahamba embili emhlabeni ngenca yemazinga alo ekunatsa tjwala.
tgt: wongeze ngelithi umzantsi afrika waziwa njenge lizwe elinengxaki yokusela, ukwelona zinga liphezulu lokusela utywala emhlabeni wonke jikelele.

src: lisekela lendvuna bogopanezulu usandza kuhambela tincenye letehlukahlukene talelive letfu, afundzisa bomake mayelana nebungoti bekunatsa tjwala bakhulelwe njengencenye yemkhankaso we999 fasd.
tgt: njengenxalenye yephulo le999 fasd, usekela mphathiswa ubogopanezulu kutsha nje utyelele iindawo ezohlukeneyo zelizwe, efundisa amanina ngobungozi bokusela utywala ngethuba ekhu lelwe.

src: lesikhatsi aseboitekong erustenburg enyakatfo nshonalanga, watjela takhamuti kutsi lizinga leku setjentiswa kabi kwetjwala emalokishini liyesabeka.
tgt: ngethuba ebeseboitekong erustenburg emntla ntshona, uxelele abahlali ukuba liyakhwanxhisa izinga lokuselwa kakhulu kotywala kule lokishi.

src: make lonetinyanga letine akhulelwe lohlala eboite kong, basetsane tlalang (28), lobekahambele lomunye walemikhankaso, utse wayekela futsi wagcina ngci kunatsa emva kwekutfola kutsi ukhulelwe futsi watsi sewuhambela emaseshini asemtfolamphilo elwatiso newesikhatsi lesandvulela kubeleka.
tgt: owasetyhini oneenyanga ezine ekhulelwe nokwangumhlali waseboitekong, ubasetsana tlalang (28), obezimase elinye lala ma phulo, uthi wayeka kwaphela ukusela utywala emva kokuva ukuba ukhulelwe kwaye uthi uhamba iiseshoni ezifundisa ngolwazi lwangaphambi kokubeleka ekliniki.

src: uncusa labanye bomake labakhulelwe kutsi bayekele leso sikhatsi kunatsa tjwala nekusebentisa tidzakwamiva.
tgt: ubongoze nabanye oomama abakhulelweyo ukuba bayeke kwangoko ukusela utywala nokusebenzisa iziyobisi xa befumana iindaba zokuba bakhulelwe.

src: umshikashika wekubuyisa ubuntfu eningizimu afrika vukuzenzele unnamed mhla ti12 inyoni 1977, ste phen bantfu biko washona agcinwe maphoyisa ejele lelatiwa ngepretoria central prison.
tgt: umzabalazo wokubuyisa ubuntu emzantsi afrika vukuzenzele unnamed ngomhla we12 kweyomsintsi 1977, ustephen bantu biko wasweleka eselugcinweni lwamapolisa kwintolongo enkulu ekumbindi wasepitoli.

src: sitfunti sebuntfu, leku simiso lesihamba embili kulobushoshovu bakhe bekubuyisa sitfunti semuntfu lomnyama, sacekelwa phasi.
tgt: kodwa ke yena wasweleka engakhange ayingcamliswe incindi yokunikwa isidima somntu, lo kwakungowona mongo womgaqomthetho owawuphembelela ubutshantliziyo bakhe obabukhuthaza isidima somntu omnyama.

src: ngekwemagama emmeli wemndeni wakhe sir sydney kentridge, "kushona kwakhe bekubuhlungu kakhulu futsi bekayedvwa ashonela emethini lephasi esemendeni yelijele."
tgt: ngokwamazwi egqwetha losapho luka biko, umhlekazi usydney kentridge, wathi "ukufa kuka biko yayikukufa okwakubuhlungu, ukufa komntu owayesele elilolo eliqhaqhazela amazinyo lodwa lilele phezu kwemethi ebandayo eyondlalwe phezu komgangatho wesisele sento longo owawubanda okwelitye lomkhekce".

src: kutawuhlala kuyintfo lebanga lusizi lolukhulu emva kwayo yonkhe leminyaka leyengcile, kukhumbula kutsi steve biko bakaneminyaka le30 kuphela uma ashona.
tgt: kunanamhla oku kuya kuhlala kungumthombo ompompoza usizi olukhulu kuyo yonke le minyaka, ukukhumbula ukuba usteve biko wasweleka eneminyaka engama30 kuphela nje qha ubudala.

src: wabulawa asengakafiki esicongweni semphilo yakhe ngilabo bebasaba emandla ekubona imibono yakhe lesetulu yekutikhulula kanye nemitamo yekufaka kumuntfu lomnyama kutitsandza nekuba nesitfunti emadvodzeni nakubomake besive lesinsundvu.
tgt: isibane sakhe sobomi saci nywa ngaphambi kwexesha ngabo babesoyika amandla kunye nefuthe lokuvakala kweengcamango zakhe zokuzikhulula kwakunye neenzame zakhe zokuxhobisa amadoda namabhinqa amnyama ukuba azingce ngobu bona kunye nesidima sawo.

src: azange akhone kubona ekuphileni kwakhe loko lokubitwa ngekutsi ‘ngumklomelo lokhatimu lako", lekukubona buntfu bangemphela.
tgt: akazange akubone ebomini bakhe oko wayesakukubiza ngokuba ‘libhaso elimenye zelayo’, ukuqondwa kobuntu bokwenene.

src: abhala ngalomcondvo, kwadvuma kutsi watsi: "ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi sitawukhona kupha iningizimu afrika sipho lesikhulu kunato tonkhe – kukhulisa sitfunti sebuntfu."
tgt: ebhala ngalo mbono, waba ngundaba mlonyeni xa wayesithi: "ekuhambeni kwexesha siza kukwazi ukunika umzantsi afrika esona sipho sikhulu sinokubakho – ubuntu."

src: uma sincoba sitfola inkhu luleko yetfu ngemnyaka we1994, besivisisa kutsi lilungelo lekuvota liyincenye leyodvwa yemzabalazo wetfu wekutfola sitfunti sebuntfu.
tgt: xa sasifumana inkululeko yethu ngo1994, saye saqonda ukuba ilungelo lokuvota liyenye inxalenye nje yomza balazo wethu wokubuyiselwa kwesidima somntu.

src: eminyakeni lemashumi lamabili nesiphohlongo singene kuntsandvoye linyenti, sihlangabetene netinseyeya letinyenti, letifana nebuphuya, kuswelakala kwemisebenti nekungalingani.
tgt: kwiminyaka engamashumi amabini anesibhozo singcamla kulawulo lwethu lwentando yesininzi, sijongene nemingeni emininzi, efana nentlupheko, intswelangqesho nokungalingani.

src: ngenca yaloko, sivamise kunga boni kutsi sisuka khashane kanganani kute sikhone kufeza timiso letisisekelo semtsetfosisekelo wetfu futsi letichumanisa imicondvo netifundziso tasteve biko.
tgt: ngenxa yoko, side sizifumane sele silibele ukujonga ukuba mngakanani na umgama esele siwuhambile wokufe zekisa umgaqosiseko wethu osekelwe phezu kwemithethosiseko eyayibethelelwe ziingcinga neemfundiso zikasteve biko.

src: ngemnyaka we1997, umbuso lobewungenalu velo wabulala lomunye umholi walelive lakitsi lobekatse mbisa kakhulu ngekumncisha kudla, emanti kanye nekwelashwa lobe kakudzinga kakhulu ngenca yekushaywa kabuhlungu ngemaphoyisa elubandlu lulo.
tgt: ngo1977, urhulumente ongenantliziyo nowayexhu zula imikhala ngelo xesha, wabulala enye yeenkokeli zelizwe lethu ezazinenkamva eliqaqambileyo ngokuyivimba ukutya, amanzi kunye nonyango eyayilufuna ngokukhawuleza ngenxa yezivubeko zokubethwa kabuhlungu ngamapolisa ocalucalulo.

src: emva kweminyaka lemashumi lamabili, sincumo senkantolo semnyaka we1997, inkantolo yemtsetfosisekelo yatsi kuphumelelisa emalungelo lasisekelo awo wonkhe umuntfu nekutfola ema lungelo abo etemnotfo kuluphawu lwemmango wentsandvoyelinyenti loluhlose kubuyisela sitfunti lesilahlekile.
tgt: kwiminyaka engamashumi amabini emva kwesi sithwakumbe, kwisigwebo sango1997, inkundla yomgaqosiseko yagweba ngelithi ukuzalisekisa amalu ngelo asisiseko ommi ngamnye kunye nokuzama ukufezekisa amalungelo ommi ngamnye entlaloqoqosho luphawu loluntu olubonisa intando yesininzi olunjongo yalo ikukuhlangula isidima somntu esasisele silahlekile.

src: namuhla eningizimu afrika, siyachubeka kuse bentela kuphumelelisa emalungelo lasisekelo awo wonkhe umuntfu waseningizimu afrika kute baphile imphilo lesezingeni lenge nato tifo, indlala nekuswela.
tgt: nanamhla oku emzantsi afrika, siyaqhubeka nokuse benzela ukuzalisekisa amalungelo asisiseko omntu ngamnye wasemzantsi afrika ukuze aphile ubomi obusemgangathweni obungenazifo, indlala nokuswela.

src: imibuso yentsandvoye linyenti lelandzelanako isebentise imitsetfomigomo leletsa sitfunti sebantfu balelive lebesilahlekile ngekubanika imfundvo, kunakekelwa kwetemphilo, tindlu kanye netinsita letisi sekelo.
tgt: ulawulo lwalo rhulumente wentando yesininzi ngo kulandelanayo luphumeze imigaqonkqubo yokuhlangula isidima esilahlekileyo soninzi lweli lizwe ngokuthi lubonelela ngemfundo, ukhathalelo lwempilo, izindlu kunye neenkonzo ezisisiseko.

src: namuhla eningizimu afrika, kutfola imfundvo lesezingeni kulilungelo lelisisekelo.
tgt: namhlanje emzantsi afrika, imfundo ekwinqanaba eliphukcukileyo ililungelo elisisiseko.

src: hulumende utjale timali kumfundvo legcile ekukhuliseni kahle bantfwana, ekusekeleni imiphumela yetifundvo ebantfwaneni balelive lakitsi labasesebancane, futsi kusita ummango ngeluhlelo leku phakela bantfwana kudla etikolweni kucinisekisa kutsi bafundzi labasesebancane batfola imiphumela lesetulu.
tgt: urhulumente utyala imali kuphuhliso lwabantwana kwisigaba esisaqalisa imfundo, oku ukwenza ngelokuxhasa iziphumo ezintle zokufunda kubemi bethu abangabona baselula, kwaye ukwabo nelela ngohlangulo loluntu ngeenkqubo zokutyisa abantwana ezikolweni ukuqinisekisa ukuba aba fundi abaselula bayakwazi ukufumana ezona ziphumo zibhetele kangangoko banako.

src: ngalesikimu savelonkhe selusito lwetimali kuba fundzi nangaletinye tinhlobo telusito lwahulumende, tinkhulungwane tebantfu labasha baseningizimu afrika labavela eminde nini lephuyile bakhonile kuba bodokotela, bammeli, bothishela, bososayensi, emaathizeni nabosomabhi zinisi.
tgt: ngenkqubo yesizwe yoncedo lwezezimali yabafundi kunye nezinye iindlela ezahlukeneyo zenkxaso karhulumente, amawakawaka abantu abatsha basemzantsi afrika abaphuma kumakhaya angathathi ntweni baye bakwazi ukuba ngoogqirha, amagqwetha, ootishala, izazinzulu, amagcisa kunye noosomashishini.

src: hulumende usekela takhamuti letibutsakatsaka ngekusebentisa tinhlelo tekusita emakhaya laphuyile futsi iniketa ematfuba emisebenti ngaletinhlelo tahulumende tekucasha bantfu labanengi.
tgt: urhulumente uyabaxhasa abemi abasokolayo nabasemngciphekweni ngokusebenzisa iindlela eziluqilima eziqinisekisa ukubonelelwa koluntu, kwaye ubonelela ngamathuba emi sebenzi amaninzi ngokuvula iinkqubo ezininzi zokuqeshwa koluntu.

src: kuleningizimu afrika lebeyicindzetela leyabulala steve biko, bekute kukhu luma ngekukhululeka kantsi kuba sishoshovi kutepolitiki bekuholela ekutseni uboshwe ngaphandle kwekushushiswa noma ubulawe.
tgt: kumzantsi afrika wengcinezelo usteve biko owasweleka ephila kuwo, inkululeko yokuthetha yayinemida nemimiselo, kwaye xa ulitshantliziyo lezopolitiko wawuye uzitsa lele amanzi ngomsele, kuba kaloku wawuvalelwa okanye ufumane isohlwayo esiqatha nangakumbi.

src: namuhla eningizimu afrika, bantfu labasha labaneminyaka lelingana naleyo bekanayo steve biko noma lemincane kunaleyo bahamba embili kutebu shoshovi betintfo leti sedvute nabo, futsi bayakhona kutihlela kahle ngekukhululeka ngaphandle kwekuhlukunyetwa noma kwekudzingiswa.
tgt: namhlanje emzantsi afrika, abantu abatsha abakule minyaka wayekuyo usteve biko abanye bade bangaphantsi, bahamba phambili kubutshantliziyo bezabalazela izizathu ezihambelana neemfuno zobomi babo, kwaye bayakwazi ukuququzelela iindibano ngaphandle kokungcungcuthekiswa okanye ukugxothwa.

src: kukhu luma nekuhlanganyela ngekukhululeka, lilungelo lekubhikisha kanye nelilungelo lekulingana ngembi kwemtsetfo ku yalandzelwa kubo bonkhe bantfu.
tgt: inkululeko yokuthetha nokunxulumana, ilungelo lokuqhankqalaza kunye nelungelo lokulingana phambi komthetho lifunyanwa ngumntu wonke.

src: sisive, sihambe libanga lelidze kute siphumelele kutfola sitfunti sebuntfu, lekusimiso besihlonishwa ngusteve biko.
tgt: njengelizwe, sele sihambe umgama omde ekufezekiseni ukuhlangulwa kwesidima somntu, nekungeyona nto owayeyixabisile kakhulu usteve biko.

src: kodvwa, sisanendlela lendze leku mele siyihambe.
tgt: ukanti ke, usemde nomgama ekusafu neka siwuhambile.

src: kungasebenti, kungabi nendlu, nagezi noma emanti lahambako, kungabi nemhlaba, kungabi nemakhono noma ematfuba, tigidzi tebantfu baseningizimu afrika basengakayitfoli imphilo lebafuna kuyi phila.
tgt: ngaphandle kwemisebenzi, ngaphandle kwendlu, umbane okanye amanzi, ngaphandle komhlaba, ngaphandle kwe zakhono okanye amathuba, izigidi zabemi bomzantsi afrika zisavinjwe ubomi ezi bufunayo nezibufaneleyo.

src: kungako hulu mende asebentisana nebalingani betemnotfo kute kwakhiwe umnotfo lofaka wonkhe umuntfu, kwakhiwe ematfuba emisebenti, kuncedvwe emabhizinisi aphumelele futsi kuliwe nebuphuya nendlala.
tgt: yiyo loo nto urhulumente esebenzi sana namahlakani kwezentlalo ukwakha uqoqosho olubanda kanyayo, ukudala amathuba emisebenzi, ukwenza ukuba amashishini aphumelele kwaye alwe nentsokolo nendlala.

src: luhlelo lwekunika bahlukunyetwa emandla lubuyisa litsemba owen mngadi luhlelo lasethohoya ndou lwekunika bahlu kunyetwa emandla (itvep) lufuna kubuyisa litsemba nekutitsemba kuluhlelo lwetebulungiswa ngekusebentisa tinyatselo talo letinemandla letihlose kusita labo labasindzile kuludlame lolumayelana netebulili (igbv) nasekudlwengulweni ngekubanika tinsita tetengco ndvo.
tgt: inkqubo yokuxhotyiswa kwamaxhoba ibuyisela ithemba owen mngadi inkqubo yokuxhotyi swa kwamaxhoba asethohoyandou (itvep) izama ukubuyisela ithemba kwinkqubo yobulungisa ngamaphulo ayo angqingqwa ajolise ekuncedeni amaxhoba obundlobongela obusekelwe kwisini (igbv) kunye no dlwengulo ngokuwabonelela ngeenkonzo zeengcebiso ngokwasengqondweni.

src: letvep leyacalwa elimpo po eminyakeni lema20 leye ngcile, isebentela etibhedlela itshilidzini nedonald fraser letingaphasi kwamasipala wasekhaya ithulamela.
tgt: itvep eyasekwa elimpopo kwiminyaka engama20 eyadlulayo, isebenza kwizibhe dlele zasetshilidzini nasedonald fraser phantsi ko masipala wasekhaya wasethulamela.

src: libamba lemcondzisi waloluhlelo fhatuwani manthada utsi loluhlelo luhlose kufaka indlela yekubuka tintfo lengavumeli nakancane kutsi kube nekuhlukunyetwa ngekwemacansi, ngekwegbv kanye nekwebantfwana kuletakhamuti tasethohoyandou, ngoba kuliciniso lelimsulwa kutsi loluhlobo lwemacala ayenteka kulendzawo.
tgt: umlawuli obambeleyo ufhatuwani manthada uthi le nkqubo ijolise ekuwusiphu leni kungasali nengcambu umkhwa wokuhlasela ngokwesondo, igbv kunye nokuxhatshazwa kwabantwana kubahlali basethohoyandou, oku ngenxa yokuba la matyala axhaphakile kulo mmandla.

src: utsi esikhatsini lesengci le, lubalobalo lwemacala beluvamise kukhomba kutsi bewamanengi emacala ekudlwengula ethohoyandou, kodvwa itvep ibe neligalelo lelikhulu ekuletseni lwatiso nekunika bantfu tinsita tekwelulekwa ngekuhlukumeteka kute kuliwe nalomkhuba lomubi.
tgt: uthi kwixesha langaphambili, amanani olwaphulomthetho ayebonisa ukuba maninzi amatyala odlwengu lo ethohoyandou, kodwa itvep yenze imitsi emikhulu ekufundiseni, nasekunqa ndeni lo mkhuba eluntwini, nasekuboneleleni ngeenkonzo zokucebisa ngokwasengqo ndweni kwixhoba elisothuki leyo.

src: njengoba umhlaba wonkhe utawube ubuke lomkhankhaso wetinsuku leti16 tebushoshovi bekucedza ludlame lolubhekiswe kubomake nasebantfwaneni kusuka mhla ti25 lweti kuya kumhla ti10 ingongoni, manthada utsi loluhlelo lunelisekile ngaloku leselikwentile lekukugcugcutela takhamuti kutsi tiwavisise emalungelo ato nekutsi tibike uma kwenteka emacala.
tgt: njengoko ihlabathi liza kube liqwalasela iphulo leentsuku ezili16 zokungaxhatshazwa kwabasetyhini nabantwana ukusuka ngomhla wama25 kweyenkanga ukuya kowe10 kweyomnga, umanthada uthi le nkqubo yanelisekile yinkqubela esele yenziwe yokukhuthaza abahlali ukuba baqonde amalungelo abo kwaye baxele nezenzo zolwaphulomthetho.

src: "letvep itfola bahlukunye twa beludlame lwasekhaya labasemkhatsini kwe80 ne100 njalo ngenyanga, bese kuba macala ekudlwengulwa la45 kuya ku50 labikwa njalo ngenyanga," kusho manthada.
tgt: "itvep yamkela amaxhoba aphakathi kwama80 ukuya kwi100 odushe lwasekhaya nyanga nganye, ngelixa amatyala odlwengulo angama45 ukuya kuma50 nawo axelwa ngenyanga," utsho umanthada.

src: sikhungo lesisodvwa lesiphetse konkhe kwalolu lelo siniketa tinsita letehluka hlukene kubahlukunye twa, letifaka ekhatsi lusito lwetemtsetfo, kuvikeleka kwebahlukunyetwa kulabo lababahlukumetako, kula ndzelela emacala lasenkantolo, kwelulekwa nekuniketwa emandla ngekusebentisa luhlelo lwekutfutfukisa emakhono, ngaloko bahlukunyetwa batfola litfuba lekucala kabusha.
tgt: amaziko enkqubo anikezela ngeenkonzo ezahlukeneyo kumaxhoba, kubandakanywa ukufikelela kuncedo lwezomthetho, ukukhuselwa kwamaxhoba kubenzi bobubi, ukujongwa kwamatyala ezi nkundleni, iingcebiso kunye nokuxhotyiswa ngophuhliso lwezakhono, ngaloo ndlela ke le nkqubo inika amaxhoba isiqalo esitsha.

src: manthada utsi letvep isebenta ngekubambisana nebetemisebenti yetemapho yisa aseningizimu afrika, litiko letemphilo kanye nelekutfutfukiswa kwemma ngo kute kuvikelwe kutsi bahlukunyetwa bangaphindzi bahlukumeteke kwesibili ngalesikhatsi bavula emacala.
tgt: umanthada uthi itvep isebenzisana ngokusondeleleneyo nenkonzo yesipolisa yomzantsi afrika, isebe leze mpilo kunye nesebe lophu hliso loluntu ukuthintela uku phathwa kakubi kwamaxhoba ityeli lesibini xa ekwinkqubo yokuvula ityala.

src: "emacaleni ekudlwengula, basebenti betemphilo nema phoyisa beta etikhungweni tetvep kutosita bahlukunye twa bavule emacala bavulele labo lababahlukumetako futsi, babanika tinsita tekwelulekwa," usho njalo.
tgt: "kumatyala odlwengulo, abasebenzi bezempilo kunye namapolisa beza kumaziko etvep ukuzakunceda ama xhoba ukuba avule amatyala olwaphulomthetho avulele abophulimthetho kwaye ba phinde babonelele ngeenkonzo zoluleko ngokwasengqo ndweni," utshilo.

src: itvep ihlalisa labo labahlukumetekile kute kufike etinsukwini leti14, kodvwake, loluhlelo lwekuhlaliswa lungalulwa emacaleni lafaka umndeni wonkhe noma bantfwana.
tgt: itvep ihlalisa amaxhoba ukuya kutsho kwiintsuku ezili14, nangona kunjalo, ulungiselelo linokwandiswa kwiimeko ezibandakanya usapho lonke okanye aba ntwana.

src: "sineyunithi yekunika emandla lehamba icocisana nebantfu futsi ibafundzise mayelana nemalungelo abo.
tgt: "sinomanyano lokuxhobisa, oluqhuba iingxoxo zoluntu kwaye lufundise abantu ngamalungelo abo.

src: sisebentela bantfu labatakha muti tasethohoyandou nemaphetselo labangetulu kwesigidzi.
tgt: sinceda abahlali abangaphezu kwesigidi abasuka ethohoyandou nakwiindawo ezisingqongi leyo.

src: itvep futsi ivulele bantfu laba44 ematfuba emsebenti labasebentela ematiko lahlukahlukene lafana nelitiko letetimali, letebasebenti nelekwenta luhlolo.
tgt: sikwazile ukubuyisela ithemba kwinkqubo yobulungisa nokulawulwa kolwaphulomthetho ngenxa yobudlelwane bethu namapolisa," utshilo.

src: nanoma loluhlelo luhlala lutfola imali ler90 000 ngekota lebuya kulitiko lwetekutfutfukiswa kwe mmango laselimpopo, itvep yatsintseka kabi ngecovid19 ngoba bonkhe labo bebanikela ngetimali bahoca, ngaleyondlela taba nemtselela lomubi tinchubo tekusebenta talenhlangano.
tgt: itvep ikwadale amathuba engqesho kubantu abangama44 abasebenza kumasebe awohlukeneyo afana nelezemali, alabasebenzi kunye novavanyo.

src: kodvwa, sikhwama sekuphendvula kuludlame lolubhekiswe kubomake nakulabasikati (igbvf), lesasungulwa ngumengameli cyril ramaphosa ngendlovana kulomnyaka, abambisene nenhlangano yabomake yemhlaba yaseningizimu afrika kanye nebalingani bayo kutenhlalo, balusitile loluhlelo.
tgt: nangona le nkqubo ifumana inkxasomali ye r90 000 rhoqo ngekota kwisebe lophuhliso lwentla lo laselimpopo, itvep yachatshazelwa yicovid19 njengoko abaxhasi ngezimali baye barhoxa, nto leyo echaphazela kakubi iinkqubo zokusebenza zalo mbutho.

src: kunemali letigidzi letir128 leyacokelelwa ngeminikelo levela kumkhakha lotimele, lephuma esikhwameni semikhakha lehlukahlukene, lesikhwama segbvf sitawusita futsi sitawusekela kusetjentiswa kweluhlelo lwendlelalisu yavelonkhe yegbvf.
tgt: kodwa ke nangona kunjalo, ingxowamali yokusabela ubundlobongela obusekwe kwisini nokubulawa kwabasetyhini (igbvf), eyaphehlelelwa ngumo ngameli ucyril ramaphosa kweyomdumba kulo nyaka, kunye neqonga lamazwe ngamazwe lamakhosikazi omzantsi afrika kunye namahlakani asekuhlaleni ayincedile kakhulu le nkqubo.

src: itvep yaniketwa imali yalomnyaka ler250 000 futsi itawuphindze itfole lenye imali ngemnyaka we2023.
tgt: itvep yayiphakathi kweqela lokuqala lemibutho elwa negbvf, ukufumana inkxasomali.

src: manthada utsi timali tente kutsi itvep ikhone kufinye lela kubahlukunyetwa labanengi futsi ibe igcina inhlangano isebenta kahle.
tgt: ngesixamali ser128 lezigidi esathi saqokelelwa ngeminikelo esuka kwicandelo labucala, ingxowamali yamacandelo amaninzi, ingxowamali yegbvf iza kunceda kwaye ixhase ukuphunyezwa kwesicwa ngcisoqhinga sesizwe segbvf.
